tgt: Walk on carpet, past the bed, go out double doors and wait by wine rack.

src: exit room straight toward couch there
tgt: Exit the room and go straight toward the couch and stop there.

src: down first flight of stairs right steps stop
tgt: Walk down the first flight of stairs and turn right. Go down 2 steps and stop.

src: turn right down hallway right past water cooler once at last doorway on right
tgt: Turn right and walk down the hallway to your right past the water cooler. Stop once you are at the last doorway on the right.

src: straight toward fireplace then stairs on left then
tgt: Go straight toward the fireplace then turn left and pass the stairs on your left then stop.

src: stairs then right wait in front of double doors in hallway
tgt: Go up the stairs then turn right. Wait in front of the double doors in the hallway.

src: exit room walk straight across next room wait in front of bathroom
tgt: Exit the room and walk straight across the next room. Wait in front of the bathroom.

src: with pool behind into house right past chairs piano into room with shelves with books alcohol
tgt: With the pool behind you, go into the house. Take a right past the chairs and to the piano. Go into the room with all the shelves with books and alcohol.

src: stairs straight into kitchen there
tgt: Go down stairs, walk straight into the kitchen and stop there.

src: straightly with upstairs.then enter in room
tgt: Go straightly with upstairs.Then enter in to wash room.

src: walk out of closet right through door on right down steps once down steps right down steps once at bottom of steps there
tgt: Walk out of the closet and turn right. Go through the door that will be on your right and walk down the steps. Once down the steps, turn right and walk down more steps. Once at the bottom of the steps, wait there.

src: with green wall immediate left forward into hallway way end at end of hallway right bedroom
tgt: With the green painted wall to your immediate left, walk forward into the hallway all the way to the end. At the end of the hallway, turn right and enter the bedroom.

src: stairs with slatted fence left forward until door on left
tgt: Go down the stairs with the slatted fence to your left and continue forward until you reach the door on your left.

src: walk past couch turn walk past counter in front of shelf
tgt: Walk past the couch and turn left. Walk left past the counter and stop in front of the shelf.

src: forward first door on right into door then right into second door on right forward diagonally in front of bed
tgt: Move forward to the first door on the right. Turn into the door, and then turn right into the second door on the right. Move forward diagonally to stand in front of the bed.

src: walk around exterior of home through tiled patio area towards backyard pool area walk between home pool along tiled patio open door home walk towards hot tub in corner of yard
tgt: Walk around the exterior of the home through the tiled patio area towards the backyard and pool area. Walk between the home and the pool along the tiled patio continue passed the open door to the home and walk towards the hot tub in the corner of the yard.

src: turn next second black chair
tgt: Turn around and wait next to the second black chair.

src: walk through garage door wait outside
tgt: Walk through the garage door and wait outside.

src: exit laundry room left stairs door on balcony turn then right on first stair outside
tgt: exit laundry room to hallway, turn left and go up stairs, go out the door and on to the balcony, turn left then right and stop on first stair outside.

src: walk past bed on left through door immediatly before under doorway
tgt: Walk past the bed on the left, and through the door. Stop immediatly before passing under the doorway.

src: walk toward bed bed right room straight room ahead wait near sink
tgt: Walk toward the bed. When you get to the bed. Turn right and exit the room. Continue straight and enter the room straight ahead. Wait near the sink.

src: walk into dinning room turn left then through kitchen stop near kitchen table
tgt: Walk into the dinning room and turn left. Then walk through the kitchen and stop near the kitchen table.

src: exit room immediately left then right forward in room entrance
tgt: Exit the room and immediately turn left, then turn right, move forward and wait in the room entrance.

src: stairs straight wooden table with wooden benches stop after on blue carpet at end closest
tgt: Go up the stairs and go straight to the wooden table with wooden benches.  Stop after stepping on the blue carpet at the end closest to you.

src: walk along kitchen counter then right past arched windows wait by buffet
tgt: Walk along the kitchen counter, then turn right, proceed past the arched windows. Wait by the buffet.

src: past top of stairs right at end of walkway turn left wait in doorway
tgt: Go past the top of the stairs and go to the right. At the end of the walkway turn to the left and wait in the doorway.

src: turn degrees stairs up stairs on landing slight toward door in corner with light switch next in front of door
tgt: Turn 180 degrees to face stairs. Walk up stairs. On landing, make slight left toward door in corner with light switch next to it. Stop in front of door.

src: turn around out of room left straight past stairs into last room on left wait in bedroom
tgt: Turn around and walk out of the room and take a left. Walk straight past the stairs and into the last room on the left. Wait in the bedroom.

src: exit walk in closet room then right double door patio wait there
tgt: Exit the walk in closet to the room then turn right and go out the double door to the patio and wait there.

src: exit kitchen through living room hallway right by statute wait at painting
tgt: Exit the kitchen, walk through the living room, enter the hallway to the right by the statute, wait at the painting.

src: away from desk on left side of foose ball table turn through doorway straight before over sized chair
tgt: walk away from desk on the left side of foose ball table, turn left and walk through doorway, walk straight and stop before you reach the over sized chair.

src: exit room turn on second door wait near bed
tgt: Exit the room. Turn left on the second door and wait near the bed.

src: with abstract art towards left forward until stairs ahead slightly left down stairs until steps from bottom
tgt: With the abstract art towards your left, go forward until you reach the stairs ahead and slightly to the left. Continue down these stairs until you're four steps from the bottom.

src: enter house right straight into bathroom once counter on right
tgt: Enter the house and go right. Go straight into the bathroom. Stop once you pass the counter on the right.

src: turn degrees down hall past posters past first set of doorways right into room walk toward double doors that lead outside wait at end of rug
tgt: Turn around 180 degrees and walk down the hall past the posters. Go past the first set of doorways and turn right into the room walk toward the double doors that lead outside and wait at the end of the rug.

src: exit bathroom walk on carpet then right bedroom door face room through glass door wait on balcony
tgt: Exit bathroom.   Walk on carpet, then turn right.  Enter the bedroom door.  Face left, and exit the room through glass door.  Wait on balcony.

src: straights through door into main entry behind couch
tgt: Walk up straights through door into main entry, stop behind couch.

src: walk through dining room toward partition then right in exterior doorway
tgt: Walk through the dining room, toward the partition, then veer right and wait in the exterior doorway.

src: walk along front porch past rocking chairs into front door of home inside around corner near before couch walk into bedroom at end of hall
tgt: Walk along the front porch past the rocking chairs and into the front door of the home. Continue inside and walk around the corner near before reaching the couch. Walk into the bedroom at the end of the hall.

src: turn stairs turn at bottom of stairs
tgt: TURN AROUND AND GO DOWN THE STAIRS. TURN LEFT AT THE BOTTOM OF THE STAIRS.

src: down stairs left walk glass table stand behind clear chair at end of table
tgt: Walk down the stairs and take a left. Walk to the glass table and stand behind the clear chair at the end of the table.

src: turn right into second door
tgt: Turn around and take a right into the second door.

src: away from windows through doorway towards small blue couch turn through doorway before white chair right at room table turn on red carpet walk through doorway towards wall stop
tgt: walk away from windows to outside through doorway towards small blue couch, turn left and walk through doorway before white chair, turn right at dining room table and turn left on red carpet, walk straight through doorway towards red wall and stop.

src: away from piano right of wood door down hallway into bedroom on right in bedroom walk towards bathroom once onto tile floor
tgt: walk away from the piano, to the right of the wood door, down the hallway and into the bedroom on the right. turn left in the bedroom and walk towards the bathroom. stop once you made it onto the tile floor.

src: walk bedroom door bedroom dining table backs of couches
tgt: Walk to the bedroom door, and exit the bedroom. Face the dining table and the backs of the couches.

src: walk through doorway right in doorway of room with plane on table
tgt: Walk straight through the doorway and take a right. Stop in the doorway of the room with a plane on the table.

src: stairs hard right into sauna entry stop wait near stacked towels
tgt: Continue up the stairs, turn hard right into the sauna entry. Stop and wait near the stacked towels.

src: exit room on left across lobby room with candles on right at candles
tgt: Exit dressing room to lobby on the left. Walk across lobby to a room with five candles on your right. Stop at candles.

src: up staircase after top of stairs forward outside through door wait by couch
tgt: Walk up the staircase.   After you reach the top of stairs, continue forward to go outside through the door.  Wait by couch.

src: turn right immediately right again right into bedroom through bedroom through bathroom door
tgt: Turn right and immediately right again.  Take another right into the bedroom.  Walk through bedroom and through the bathroom door.

src: walk along insulated bare walls towards window ahead in next room walk through unfinished room through door on other side of room hallway walk into first open door in hall bedroom with photo art on wall near entrance of classic black white scenes
tgt: Walk along the insulated bare walls towards the window ahead in the next room. Walk through the unfinished room and through the door on the other side of the room that leads to a finished hallway. Walk into the first open door in the hall that leads to a bedroom with photo art on the wall near the entrance of classic black and white scenes.

src: down stairs turn right down stairs right down rest of stairs straight past tree through doorway right between red chairs slight doorway stop at edge of carpet
tgt: walk down stairs, turn right, walk down stairs, turn right and walk down rest of stairs go straight past tree through doorway, slight right between two red chairs, slight left through doorway stop at the edge of carpet.

src: turn until dining room with mirror in corner few steps towards wall next mirror then
tgt: Turn around until you can see the dining room with the mirror in the corner. Take a few steps towards the wall next to the mirror, then stop.

src: turn around past bath tub stairs right towards second set of stairs up at top
tgt: Turn around and walk past the bath tub, move up the stairs and take a right towards the second set of stairs. Walk up them and stop at the top.

src: walk out of bathroom right past table chairs sharp turn right up steps on first step from top
tgt: Walk out of the bathroom and right past the table and chairs. Make sharp turn right and walk up the steps. Stop on the first step from the top.

src: straight path first door into living room area through living room stop at door balcony
tgt: Go straight down the path passing the first door into the living room area. Go through the living room and stop at the door to the balcony.

src: walk across room head hallway right of stairs turn in door left straight next room in front of desk
tgt: Walk across the room and head down the hallway to the right of the stairs. Turn in the door to your left. Keep walking straight and enter the next room and stop in front of the desk.

src: walk into second doorway on left right into hallway stop
tgt: Walk into the second doorway on the left. Turn right and walk into the hallway and stop.

src: walk out of shower past vanity counter with mirrors on top walk through bathroom area around bathtub passing by large cupboards walk over lounge chair near balcony door in bedroom
tgt: Walk out of the shower and past the vanity counter with mirrors on top. Walk through the bathroom area and around the bathtub  passing by the large cupboards. Walk over to the lounge chair that is near the balcony door in the bedroom.

src: walk bed out of door into hallway right out of door dining table out onto patio just patio doors
tgt: Walk straight pass the bed and take a left out of the door and into the hallway where you take a right out of the door pass the dining table out onto the patio stopping just pass the patio doors.

src: down hallway past stairs walk bedroom door on left bedroom walk bathroom then by sink
tgt: Walk down the hallway past the stairs and walk to the bedroom door on your left. Enter the bedroom and walk to the bathroom. Then stand by the sink.

src: walk other side of kitchen wait near sink
tgt: Walk to the other side of the kitchen and wait near the sink.

src: walk in direction of refrigerator right past stove walk across hall into bathroom in front of credenza
tgt: Walk in the direction of the refrigerator, and take a right past the stove. Walk across the hall into the bathroom. Stop in front of the credenza.

src: turn around straight wait at top of stairs in front of second window
tgt: Turn around and walk straight. Wait at the top of the stairs, in front of the second window.

src: through double doors right through entry then through doors stop
tgt: Go through the double doors and turn right. Go through the entry and then go through the doors and stop.

src: walk through doorway towards staircase right hallway enter bedroom on right wait in front of double doors
tgt: Walk through doorway towards staircase. Turn right and proceed down curved hallway. Enter bedroom on your right. Wait in front of double doors.

src: down wooden floor hall with large mirror on wall right until bedroom at end of hall before black desk on right wall
tgt: Walk down the wooden floor hall with a large mirror on the wall to the right until you reach the bedroom at the end of the hall. Stop before the black desk on the right wall.

src: turn after bed wait in doorway of bathroom on left
tgt: Turn left after the bed. Wait in the doorway of the bathroom on the left.

src: turn around across sofas towards doorway slightly left wait just past doorway
tgt: Turn around and walk across the sofas towards the doorway slightly to your left. Wait just past the doorway.

src: step forward right near couch
tgt: Step forward, turn right, turn left and wait near the couch.

src: exit bedroom turn wait at exit
tgt: Exit the bedroom, turn left and wait at the exit.

src: pass large table head straight into door ahead wait by statue on left
tgt: Pass the large table and head straight into the door ahead. Wait by the statue on the left.

src: exit room right straight through room next archway then few steps into big room stop
tgt: Exit the room, make a right and go straight through the room to the next archway, then take a few steps into the big room and stop.

src: exit bathroom left head forward then right bedroom wait at door
tgt: Exit bathroom and make a left, head forward then make a right to enter bedroom, wait at door.

src: past ladies room down long hallway past elevators door staff only on right
tgt: Go past the ladies room down the long hallway, past the elevators, and stop when you reach a door that says staff only on the right.

src: towards door on left of sofas bedroom stop at door balcony
tgt: Go towards the door on the left of the sofas. Enter the bedroom and stop at the door to the balcony.

src: forward so that line up with pool towards middle of pool turn right between chairs forward until stairs
tgt: Go forward so that you line up with the pool. Towards the middle of the pool turn right to be between two chairs. Continue forward until you reach the stairs.

src: walk towards table wait by bowl of fruit
tgt: Walk towards dining table.  Wait by bowl of fruit.

src: recreation area walk across gangway at foot of right bed
tgt: Leave the recreation area and walk across the gangway. Stop at the foot of the right bed.

src: walk along house towards small round table table doorway doorway right inside doorway on wood floor
tgt: Walk along the house towards the small round table. Pass the table and continue to the doorway. Enter the doorway to the right. Wait inside the doorway, on the wood floor.

tgt: Walk straight until you exit the hallway. Turn left and walk toward the large red and white sign. Wait near there.

tgt: Exit the room using the door on the right. Turn left and walk straight down the hallway until you get to the top of the stairs on the left. Wait there.

tgt: Walk around the hot tun and enter the first door past it. In the house take a right into the are with the bed. Stop next to the window before you reach the rug.

tgt: Walk through the doorway, then walk into the next doorway on your left. Walk past the couch on your left, and past the stairs on your right. Walk through the hallway that is past the staircase, Walk through the first door on your left and stop immediatly after walking through.

tgt: exit room make a left, then a right. go down hallway, wait in front of the first office.

tgt: Turn to the inside of the house. Walk to the short marble column. Turn right. Walk towards the mirror. Turn left at doorway. Turn right at first door. Stop at doorway to bedroom.

src: head hallway double doors right hallway right next desk
tgt: Head down the hallway to the double doors.  Turn right and go down the hallway.  Make a right and stop next to the desk.

tgt: Turn around to walk down the hallway past the kitchen. Stop in the dining room and wait near the piano.

src: sign right at sink
tgt: Walk down hall to exit sign. Turn right and stop at sink.

src: bathroom walk through bedroom passing by foot of bed mirror just after through doorway out of bedroom
tgt: Leave the bathroom and walk through the bedroom passing by the foot of the bed and the mirror.  Stop just after passing through the doorway out of the bedroom.

src: walk around corner then forward then at front of lamp
tgt: walk around the corner then turn left, walk forward then stop at the front of the lamp.

src: walk through glass doorway turn left through white doorway then towards stairs wait at top of stairs
tgt: Walk through a glass doorway.  Turn to the left and go through a white doorway.  Then go towards the stairs.  Wait at the top of the stairs.

tgt: Walk straight. Make a slight left to walk through the hallway. Turn slight left into the room and take a right. Walk past the counter and take a right. Wait there.

src: long red rug sitting room froward in open area right at end of area on red rug behind area before doorway into next room/
tgt: Follow the long red rug and leave the sitting room. walk froward in the open area and take a right at the end of the roped off seating area and stand on the red rug behind the sitting area before you reach the doorway into the next room/.

tgt: Turn left out of the seated deck area. Go forward and turn right into the outdoor bedroom area. Head inside through the double doors. Enter the bedroom directly ahead. Stop there.

src: down hall past double glass doors on left after doorway at end of hall
tgt: walk down the hall past the double glass doors on your left. Stop after entering the doorway at the end of the hall.

tgt: Exit the room and follow the hallway to the right. Walk through the first door on the left and continue walking, past the foot of the bed. Enter the bathroom on the left and wait by the door.

src: straight then right step wait in porch
tgt: Go straight then turn right. Go up the step and wait in the porch.

tgt: Exit Laundry room through door. Take a sharp left. Go up the stairs. Wait at the top of stairs by the doorway.

tgt: Walk up the steps in front of you. Turn left and enter the bedroom. Once in the bedroom, turn left and enter the bathroom. Stop in front of the sink facing the mirror.

src: walk through room into bathroom just inside doorway of bedroom
tgt: Walk through the room and into the bathroom. Stop just inside the doorway of the bedroom.

src: room stairs door at top of stairs in doorway
tgt: Leave the room, and go up the stairs. Enter the door at the top of the stairs. Stop in the doorway.

tgt: Walk to the top of the stairs, take a left, walk through the middle door walk way, take a ride, stop in front of the window.

tgt: Head indoors, pass the hallway to the game room and into the bedroom on the far left. Wait near the bed.

tgt: Go to the left of the bed and out of the bedroom. Then go down the hall and make a right at the top of the stairs, go past the stairs and go a couple steps into the bedroom and wait there.

src: way down stairs into hallway through archway right in middle of foyer
tgt: Go all the way down the stairs and turn left into the hallway. Go through the archway and turn right. Stop in the middle of the foyer.

src: turn around out of bathroom right then right room on right wait there
tgt: Turn around and walk out of the bathroom. Take a right and then take another right. Enter the room on the right and wait there.

tgt: Walk straight ahead and past the stairs and enter the doorway.  Turn left and enter the bedroom. Walk to the other side of the bed and enter the doorway to your left. and stop facing in the bathroom.

src: move forward down wooden stairway on left stairs so first stairwell next set of stairs end at stairway right in front of living area with white couch brown table
tgt: Move forward down the wooden stairway on your left. The stairs are split, so you'll need to turn left when you come down the first stairwell to continue down the next set of stairs. End at the stairway right in front of the living area with the white couch and the brown table.

src: bathroom hall on left next brown door across from lounge chairs in pool
tgt: Leave the bathroom and go down the hall on the left. Stop next to the the brown door across from the lounge chairs in the pool.

src: exit bedroom walk through hall toward stairs before wall on left ends stairs thermostat light switches
tgt: Exit the bedroom and walk through the hall toward the stairs. Stop before the wall on your left ends and opens to the stairs, where there is a thermostat and light switches.

src: stairs then right through double doors right of stairs through next doors ahead in front of table with chairs
tgt: Go down the stairs. Then turn right and go through the double doors to the right of the stairs going down. Continue through the next two doors straight ahead and stop in front of the table with four chairs.

src: with bookcase behind forward dinning room through next room until in entry foyer with staircase directly in front of exterior door left
tgt: With the bookcase behind you, start walking forward to exit the dinning room. Continue through the next room until you arrive in the entry foyer with a staircase directly in front of you and the exterior door to your left.

src: straight through hallway turn left on third stair
tgt: Go straight through hallway and turn left and stop on the third stair.

src: exit bathroom main entrance slight into hallway right into open door at steps
tgt: exit bathroom to main entrance. turn slight left into hallway, turn right into open door stopping at steps.

src: walk forward then walk forward again then at console table
tgt: walk forward then turn left the walk forward again then stop at the console table.

src: turn slim hallway straight until doorway right into right at door
tgt: turn around and go down the slim hallway and keep going straight until you get to a doorway and turn right into it and stop right at the door.

src: walk then then at living room
tgt: walk straight then then stop at the living room.

src: walk out of closet in turn past bathroom stop by desk
tgt: Walk out of the closet in turn left. Walk past the bathroom and stop by the desk.

src: stairs at bottom turn then left again down steps wait at bottom of steps
tgt: Continue down the stairs. At the bottom, turn left, then turn left again. Walk down two steps. Wait at the bottom of the steps.

src: step forward turn stairs right wait near television
tgt: Step forward, turn left and go down the stairs. turn right wait near the television.

src: through gate door inside right steps turn into room wait there
tgt: Go through the gate and the door and go inside. Turn right and go down the steps. Turn left and go into the room. Wait there.

src: turn hall at double doors
tgt: Turn around and go down the hall. Stop at the double doors.

src: forward past dresser then then family room by pool table past pool table small bathroom on right wait by sink
tgt: Proceed forward past the dresser then turn left. Then enter family room and go by the pool table. Proceed past the pool table and enter the small bathroom on your right.  Wait by the sink.

src: walk past medical equipment draining platform through door near wall mirror walk into open room past tile mosaic on floor walk into next room massage beds with metal bowls above
tgt: walk past the medical equipment and draining platform through the door near the wall mirror. Walk into the open room past the tile mosaic on the floor. Walk into the next room that has massage beds with hanging metal bowls above.

src: walk out doorway left left walk straight hallway walk past stairs walk into room on left stop
tgt: Walk out the doorway, farthest to the left. Take a left, and walk straight down the hallway. Walk past the stairs, and walk into the room on the left and stop.

src: exit room door on left right near stairs on left
tgt: Exit the room using the door on the left. Turn right. Stand near the stairs going up on the left.

src: turn head toward front doors right see on right stairs first room once through washroom doorway
tgt: Turn around and head toward the front doors, take a right to the see stairs on your right, head up the stairs and enter the first room, stop once you are through the washroom doorway.

src: exit nook then right cement slab on as forward until on slab number ping pong table on slab left long table with mixture of black white wood grain chairs ahead of slightly left
tgt: Exit the nook, then turn right. Counting the cement slab you're standing on as "one", move forward until you're on slab number "five". There will be a ping pong table on the slab to your left and a long table with a mixture of black, white, and wood grain chairs ahead of your and slightly to your left.

src: stairs top right few steps before
tgt: Go up the stairs and when you get to the top, turn right and walk a few steps before stopping.

src: exit bathroom then right immediately hallway after white lamp on left turn right wait by black door straight ahead
tgt: Exit the bathroom then turn right and immediately turn left to continue down the hallway. After you pass the white lamp on the left turn right and wait by the black door straight ahead.

src: turn right into hallway next hallway right wait in front of exit sign
tgt: Turn right and go into the hallway.  When you get to the next hallway, you could go left or right, you will stop there and wait in front of the exit sign.

src: around table ping pong table wait near desk with brown chairs black chair
tgt: Go around the table and pass the ping pong table. Wait near the desk with the two brown chairs and one black chair.

src: walk out of bathroom walk past couches in front of dining room table
tgt: Walk out of the bathroom. Walk past the couches. Stop in front of the dining room table.

src: right after stairs at first door on right in front of shower doors
tgt: Take a right after the stairs, and turn left at your first door on the right. Stop in front of the shower doors.

src: away from hammock right walk under sign host straight stop between middle columns meeting room right of long wooden table with just plant on
tgt: Walk away from the hammock, turn right, and walk under the sign that says host. Continue straight. Stop between the middle two columns bordering the meeting room to the right of the long wooden table with just a plant on it.

src: slightly left then staircase top
tgt: Go slightly left and then head up the staircase.  When you get to the top, stop.  That's where you will wait.

src: down hallway with art on wall room directly in front of carpet
tgt: Walk down the hallway with the art on the wall.  Enter the room directly in front of you and stop when you reach the carpet.

src: turn stairs in kitchen right past table veer right past bar table then wait there
tgt: Turn around, go up stairs.  You'll be in the kitchen.  Turn right, go past the table.  Veer right and go past the bar table and then stop.  Wait there.

src: bedroom turn through doorway on right walk past piano stand in hallway next paintings
tgt: Leave the bedroom turn left and go through the doorway on the right.  Walk left past the piano. stand in the hallway next to the two paintings.

src: door take left hall left rectangular table at round table
tgt: Go out the door a take a left. Go down the hall. Take another left, pass the rectangular table, and stop at the round table.

src: walk past fireplace dining room in hallway right next right in front of bathroom
tgt: walk past the fireplace and leave the dining room. In the hallway take a right. Take the next right, and stop in front of the bathroom.

src: walk through kitchen past yellow cabinets at door wait by water heater
tgt: Walk through kitchen past yellow cabinets and go left at the door, wait by water heater.

src: exit sauna stairs on left turn steps steps top
tgt: Exit the sauna and go up the stairs on the left. Turn left and continue going up the steps. Wait three steps to the top.

src: down stairs through foyer into living room then wait by chair on right
tgt: Walk down the stairs, through the foyer and into the living room. Then wait by the chair on the right.

src: walk way forward brown door on right right at end of corner there
tgt: Walk all the way forward passing the brown door on your right. Turn right at the end of the corner and stop there.

src: turn room once turn right forward out door on left once turn left walk until fireplace at fireplace turn straight forward right before white table right
tgt: Turn left and exit the room. Once out turn right and walk forward and out the door on the left. Once out turn left and walk until you reach the fireplace.  At the fireplace, turn left and walk straight forward. Stop right before you reach the white table to your right.

src: exit bathroom turn stairs turn wait near bookcase
tgt: Exit the bathroom. Turn left and go down the stairs. Turn left and wait near the bookcase.

src: exit laundry room turn hallway large mirror right into kitchen right again between counters before stove
tgt: Exit laundry room to hallway Turn left and walk down hallway to large mirror. Turn right into kitchen and right again stopping between two counters before stove.

src: exit room then left straight until couches then in hallway ahead
tgt: Exit the room then turn left. Go straight until you pass the couches and then wait in the hallway ahead.

src: walk past kitchen through second door on right inside bathroom next sink
tgt: Walk past the kitchen and through the second door on the right. Wait inside the bathroom next to the sink.

src: straight through opening slightly left move through opening straight
tgt: Go straight through the opening.  Turn slightly to the left.  Move straight through opening.  Go straight to bedroom.

src: walk past piano into entry walk past front door study many bookshelves in front of rug under desk
tgt: Walk past the piano and into the entry. Walk past the front door and enter the study that has many bookshelves. Stop in front of the rug that's under the desk.

src: exit bathroom walk through doorway then right down stairs at landing right stairs at bottom of stairs wait

Following the left side of the room with the white table walk down the length of the kitchen.   Stop in the area in front of the stacked washer and dryer and in front of the bathroom door.

Continue down the hallway staying close to the left hand wall until you can make a sharp left hand turn. There will be a sign straight ahead with a quote from Matthew 18:20. Go right from there into the laundry room.

src: walk through living room wait in foyer near table
tgt: Walk through the living room and wait in the foyer near the table.

src: turn stairs left left down hallway until just inside doorway of bedroom
tgt: Turn around and go up the stairs, take a left and go left, down the hallway until you are just inside the doorway of the bedroom.

src: exit bathroom then right.turn left stairs on left wait there
tgt: Exit the bathroom then turn right.Turn left and go down the stairs on the left. Wait there.

src: leave bathroom table turn into bedroom at bed table next bed
tgt: Leave bathroom, walk to pool table, turn left into bedroom. Stop at bed table next to bed.

src: down hall up stairs in doorway near water
tgt: Walk down the hall and up three stairs, stopping in the doorway near some water.

src: turn stairs at top of stairs stop before into next room
tgt: Turn around and go up the stairs. At the top of the stairs stop before going into the next room.

src: walk past stairs into hallway right down stairs in front of doorway
tgt: Walk past the stairs into the hallway and turn right. Walk down the stairs. Stop in front of the doorway.

src: stairs straight bedroom at top of stairs once bedroom
tgt: Go up the stairs and go straight. Enter the bedroom at the top of the stairs. Stop once you enter the bedroom.

src: from turn right down hall hall up steps next
tgt: From closet turn right down hall, follow hall up steps and stop next to painting.

src: walk left of bed stop at hallway
tgt: Walk to the left of the bed. Stop at the hallway.

src: down hall stop at end of hall
tgt: Walk down the hall and stop at the end of the hall.

src: enter house through door with welcome mat stairs on left with directions of steps turn first set of steps wait by window
tgt: Enter the house through the door with the Welcome mat. Go up the stairs on the left. When faced with two directions of steps, turn left. Go up the first set of steps and wait by the window.

src: outside walk towards pool stop near patio
tgt: Go outside, walk towards the pool and stop near the patio.

src: down steps down hallway right into blue bedroom wait at entrance
tgt: Walk down steps and straight down hallway, turn right into blue walled bedroom. Wait at entrance.

src: turn out of bathroom into room room slight right onto stairs wait here on stairs
tgt: Turn around and go out of the bathroom into the room. Exit the room and take a slight right onto the stairs. Wait here on the stairs.

src: walk through doorway directly in doorway on right side of through in front of table
tgt: Walk through the doorway, walk directly in the doorway on the right side of the one you walked through, stop in front of table.

src: leave bathroom through bedroom then out bedroom door through hallway step into kitchen then
tgt: Leave bathroom, walk through bedroom, then out the bedroom door, through the hallway, take one step into the kitchen, then stop.

src: stairs into hall into first bedroom on right next nightstand with telephone on
tgt: Continue up the stairs and turn left into the hall. Turn into the first bedroom on the right and stop next to the nightstand with a telephone on it.

src: walk inside towards red circle on marble floor straight wait at bottom of staircase
tgt: Walk inside towards the red circle on marble floor.  Continue straight.  Wait at the bottom of staircase.

src: turn right down hall right at stairs on first landing
tgt: Turn right and walk down the hall.  Turn right at the stairs and go down them stopping on the first landing.

src: up stairs wait on balcony directly outside door
tgt: Walk up the stairs and wait on the balcony directly outside the door.

src: walk around bed right doorway right past staircase in front of bathroom
tgt: walk around the bed, take a right. Walk to the doorway, take a right. Walk past the staircase, stop in front of the bathroom.

src: away from bedroom right at white cabinets through doorway past sinks through doorway in front of shower
tgt: walk away from bedroom and turn right at white cabinets, continue straight through doorway, walk past sinks through another doorway and stop in front of shower.

src: walk across bedroom up stairs double doors on right into bathroom in front of toilet on right
tgt: Walk across the bedroom and up the stairs. Enter the double doors on the right and go into the bathroom. Stop in front of the toilet, which is on the right.

src: step then right into cluttered room steps into attic wait there
tgt: Go up the step then turn right and go into the cluttered room. Go up the steps into the attic and wait there.

src: walk inside hard right into kitchen forward wait at stairs
tgt: Walk inside, make a hard right into the kitchen, walk forward, and wait at the stairs.

src: turn stairs paintings turn left then left
tgt: Turn around and ascend the stairs. Pass the paintings and turn left. Then continue to turn left and stop.

src: up stairs turn through doorway right past chair walk between chair sofa towards outside door step outside wait by table chairs outside
tgt: Walk up the stairs.  Turn left and walk through the doorway.  Turn right and walk past the chair.  Walk between the chair and sofa towards the outside door.  Step outside.  Wait by the table and chairs outside.

src: walk into bedroom walk doorway turn left then straight hall veer right by stairs then on first step down basement wait there
tgt: Walk into the bedroom.  Walk to the doorway, and turn left.  Then walk straight down the hall, veer to the right by the stairs and then stop on the first step going down to the basement.  wait there.

src: stairs right next flight of stairs bedroom at bottom of stairs left into bathroom on rug in front of sink
tgt: Go down the stairs. and take a right down the next flight of stairs. Enter the bedroom at the bottom of the stairs. Take a left and go into the bathroom. Stop on the rug in front of the sink.

src: walk through door down hall into bedroom walk doorway stop
tgt: Walk through the door and down the hall into the the bedroom. Walk left to the doorway and stop.

src: hallway on right right in front of marble gold coffee table
tgt: Go down the hallway on the right.  Turn right and stop in front of the marble and gold coffee table.

src: stairs left into kitchen in kitchen right stairs stop at bottom
tgt: Go down the stairs and take a left into the kitchen. In the kitchen take a right and go down the stairs and stop at the bottom.

src: stairs left into fitness room straight ahead once room
tgt: Go up the stairs, and go left, Go into the fitness room straight ahead. Stop once you enter the room.

src: second chandelier turn right third chandelier turn wait by stairs
tgt: When you get to the second chandelier turn right and when you get to the third chandelier turn left. Wait by the stairs.

src: exit vestibule house straight past tablecloth table in front of entrance restroom
tgt: Exit the vestibule and enter the house. Continue straight past the tablecloth draped table and stop in front of the entrance to the restroom.

src: exit bedroom down hall wait by stairs
tgt: Exit the bedroom. Walk down the hall and wait by the stairs.

src: through library pass through large doorway.turn right towards stairs turn right at foot of stairs pass through door into home office wait there
tgt: Go through the library and pass through the large arched doorway.Turn right and move towards the stairs. turn to the right at the foot of the stairs and pass through the door into the home office. Wait there.

src: steps front door into building through first door on right wait by washer dryer in bathroom doorway
tgt: Go up the steps to the front door and into the building. Go through the first door on the right wait by the washer and dryer in the bathroom doorway.

src: exit shower walk through door right of sink turn then again at pool table wait in doorway bedroom
tgt: Exit the shower and walk through the door to the right of the sink. Turn left and then left again at the pool table. Wait in the doorway to the bedroom.

src: down hallway past bathroom turn hallway top of stairs wait at top of stairs
tgt: Walk down the hallway past the bathroom. Turn left and continue down the hallway to the top of the stairs. Wait at the top of the stairs.

src: walk through hallways with spiral trees enter through open doorway immediately bedroom wait at foot of bed
tgt: Walk through the hallways with spiral trees. Enter through the open arched doorway and immediately turn left. Enter the bedroom and wait at the foot of the bed.

src: in large room stairs first stairs wait here
tgt: Go in to the large room and towards the stairs Go up the first two stairs. Wait here.

src: walk through area past table walk into next room walk towards first open door walk through door with painting bedroom walk through bedroom into bathroom with tiled floor
tgt: Walk through the kitchen area past the table. Walk into the next room and walk towards the first open door. Walk through the door with a hanging painting, which leads to a bedroom. Walk through the bedroom and into the bathroom with tiled floor.

src: down hallway past living room on left next light switch on right in living room
tgt: Walk down the hallway and go past the living room on your left. Stop next to the light switch on the right in the living room.

src: turn around out of bathroom in hall turn left hallway next place that right in long hallway with big planter things by wait
tgt: Turn around and walk out of the bathroom.  When you're in the hall turn to the left and walk down that hallway.  When you get to the next place that you can, turn right.  You'll be in a long hallway with big planter things.  Stop by one and wait.

src: turn spiral stairs at borrom continue near counter
tgt: Turn around and descend the spiral stairs. At the borrom continue straight and stop near the counter.

src: down stairs wait near bottom
tgt: Walk down the stairs and wait near the bottom.

src: turn room left side into large open room across room past pool once past pool right in doorway lobby area
tgt: Turn left and exit the room to the left side into the large open room. Go across the room and past the pool. Once past the pool. Turn right and stop in the doorway facing the lobby area.

src: turn exit room straight chair turn beside exercise bike into open door walk through door stop between massage tables
tgt: Turn left and exit room. Walk straight passed the barber chair. Turn left beside the exercise bike into the open door. Walk through the door and stop between the two massage tables.

src: walk towards fireplace right through double doors
tgt: Walk towards the fireplace and turn right. Walk through the double doors.

src: exit area left right right enter bedroom wait by bed
tgt: Exit washing area, make a left, make a right, make a right and enter bedroom, wait by bed.

src: stairs top
tgt: Go up the stairs and stop when you reach the top.

src: exit closet toward room room door on right turn right into bathroom wait near first sink
tgt: Exit the closet toward the room. Exit the room using the door on the right. Turn left. Turn right into the bathroom. Wait near the first sink.

src: walk end of corridor wait in kitchen
tgt: Walk to the end of the corridor and wait in the kitchen.

src: turn left pool into first room on left with bed
tgt: Turn around and go left passed the pool. Go into the first room on the left with a bed.

src: straight stairs on left then as soon as tv on left slightly right near white bookshelf
tgt: Go straight and pass the stairs on your left. Then as soon as you pass the TV on your left turn slightly right and stand near the white bookshelf.

src: walk yellow kitchen area through door just of counters once inside in front of white tank
tgt: Walk to the yellow kitchen area and go through the door just left of the counters.  Stop once you step inside in front of the white tank.

src: steps then wait there
tgt: Go up the steps then turn left. Wait there.

src: exit bathroom area turn left in doorway near bottom of stairs
tgt: Exit the bathroom area and turn left and stop in the doorway, near the bottom of the stairs.

src: in front of family picture turn walk straight through bathroom past tub mirrors through doorway door bathroom on right door closet left
tgt: Standing in front of the family picture, turn left and walk straight through the bathroom past the tub and mirrors.  Go through the doorway and stop when the door to the bathroom is on your right and the door to the closet is to your left.

src: down hallway right into room at end of hallway in front of rug
tgt: Walk down the hallway and turn right. Walk into the room at the end of the hallway and stop in front of the rug.

src: walk end of bed bedroom door on left through door turn forward stairs on other side of potted plant
tgt: Walk to the end of the bed and to the bedroom door on the left. Walk through the door and turn left. Walk forward to the stairs and railing on the other side of a potted plant.

src: exit bedroom right hallway right down stairs turn down stairs on next landing
tgt: exit bedroom and turn right walk down hallway, turn right and walk down the stairs, turn left and walk down those stairs, stop on the next landing.

src: through gate inside open door on first entrance on right down hallway until bathroom turn then right in doorway of bedroom
tgt: To through the gate and left inside the open door, continue on to the first entrance on the right, down the hallway until you see a bathroom turn left, then turn to the right and stop in the doorway of the bedroom.

src: start with elevators back turn open door in right corner of room walk through doorway directly across hallway into room with white lounge beds few steps into room on tile few feet from first lounge bed
tgt: Start with the elevators to your back, turn left and walk to the open door in the right corner of the room.  Walk through the doorway and directly across the hallway leading into a room with two white lounge beds.  Take a few steps into the room and stop on the tile.  You should be a few feet from the first lounge bed.

src: turn around up stairs right right at fireplace wait on third step on stairs
tgt: Turn around and walk up the stairs and take a right. Take another right at the fireplace and wait on the third step on the stairs.

src: bathroom down hallway past chairs turn after second chair in doorway of bedroom
tgt: Leave the bathroom and walk down the hallway past the two chairs.  Turn left after passing the second chair and stop in the doorway of the bedroom.

src: into hallway turn head past table chairs couch down doorway into purple room stop outside bathroom
tgt: Go into the hallway and turn left.  Head past the table, chairs, and couch down to the doorway.  Go into the purple room and stop; outside the bathroom.

src: exit bedroom left down hall first doorway on left in empty room with brown carpet in doorway
tgt: Exit the bedroom, and make a left.  Walk down the hall and take the first doorway on your left.  You will be in an empty room with brown carpet.  Stop in that doorway.

src: room right straight through door across room left at end of screen wait between screen wicker chair
tgt: Leave the room and take a right. Go straight through the door across the room. Make a left at the  end of the screen and wait between the screen and wicker chair.

src: head down hallway past brown chairs wait in middle of hallway in front of entryway room
tgt: Head straight down hallway past two brown chairs. Wait in middle of hallway in front of entryway to blue room.

src: stairs right straight through doorway in doorway of bathroom
tgt: Continue up the stairs and turn right. Continue straight through the doorway. Stop in the doorway of the bathroom.

src: exit bedrooms.go down hallway turn top of stairs
tgt: Exit bedrooms.Go straight down hallway. Turn left and stop and the top of the stairs.

src: turn then right into laundry room wait near sink
tgt: Turn left and then turn right. Go into the laundry room and wait near the sink.

src: exit bathroom through door right stairs ahead of left at top of stairs
tgt: Exit the bathroom and go through the door opening to your right. Climb the stairs that are ahead of you and to the left. Stop at the top of the stairs.

src: walk through living room past small dining table wait near giraffe print bench seat
tgt: Walk straight through the living room and past the small dining table. Wait near the giraffe print bench seat.

src: stand in kitchen entrance
tgt: Go stand in the kitchen entrance.

src: walk out of bedroom hallway past stairs bathroom in second bathrooms doorway on right
tgt: Walk out of the bedroom. go down the hallway past the stairs and bathroom. Stop in the second bathrooms doorway on your right.

src: through double doors turn through archway through door bedroom
tgt: Go through the double doors. Turn left and go through the archway and through the door to the bedroom.

src: walk past fireplace on right past bathroom on right right opposite drip painting bedroom open door right of thermostat on wall walk past white ottoman left wait on roof deck
tgt: Walk past the fireplace on the right. Walk past the bathroom on the right. Make a right opposite the drip painting. Exit the bedroom. Enter the open door to the right of the thermostat on the wall. Walk past the white ottoman to the left. Wait on the roof deck.

src: up stairs porch living room wait at doorway kitchen
tgt: Walk up the stairs, cross the porch, enter the living room, wait at the doorway to the kitchen.

src: walk slightly right past silver metal chair through doorway straight walk between hot tub lounge chairs forward with pool right past table on left wait near lounge chairs
tgt: Walk slightly to the right, past the silver metal chair. Go through the doorway and continue straight. Walk between the hot tub and the lounge chairs, walk forward with the pool to your right. Walk past the table on the left and wait near the two lounge chairs.

src: down front near flat screen then around couches door in back
tgt: Walk down to the front near the flat screen.  Then  walk around the couches to the door in the back.

src: magazine rack plant lamp pencils tubes
tgt: Go to the magazine rack. Go to the plant. Go to the standing lamp. Go to the pencils. Go to the tubes.

src: walk out of bedroom under wine bottle decoration past bathroom left into first room fish on wall above bed
tgt: Walk out of the bedroom under the wine bottle decoration. Go past the bathroom and take a left into the first room which has two fish handing on the wall above the bed.

src: pass through hallway toward outside door right in doorway
tgt: pass through hallway, walk toward outside door, turn right, stop in doorway.

src: turn right stairs at bottom of stairs patio right there pool in front of there
tgt: Turn to the right and go down the stairs.  At the bottom of the stairs turn left and proceed out to the patio.  Stop right there, you will see the pool in front of you.  Wait there.

src: step forward toward sink then right into lounge area.walk around pillar right outside onto balcony forward by pool
tgt: Step forward toward the sink, then turn right and walk into the lounge area.Walk around the pillar to your right. Continue outside onto the balcony. Walk forward and wait by the pool.

src: into hallway turn hallway right straight right into room wait at entrance
tgt: Go into the hallway. Turn left and go down the hallway. Turn right and go straight. Turn right and go into the room. Wait at the entrance.

src: towards christmas tree way up stairs wait
tgt: Go towards the Christmas tree and walk all the way up the stairs, and wait.

src: walk toward refrigerator right out of kitchen past dining room table on first step of stairs
tgt: Walk toward the refrigerator and turn right. Walk out of the kitchen and past the dining room table. Stop on the first step of the stairs.

src: with wall left walkway stop at door inside
tgt: With the curving wall to your left, continue down the walkway and stop at the door leading inside.

src: stairs then white vase with white flowers turn on wooden door wait by sink
tgt: Go down the stairs then pass the white vase with the white flowers and turn left on the wooden door and wait by the sink.

src: down hall into open room with stairs walk over glass part of floor through doorway straight ahead into room on right just inside doorway
tgt: Walk down the hall and into the open room with the stairs. Walk over the glass part of the floor and through the doorway straight ahead. Turn into tho the room on the right and stop just inside the doorway.

src: out of bedroom into hallway left hall stair right stairs second landing on second landing before next floor
tgt: Go out of the bedroom into the hallway, and take a left.  Go down the hall to the stair and take a right to go down to the stairs to the second landing. Stop on the second landing before you reach the next floor.

src: exit turn then tub turn again wait near bathroom sink
tgt: Exit the shower turn left and then when you get to the tub turn left again. Wait near the bathroom sink.

src: leave enter bedroom right around bed slider through slider
tgt: leave closet enter bedroom, turn right and go around the bed to the slider. go through slider to balcony and stop.

src: turn until gray rug on floor walk forwards over rug in front of couch through open door outside right walk in front of long gray couches on porch right edge of second gray couch enter into large living room area behind white chairs in front of statue like man
tgt: Turn around until facing the gray rug on the floor. Walk forwards over the rug in front of the couch. Go through the open door to the outside. Turn right and walk in front of the long gray couches on the porch. Take a right when you get to the edge of the second gray couch and enter into the  large living room area and stop behind the two white chairs, in front of the statue that looks like a man.

src: exit room right into third door on right straight into door in middle wait therfe
tgt: Exit the room. Turn right and go into the third door on the right. Go straight into the door in the middle and wait therfe.

src: between poles between tables white couch in corner of room coffee table in front of white couch
tgt: Go between two poles and between all the surrounding tables. There is a white couch in the corner of the room. Go to the coffee table in front of the white couch.

src: stairs turn wait in front of bedroom door
tgt: Go down the stairs and turn left. Wait in front of the bedroom door.

src: after pool turn right down toward statues wait near patio table chairs
tgt: After you pass the pool turn right and walk down toward the statues. Wait near the patio table and chairs.

src: finish stairs at floor then right into room turn head toward stairs on left steps then
tgt: Finish going up the stairs and stop at that floor then turn right and go into that room. Turn left and head toward the stairs on the left. Go up two steps then stop.

src: head then right towards stairwell at bottom
tgt: Head straight then right towards the stairwell and go down. Stop at the bottom.

src: exit bedroom slight left main hall slight right walk of hall into doorway other hall right forward room with loungers stop
tgt: exit bedroom turning slight left to enter main hall, turn slight right and walk to edge of hall into doorway to other hall turn right and walk forward room with loungers and stop.

src: walk towards round table with chairs in front of bookcase ladder on left
tgt: Walk towards the round table with the two chairs and stop in front of the bookcase ladder on the left.

src: walk out of bedroom walk hall right past brick wall walk into second doorway from left stop
tgt: Walk out of the bedroom and walk left down the hall. Walk right past the brick wall. Walk into the second doorway from the left and stop.

src: walk through doorway between wood tables past bar left at cigar case down hallway in middle of black bench
tgt: walk through the doorway between the wood tables, continue past the bar and towards the left at the cigar case. Walk down the hallway and stop in the middle of the black bench.

src: straight hallway until door on end wait there
tgt: Go straight down the hallway until you get to the door on the end. Wait there.

src: exit bedroom left left in front of potted plant past bed on right wait at threshold of bathroom door
tgt: Exit the bedroom. Make a left. Make a left in front of the potted plant. Walk past the bed on the right. Wait at the threshold of the bathroom door.

src: walk into massage room head left through doorway into next room staircase little farther stand by base of stairs
tgt: Walk into the massage room and head to the left.  Go through the doorway.  Go into the next room where there is a staircase.  Keep going a little farther and stand by the base of the stairs.

src: turn turn through door until next room then
tgt: Turn around and turn left through the door. Continue until the next room and then stop.

src: walk right past metal bench right through door walk into hallway across way right then in front of stairs in doorway bedroom
tgt: Walk right past the metal bench. Turn right and walk through the door. Walk into the hallway across the way. Turn right and then turn left in front of the stairs. Stop in the doorway to the bedroom.

src: exit then u turn into room room second door on right steps book case wait near plant in brown pot
tgt: Exit the shower then turn u turn left and go into the room. Exit the room using the second door on the right and go up the steps. Pass the book case and wait near the plant in the brown pot.

src: exit room by leftmost entrance wait on edge of carpet by painting
tgt: Exit the the room by the leftmost entrance. Wait on the edge of the carpet by the painting.

src: head inside through left doorway right near stairs
tgt: Head inside through the left doorway, turn right, wait near the stairs.

src: walk past glass table right stairs wait at top of stairs
tgt: Walk past the glass table and turn right. Go up the stairs and wait at the top of the stairs.

src: turn around down hallway then across corridor left next hallway bedroom left wait by bed
tgt: Turn around and walk down the hallway.  Then walk across the corridor and to your left continue down the next hallway and enter the bedroom to your left and wait by the bed.

src: walk through doorway towards small black carpet turn right again up staircase on top step
tgt: walk through doorway towards small black carpet, turn left and right again to walk up staircase, stop on the top step.

src: through brown double doors third door on left into doorway then
tgt: Go through the brown double doors, go to the third door on your left and go into that doorway then stop.

src: turn around past easel with sign on up second step
tgt: Turn around and walk past the easel with the sign on it. Walk up to the second step.

src: turn right room walk past stairs turn hall turn at doorway just past statuette on right on corner of black white rug
tgt: Turn right to leave room. Walk past the stairs. Turn left down the hall. Turn at the doorway just past the statuette on the right. Stop on the closest corner of the black and white rug.

src: bathroom through door on right down room until beginning of stairs stairs on third step from top
tgt: Leave the bathroom and go through the door on the right.  Walk down the room until you get to the beginning of the stairs.  Go down the stairs and stop on the third step from the top.

src: turn desk toward door room turn outside room down hall living room turn living room walk past kitchen island next table
tgt: Turn left to face desk. Walk toward door to leave the room. Turn left outside room. Walk down hall to living room. Turn left to enter living room. Walk past kitchen island. Stop next to round table.

src: pass small closet long hallway at end of hallway after bathroom
tgt: Pass a small closet down a long hallway, and stop at the end of the hallway after you pass a bathroom.

src: walk out of room with piano into living room wait just outside doorway behind couch
tgt: Walk out of the room with the piano and into the living room. Wait just outside the doorway and behind the couch.

src: turn staircase at top
tgt: Turn around and go up the staircase. Stop at the top.

src: walk through kitchen right into next building walk through doors on right past chair just inside hallway
tgt: Walk through the kitchen and to the right into the next building. Walk through the doors on the right and past the chair. Stop just inside the hallway.

src: down flights of stairs stop at third step from bottom
tgt: Walk down the three flights of stairs, stop at the third step from the bottom.

src: walk through door right of double door through doorway stop
tgt: Walk through door to the right of the double door closest, walk through doorway and stop.

src: with pool right forward slightly left steps at base of spiral staircase
tgt: With the pool to your right, start walking forward and slightly to the left, climbing three steps, and arriving at the base of the spiral staircase.

src: turn around right of grey couch wait at top of stairs ahead
tgt: Turn around and walk to the right of the grey couch. Wait at the top of the stairs ahead.

src: walk forward towards patio with love seat on left around love seat from rear into hallway with plant on right walk into hallway through doorway in hall left into empty bedroom in bedroom stop just inside doorway
tgt: walk forward towards the patio with the love seat on your left. walk around the love seat from the rear and into the hallway. with the plant on your right walk into the hallway through the doorway. In the hall take a left, and another left into the empty bedroom. In the bedroom stop just inside the doorway.

src: down hall past rug on floor next spot right wait
tgt: Walk down the hall, past the rug that's on the floor.  When you get to the next spot where you could turn left and right, you need to stop there and wait.

src: into room with big blue rug foot of bed through open door foot of bed intersection of hallways stop
tgt: Go into the room with the big blue rug. Go to the foot of the bed. Go through the open door nearest the foot of the bed. Go to the intersection of hallways and stop.

src: inside kitchen into second door from left wait there
tgt: Go inside. Pass the kitchen and go into the second door from the left. Wait there.

src: walk out of bathroom into hallway into hall pool left in hall right outside onto patio once doors
tgt: Walk out of the bathroom and into the hallway crossing into the hall overlooking the pool and take a left in the hall and a right outside onto the patio stopping once you pass the doors.

src: head towards bathroom right at top of stairs turn few stairs hallway wait in front of last framed picture on wall right
tgt: Head towards bathroom and turn right at the top of the stairs. Turn left to go up a few stairs and head down a hallway. Wait in front of last framed picture on the wall to your right.

src: walk through door in front of pool slight left steps at end of room up steps wait at top
tgt: Walk through the door in front of the pool and make a slight left to get to the steps at the end of the room. Walk up the steps and wait at the top.

src: start on top of bottom set of stairs not top of stairs head down room with open door in front of white cabinets room
tgt: Start on the top of the bottom set of stairs, not the top of the stairs, head straight down and towards the room with open door in front of you and the white cabinets, stop when you enter this room.

src: hard left walk towards area towards door right across room past carpet walk through doorway right of mirror wait by chairs
tgt: Turn hard left and walk towards the kitchen area. Go towards the door to the right. Walk across the room past he carpet. Walk through the doorway right of the mirror and wait by the chairs.

src: turn hall way then right hallway first door on right wait by door
tgt: Turn around and go down the hall way, then turn right.   Proceed down the hallway and enter the first door on your right. Wait by the door.

src: walk toward fireplace pass then straight into room on left side wait near table chairs
tgt: Walk toward the fireplace. pass it and then go straight into the room on the left side. Wait near the table and chairs.

src: walk past oval table straight into bedroom with long brown grey rug wait here
tgt: Walk past the oval table, straight into the bedroom with the long striped brown and grey rug.  Wait here.

src: bedroom through arched doorway walk through hallway into open area in front of balcony ahead
tgt: Leave the bedroom through the arched doorway. Walk through the hallway and into the open area. Stop in front of the balcony straight ahead.

src: walk up stairs right stairs at top of stairs
tgt: Go down the walk and up the stairs , turn right and go up the stairs. Stop at the top of the stairs.

src: exit closet right through doorway then into hallway immediate left living room wait on rug by console table
tgt: Exit the closet, turn right and walk through the doorway. Then turn left into the hallway and an immediate left to enter the living room. Wait on the rug by the console table.

src: turn around towards white chair on left left chair second set of stairs on left up wait on first step
tgt: Turn around and walk towards the white chair on the left. Take a left when you reach the chair When you reach the second set of stairs on the left that go up, wait on the first step.

src: down hall few steps wait on stairs
tgt: Walk down the hall. Go down a few steps and wait on the stairs.

src: straight ahead towards swimming pool
tgt: Go straight ahead towards the swimming pool.

src: walk through kitchen dining room table walk through doorway walk left wait in bedroom doorway
tgt: Walk through the kitchen and towards the dining room table. Walk through the doorway and walk left. Wait in the bedroom doorway.

src: with massage table on right walk forward away from room into room with pool left along side pool past lounge chairs right into bar walking straight at bottom of stairs
tgt: With the massage table on your right walk forward away from the room and into the room with the pool taking a left and walking along side the pool past the two lounge chairs and take a right into the bar walking straight and stopping at the bottom of the stairs.

src: walk past big number turn right through doorway just past steps turn into bathroom just outside toilet room door
