src: walk ahead sink faucet on left way end in front of round table chairs
tgt: Walk straight ahead passing the sink faucet on the left all the way to its end. Stop in front of the round table and six chairs.

src: turn around through tables chairs center of room in center of wide open space long table with white table cloth other tables chairs on other side of room
tgt: Turn around and walk through the tables and chairs to the center of the room. Stop in the center of the wide open space facing the long table with the white table cloth and the other tables and chairs on the other side of the room.

src: exit bathroom walk through bedroom right turn first door at left inside room with starfish seashell decorations
tgt: Exit the bathroom.  Walk through the bedroom and take a right turn.  Enter the first door at your left and stop inside the room with the starfish and seashell decorations.

src: exit room then locker room into neighboring room right through doorway next mirror on wall next tissue box on shelf
tgt: Exit the shower room, then exit the locker room. Go into the neighboring room to the right, through the doorway next to the mirror on the wall. Stop next to the tissue box on the shelf.

src: head out door right around banisters once ahead of
tgt: Head out the door.  Take a right. Go around the banisters and stop once ahead of them.

src: walk past fireplace through doorway left of lounger chair past table on left in doorway on right next door
tgt: walk past the fireplace, to through the doorway to the left of the lounger chair, walk past the table on the left and stop in the doorway on the right next to the door to outside.

src: walk towards white bookshelf turn at white bookshelf in between tables
tgt: Walk towards the white bookshelf. Turn left at the white bookshelf. Stop in between the two tables.

src: main entrance by staircase left into living room with mirror
tgt: Go to the main entrance by the staircase and take a left. Go into the living room with the mirror.

src: exit bedroom through kitchen turn red chair turn bathroom wait at sink
tgt: Exit the bedroom, walk through the kitchen, turn left, walk to the red chair, turn left, enter the bathroom, wait at the sink.

src: exit room right into main room slight right up steps between bathtubs
tgt: exit room slight right into main room. Turn slight right up 2 steps. Stop between 2 bathtubs.

src: flight of stairs left turn again at statue into room on right on right corner of rug near fireplace
tgt: Go up one flight of stairs and take a left. Turn left again at the statue and go into the room on the right.  Stand on the right corner of the rug near the fireplace.

src: turn right towards sofas hard right doorway area third door counting from left wait at entrance of movie entertainment area
tgt: Turn right and walk towards the sofas. Turn hard right facing the 4 doorway area and enter the third door counting from the left. Wait at the entrance of the movie entertainment area.

src: walk toward steps climb steps at top of steps right room ahead wait here
tgt: Walk toward steps.  Climb steps.  At the top of steps turn right, and enter the room ahead.  Wait here.

src: turn around television table chairs outside wait on patio
tgt: Turn around and walk passed the television and table and chairs. Walk outside wait on the patio.

src: exit men locker room through doors on left turn in hallway through double doors
tgt: Exit the men's locker room and go through the doors on the left. Turn left and stop in the hallway through the double doors.

src: walk into bedroom around bed walk past bathroom in doorway
tgt: Walk into the bedroom and around the bed. Walk past the bathroom and stop in the doorway.

src: walk through living room area into sun room area with round table chairs walk past book shelf room past floor rugs open doors walk into kitchen area near refrigerator
tgt: Walk through the living room area and into the sun room area with round dining table and chairs. Walk past the book shelf. Continue down the room past the floor rugs and open doors. Walk into the kitchen area and stop near the refrigerator.

src: from bottom on stairs forward right until hallway right hallway until fireplace on right then in front of fireplace
tgt: From the bottom on the stairs, continue forward and towards the right, until you reach a hallway extending to the right. Continue down this hallway until you see a fireplace on the right and then stop in front of the fireplace.

src: down steps into bathroom on left next toilet
tgt: Walk down the three steps and into the bathroom on the left. Stop next to the toilet.

src: opposite outside area into living room through up stairs turn doorway stop
tgt: Go opposite the outside area into the living room and straight through, up the stairs, turn left towards the doorway and stop.

src: walk past refrigerator right in bedroom across hall
tgt: Walk past the refrigerator and to the right. Stop in the bedroom across the hall.

src: walk into hallway right walk hall right just inside bedroom
tgt: Walk into the hallway and to the right. Walk left down the hall and turn right. Stop just inside the bedroom.

src: past kitchen white chairs wait by white chair
tgt: Go past the kitchen and you will see six white chairs. Wait by the farthest white chair.

src: turn room though doorway left across hallway up steps bathroom
tgt: Turn around and exit the room though the doorway to the left. Walk across the hallway, up some steps and enter the bathroom.

src: exit half bath then hallway forward until right through double doors right
tgt: Exit the half bath, then turn left down the hallway. Continue forward until you can turn right through the double doors to your right.

src: exit bathroom past fireplace through door wait inside bathroom
tgt: Exit the bathroom, walk past the fireplace and through the door. Wait inside the bathroom.

src: walk out of room right down hall turn at end of hall forward right
tgt: Walk out of the room and turn right. Walk down the hall and turn left at the end of the hall. Walk forward and turn right and stop.

src: stand so bookshelves behind sitting room via door on opposite wall into dining area walk right of dining table front door just before through door with hat rack on left
tgt: Stand so the bookshelves are behind you.  Exit the sitting room via the door on the opposite wall that leads into a dining area.  Walk to the right of the dining table and towards the front door.  Stop just before passing through this door with the hat rack on your left.

src: exit laundry room turn left through doorway directly ahead into bedroom past bed archway on right through archway in front of toilet
tgt: Exit the laundry room and turn left. Go through the doorway directly ahead into the bedroom. Go past the bed to the archway on the right. Pass through the archway and stop in front of the toilet .

src: after bedroom bedroom at end of hall into room wait at foot of bed
tgt: After you leave the bedroom you should go the bedroom at the end of the hall. When you go into the room wait at the foot of the bed.

src: walk past pool indoors right walk past couch in doorway in front of mirror
tgt: Walk past the pool and go indoors. Take a right, and walk past the couch and stop in the doorway in front of the mirror.

src: orient parallel grain on wooden floor such that doorway directly ahead of bathroom ahead right double doorway ahead left though double doorway ahead of left once room behind couch straight with glass doors left once kitchen area
tgt: Orient yourself to be parallel to the grain on the wooden floor and such that you see a doorway directly ahead of you, a bathroom ahead and to the right, and a double doorway ahead and to the left. Go though the double doorway ahead of you and to the left. Once you enter the room, go left behind the couch and continue straight with the sliding glass doors to your left. Stop once you reach the kitchen area.

src: down walkway second door on right inside bedroom by chair
tgt: Walk down the walkway and enter the second door on the right. Wait inside the bedroom by the chair.

src: up stairs wait at middle of last set of stairs
tgt: Walk up the stairs and wait at the middle of the last set of stairs.

src: stairs once level stand at bottom of stairs
tgt: Go down the stairs. Stop once you reach the level and stand at the bottom of the stairs.

src: stairs right fireplace on left beside flag pole
tgt: Go up the stairs. Take a right, and pass the fireplace on the left. Stop beside the flag one the pole.

src: hall next pulp fiction poster
tgt: Go down the hall. Stop next to the Pulp Fiction poster.

src: stairs left into bedroom at end of hall in doorway bathroom on right of bed
tgt: Go up the stairs and take a left. Walk into the bedroom at the end of the hall. Stop in the doorway to the bathroom on the right of the bed.

src: turn house then right kitchen area
tgt: Turn left and enter the house. Then turn right and enter the kitchen area.

src: straight coffee table doorway piano stop in entryway near couch
tgt: Go straight passed the coffee table and enter the doorway. Go passed the piano and stop in the entryway near the couch.

src: around stairs down stairs bottom right door on right outside in doorway
tgt: You should walk around to the stairs and walk down the stairs. When you get to the bottom make a right and go to the door on the right that leads outside. You need to wait in that doorway.

src: walk past pool on right left steps through gate wait near pots with plants
tgt: Walk past the pool on the right. Turn left and go up the steps. Go through the gate and wait near the two pots with plants.

src: exit bedroom laundry room on right there
tgt: Exit the bedroom and enter the laundry room on the right. Wait there.

src: down hall stairwell walk into bedroom ahead bed with white comforter blue floor rug underneath
tgt: Walk down the hall passing the stairwell. Walk into the bedroom ahead that has a bed with white comforter and blue floor rug underneath.

src: down hall into bedroom right past chest of drawers right in bathroom doorway
tgt: Walk down the hall and into the bedroom. Turn right and walk past the chest of drawers. Turn right and stop in the bathroom doorway.

src: walk past piano through middle entryway right in front of double doors stop
tgt: Walk past the piano and through the middle entryway. Turn right and stop in front of the double doors and stop.

src: through door into hall red carpet doorway with striped chair mirror on side stop
tgt: Go through the door into a hall down a red carpet.  When you get to another doorway with a striped chair and mirror on either side, stop.

src: turn hallway right through first door turn in first doorway
tgt: Turn around, go down the hallway, and turn right to go through the first door. Turn left and stop in the first doorway.

src: at bottom of stairs forward toward black door right toward pool wait by pillars
tgt: At the bottom of the stairs, go forward toward the black door. Turn right and go toward the pool. Wait by the pillars.

src: turn left past rope room right of fireplace once in next room turn walk end of rope right walk at top of stairs
tgt: Turn to your left and go past the rope to exit the room to the right of the fireplace. Once in the next room turn left. Walk to the end of the rope and turn right. Walk and stop at the top of the stairs facing down them.

src: into kitchen through doorway on left inside dining room
tgt: Go into the kitchen and through the doorway on the left. Wait inside the dining room.

src: walk past ottoman on right bedroom right past portraits on wall left bedroom ahead wait near chair
tgt: Walk past the ottoman on the right. Exit the bedroom, and make a right. Walk past the five portraits on the wall to the left. Enter the bedroom straight ahead, and wait near the chair.

src: turn around straight path towards pool turn at next walkway door inside
tgt: Turn around and walk straight down the path towards the pool. Turn left at the next walkway and stop facing the door to go inside.

src: doorway on far right hall right through open door on immediate right closet through doorway stop
tgt: To the doorway on the far right and head down the hall,  take a right and go through the open door, on your immediate right is a closet, go through the doorway and stop.

src: storage closet u-turn left through doorway wait on landing
tgt: Leave the storage closet and make a u-turn to the left.  Go through the doorway and wait on the landing.

src: walk past table desktop computer exit room through white double doors right past framed newspaper articles turn through doorway on left wait
tgt: Walk past the table and desktop computer. Exit room through the white double doors and turn right. Walk past the framed newspaper articles. Turn through the doorway on the left and wait.

src: walk into living room walk past couches right in doorway
tgt: Walk into the living room. Walk past the couches and turn right. Stop in the doorway.

src: walk through door continue straight through next door in room
tgt: Walk straight through the door and continue straight through the next door, stopping in the room.

src: turn until stairs on sides table in front of forward slightly left of table on left side wall open door against wall with art on though door into room many cabinets with dishes
tgt: TURN LEFT UNTIL THERE ARE STAIRS ON BOTH SIDES AND A TABLE IN FRONT OF YOU, WALK FORWARD AND SLIGHTLY TO THE LEFT OF THE TABLE, ON THE LEFT SIDE WALL IS AN OPEN DOOR AGAINST A WALL WITH ART ON IT, WALK THOUGH THE DOOR AND INTO A ROOM THAT HAS MANY CABINETS FILLED WITH DISHES.

src: away from bed through doorway turn right towards banister turn top of stairs down stairs away from bottom
tgt: walk away from the bed through the doorway turn right and walk towards the banister, turn left and walk to the top of the stairs, walk down the stairs but stop when you are four away from the bottom.

src: turn right room turn then right toward stairs wait at top of stairs
tgt: Turn right and exit the room. Turn left and then turn right and walk toward the stairs. Wait at the top of the stairs.

src: exit stairwell right hard right hallway bedroom wait
tgt: Exit the stairwell to your right.  Take a hard right down the hallway enter the bedroom and wait.

src: leave massage room right enter washroom at massage table
tgt: Leave massage room to lobby, turn right and enter washroom, stop at massage table.

src: turn in front of dining room table turn up stairs turn up stairs at top of stairs
tgt: Turn left in front of the dining room table. Turn left and walk up the stairs. Turn left and walk up the stairs. Stop at the top of the stairs.

src: walk past pool wait in corner next door
tgt: Walk past the pool and wait in the corner next to the door.

src: exit bathroom slight left through lobby stop at display case next bathroom
tgt: Exit the bathroom and make a slight left.  Walk through the lobby and stop at the display case next to the bathroom.

src: past table/chairs couches room though double doors then stairs until window on right with vase red flowers
tgt: Go past the table/chairs and the couches and exit the room though the double doors then turn left and go down stairs until you get to the window on the right with the vase and red flowers.

src: exit bathroom right down end of hall then dining room right through dining room exit out patio doors wait there
tgt: Exit the bathroom.  Turn right and walk down to the end of the hall.  Then turn left and enter the dining room. Turn right, walk through the dining room and exit out the patio doors. Wait there.

src: enter bedroom from outside across bedroom door on right wall first doorway on right bathroom wait just inside doorway bathroom
tgt: Enter the bedroom from outside and go across the bedroom to the door on the right wall. Enter the first doorway on the right and enter the bathroom. Wait just inside the doorway to the bathroom.

src: walk through entryway into hallway straight ahead bedroom through door on left in doorway
tgt: Walk through the entryway, and go into the hallway straight ahead. Enter the bedroom through the door on the left. Stop in the doorway.

src: door right hallway past first door on right right into hallway behind first big brown leather chair
tgt: Facing the door take a right and go down the hallway going past the first door on your right and take a right into the hallway stopping behind the first big brown leather chair.

src: turn hall then right stairs at painting
tgt: Turn left and walk to the hall. Then turn right and head down the stairs. Stop at the painting.

src: walk out door towards bed left turn out door slight right turn down first flight of stairs
tgt: Walk out the door towards the bed. Make a left turn and walk out the door. Make a slight right turn and walk down the first flight of stairs.

src: straight until exit sign then right into room turn balcony wait there
tgt: Go straight until you get to an exit sign then turn right and go into the room. Turn left and go out the balcony. Wait there.

src: walk left of bed into bathroom in doorway
tgt: Walk to the left of the bed into the bathroom. Stop in the doorway.

src: down stairs wait at bottom of stairway next light switch
tgt: Walk down the stairs and wait at the bottom of the stairway next to the light switch.

src: turn at bottom of stairs head through archway right first set of stairs wait at bottom near cream chair
tgt: Turn left at the bottom of the stairs. Head through the archway and turn right. Go down the first set of stairs. Wait at the bottom near the cream chair.

src: walk through kitchen turn at large gray sofa
tgt: Walk through the kitchen. turn left, and stop at the large gray sofa.

src: into room with crowd control ropes walk top of staircase
tgt: Go left to go into the room with crowd control ropes. Walk to the top of the staircase.

src: walk out of room right into great open area stairs landing at top of landing
tgt: Walk out of the room and take a right into the great, open area. Go down the stairs to the landing. Stop at the top of the landing.

src: walk across kitchen right past refrigerator forward door on right walk into restroom
tgt: Walk across the kitchen and turn right past the refrigerator. Go forward, enter  the door on your right, and walk into the restroom.

src: stairs after first set of stairs second at step fourth from top
tgt: Go up the stairs after going up the first set of stairs go up the second and stop at the step fourth from the top.

src: walk past stairs into kitchen forward past sink stove wait just inside formal dining room
tgt: Walk past the stairs and into the kitchen. Continue forward past the sink and stove. Wait just inside the formal dining room.

src: bathroom walk into main room house through door on left on rug at door on outside
tgt: Leave the bathroom and walk into the main room. Leave the house through the door on the left. Stop on the rug at the door on the outside.

src: exit room walk towards plant on ground once plant right walk top of stairs turn into first room wait here
tgt: Exit the room and walk towards potted plant on the ground.  Once you reach the plant, turn right, and walk to the top of stairs.  Turn left into the first room, wait here.

src: exit living dinning table right door stop at bar area door
tgt: Exit living, pass the dinning table and make a right door, stop at bar area door.

src: turn hallway just doorway at end of hall
tgt: Turn around and turn left down the hallway. Go just passed the doorway at the end of the hall.

src: exit room left through black archway left near sink
tgt: Exit the room, make a left and go through the black archway, take a left and stop near the sink.

src: turn right up stairs way top at top hallway at end right bedroom
tgt: Turn right and walk up the stairs all the way to the top. At the top, turn left and enter the hallway. At the end, turn right and stop when you enter the bedroom.

src: turn through door next door ahead of before door glass table on left statue of horse on right straight door once door
tgt: Turn left, walk through the door, keep going walking to the next door ahead of you and before you get to the door you will  pass a glass table on your left and a statue of a horse on your right, keep going straight to the door and stop once you pass the door.

src: turn left hallway towards bedroom through archway in front of bedroom door
tgt: Turn to the left and go down the hallway towards the bedroom. Go through the archway.  Stop in front of the bedroom door.

src: up stairs turn big statue wooden chair up next set of stairs there
tgt: Walk up the stairs and turn left passing the big statue and the wooden chair. Walk up the next set of stairs and stop there.

src: walk past fireplace out of room walk under chandelier stop
tgt: Walk past the fireplace and out of the room. Walk under the chandelier and stop.

src: exit bathroom into bedroom bedroom door on right stairs wait at bottom of stiars
tgt: Exit the bathroom and go into the bedroom. Exit the bedroom to the door on the right. Go down the stairs. Wait at the bottom of the stiars.

src: hallway in direction of plants after first plant turn room between green couch brown chairs step into doorway outside area stop
tgt: Go down the hallway in the direction of the plants, after the first plant turn left, cross the room between the green couch and the brown chairs, step into the doorway to the outside area and stop.

src: room room with mosaic on floor door of first room on left in doorway
tgt: Leave the room and enter the bigger room with the mosaic on the floor.  Go to the door of the first room on the left and stop in the doorway.

src: walk outside door right way forward towards end room on left enter inside room near staircase
tgt: Walk outside the door, and turn right. Walk all the way forward towards the end room on your left. Enter inside the room, and stop near the staircase.

src: walk forward between office desks until white sofa wait at top of stairs
tgt: Walk forward, between the two office desks until you reach the white sofa. Wait at the top of the stairs.

src: walk in between table sofa enter room left of tall wooden chairs after room right wait by bathtub
tgt: Walk in between dining table and sofa.  Enter room to the left of the tall wooden chairs.  After you enter the room, make a right.  Wait by bathtub.

src: walk right purple couch right stairs into bedroom next bedroom door
tgt: Walk to the right and towards the purple couch. Take a right and go up the stairs into the bedroom. Stop next to the bedroom door.

src: walk forward then sharp right at water fountain forward into large room past table on between benches door
tgt: Walk forward and then take a sharp right at the water fountain. Walk forward into the large room past the table. Follow on between the benches and our the door.

src: walk through door on left past big table through double doors
tgt: Walk through the door on your left, past the big table and through the double doors.

src: walk across bedroom then into hallway on left door on right in front of stairs in doorway
tgt: Walk across the bedroom, then into  the hallway on the left. Enter the door on the right in front of the stairs, and stop in the doorway.

src: turn slightly right doorway right room via doorway there
tgt: Turn slightly right and enter the doorway. Turn right and exit the room via the farthest doorway to you left. Stay there.

src: turn hallway wait in second doorway on right
tgt: Turn left to walk down the hallway. Wait in the second doorway on the right.

src: straight doorway on left right room with machine turn closet turn through doorway bathroom
tgt: Go straight and enter the doorway on the left. Turn right and enter the room with the washing machine. Turn left and enter the closet. Turn left, go through the doorway, and enter the bathroom.

src: walk out of bathroom right down hall past stairs right by kitchen island
tgt: Walk out of the bathroom and turn right. Walk down the hall past the stairs and turn right. Stop by the kitchen island.

src: straight into kitchen then left straight until round table with chairs horse statue on there
tgt: Go straight into the kitchen and then turn left. Go straight until you get to the round table with chairs that has a horse statue on it and wait there.

src: walk toward cloth table right right past table into hallway right into entryway of bathroom stop
tgt: Walk toward the cloth covered table and turn right. Walk right past the table into the hallway. Turn right and walk into the entryway of the bathroom and stop.

src: sets of stairs wait by blue couch
tgt: Go down both sets of stairs. Wait by the blue couch.

src: walk into bedroom past bed on left past stairs on left up stairs wait on third step from top landing
tgt: Walk into bedroom. Walk past bed on the left. Walk past stairs going down on the left. Walk up stairs. Wait on third step from the top landing.

src: walk past desks chairs hall on right past desks in entry of room on left with pool table
tgt: Walk past the two desks and two chairs. Take the hall on the right, past the desks. Stop in the entry of the room on the left with the pool table.

src: steps on first step
tgt: Go and start up the steps. Stop on the first step.

src: into bathroom right hallway turn left then in front of blue armchairs
tgt: Go into the bathroom and turn right, enter the hallway and turn left and then turn left, turn left and stop in front of the blue armchairs.

src: exit closet straight past mini gym on left straight into room right into room wait near desk with chairs
tgt: Exit the closet. Go straight past the mini gym on the left. Go straight into the room. Turn right and go into the room. Wait near the desk with the two chairs.

src: walk though laundry room sink on end of counter near open door right into kitchen walk through kitchen towards refrigerator on right end of counter on left forward past patio doors beginning of stairs
tgt: Walk though the laundry room to the sink on the end of the counter near an open door. Turn right and walk into the kitchen. Walk through the kitchen towards the refrigerator on the right and the end of the counter on the left. Walk forward past the patio doors and to the beginning of the stairs.

src: through doorway hall beside kitchen now left in hallway right couch through doorway of office wait
tgt: You need to walk through the doorway to the hall beside the kitchen. Now make a left in the hallway and make a right when you get to the couch. Go through the doorway of the office and wait.

src: up small set of stairs in living room stay door left turn hallway room wait beside white lamp
tgt: Walk up the small set of stairs in the living room.  Stay left and enter the door to your left.  Turn left down the hallway and enter the room.  Wait beside the white lamp.

src: straight into hall down hall right right around corner at top of stairs
tgt: Go straight into the hall and down the hall to the right. Turn right around the corner and stop at the top of the stairs.

src: straight before staircase
tgt: Go straight and stop before the staircase.

src: down walkway past chairs couches turn at double glass doors just inside building
tgt: Walk down the walkway past the chairs and couches. Turn left at the double glass doors and stop just inside the building.

src: walk past kitchen through doorway on left wait in outdoor kitchen bar area
tgt: Walk past the kitchen and through the doorway on the left. Wait in the outdoor kitchen bar area.

src: walk forward down hallway bedroom at end of hall left into closet next shelf with gray white basket
tgt: Walk forward down the hallway. Enter the bedroom at the end of the hall. Take a left into the closet. Stop next to the shelf with the gray and white basket.

src: turn handicapped bathroom left down floral carpet carpet until door with exit sign about through door in front of once through doorway outside at destination
tgt: Turn around to where there is a handicapped bathroom to your left. Head down the floral carpet. Continue down the carpet until you get to a door with an exit sign about it. Go through that door in front of you. Once you go through the doorway you will be outside and you are at your destination.

src: turn slightly into bathroom wait by weird toilet
tgt: Turn slightly left and go into the bathroom. Wait by the weird looking toilet.

src: through hallway with pictures right into room with square pattern on floor square diagonally in doorway hangings
tgt: Go through the hallway with the pictures to your right into the room with the square pattern on the floor. Cross the square diagonally and stop in the doorway where the four hangings are.

src: exit bathroom through door on left straight in front of double doors right
tgt: Exit the bathroom through the door on the left. Go straight and stop in front of the double doors to the right.

src: into bedroom around right into bathroom in front of shower
tgt: Facing into the bedroom, go around to the right into the bathroom and stop in front of the shower.

src: pass behind chairs toward table at corner of couch
tgt: pass behind chairs and toward table, turn left and stop at corner of couch.

src: down stairs straight across hallway at end of hallway turn right down stairs by first window on right
tgt: Walk down the stairs and straight across the hallway. At the end of the hallway turn right and walk down the stairs. Stop by the first window on the right.

src: toward table through door past couch on right second brown chair window with blinds
tgt: Go toward the table. Make and left and go through the door. Go past the couch on the right to the second brown chair. go to the window with the blinds.

src: walk out of living room towards dining room table past table left into wine room in doorway wine room
tgt: Walk out of the living room towards the dining room table. Past the table take a left into the wine room. Stop in the doorway to the wine room.

src: forward towards mirror turn hallway in front of doorways side by side doorway on right bathroom wait in doorway
tgt: Move forward towards the mirror, turn left and head down the hallway. In front of you will be two doorways side by side. Enter the doorway on the right which is the bathroom. Wait in that doorway.

src: straight into room through door on left turn into first door on left
tgt: Go straight into the room, and go through the door on the left. Turn left, and go into the first door on the left.

src: past bed into room on right right into bathroom first into closet once door
tgt: Go past the bed, and into the room on the right. Take a right into the bathroom. Take the first left into the closet. Stop once you pass the door.

src: walk past brown leather recliner walk through open french doors hard opposite zebra painting wait at mirror
tgt: Walk past brown leather recliner. Walk through open french doors. Make hard left opposite zebra painting. Wait at mirror.

src: straight sink on left table on right left wait near stairs
tgt: Go straight passed the sink on the left, passed the dining table on the right, make a left and wait near the stairs.

src: through hallway through doorway up stairs on left at top
tgt: Go through hallway, through the doorway and up the stairs on the left, and stop at the top.

src: walk around table past gray chair by bookshelf
tgt: Walk around the table. and past the gray chair. Stop by the bookshelf.

src: enter bedroom walk past bed turn bedroom walk past pool table turn hallway wait in front of wall shelf
tgt: Enter the bedroom and walk past the bed. Turn left and exit the bedroom. Walk past the pool table and turn left down the hallway. Wait in front of the wall shelf.

src: climb stairs walk past windows on right next set of stairs wait at top next green white chair
tgt: Climb the stairs and walk past the windows on the right. Climb the next set of stairs and wait at the top next to the green and white chair.

src: turn through purple chairs turn by box
tgt: Turn around and cross through the purple chairs. Turn left and stop by the box.

src: stand so stairs on left walk straight past kitchen area by bar stools kitchen island after kitchen area just right of artworks vertically on wood wall on right
tgt: Stand so the stairs are on your left and walk straight past the kitchen area, passing by four bar stools facing the kitchen island.  After passing the kitchen area, stop just to the right of the three framed artworks placed vertically on the wood wall on the right.

src: with wire vine artwork on left straight into big room with square mosaic on floor through door on left on wall on far side of mosaic walk into room stop at foot of bed
tgt: With the wire vine artwork on your left, walk straight into the big room with the square mosaic on the floor.  Go through the door on the left on the wall on the far side of the mosaic.  Walk into the room and stop at the foot of the bed.

src: walk across bedroom exit door straight open door into living room behind couch
tgt: Walk across bedroom to glass exit door. walk straight passed open door to outside and into living room, stop behind couch.

src: stairs down dark brown hallway of way near end
tgt: Go down the stairs and down the dark brown hallway all of the way, and stop when you get near the end.

src: walk through door out of garage down hallway turn right again in between kitchen island table right after island down hallway of fridge before first doorway
tgt: walk through door out of garage, walk down hallway and turn left, turn right again to walk in between kitchen island and dining table, slight right after island and walk down hallway to left of fridge. stop before first doorway.

src: down balcony house through green door down hall bedroom through second door on right next door in bedroom
tgt: Walk down the balcony and enter the house through the green door. walk down the hall and enter the bedroom through the second door on the right. Stop next to the door in the bedroom.

src: turn right through first entry way on left left of table through left entry way move between stairs wall toward door next plant into room with chairs at table stop

src: walk past table chairs out room double doors right through double doors wait near bottom of stairs
tgt: Walk straight past the table and chairs and out the room using the double doors. Turn right and go through the double doors. Wait near the bottom of the stairs.

src: walk through door past chair on right few steps forward
tgt: Walk left and enter through the door past the chair on your right.  Take a few steps forward and stop.

src: turn right walk towards white armchair right of white coffee table forward around left side of table until entrance kitchen at kitchen doorway
tgt: Turn to your right and walk towards white armchair to the right of the white coffee table. Continue to move forward around the left side of the dining table until you reach the entrance to the kitchen. Stop at the kitchen's doorway.

src: away from drums plant from plant through second doorway on right side
tgt: Go away from the drums. Go to the plant. From the plant, go through the second doorway on the right side.

src: walk through bedroom towards stairs up steps turn up second set of steps room ahead wait here
tgt: Walk through the bedroom towards the stairs.  Walk up steps, and turn left.  Walk up second set of steps and enter the room straight ahead.  Wait here.

src: turn bedroom then into living room then next dining room table
tgt: Turn around and exit  the bedroom, then turn left and walk into the living room. Then stand next to the dining room table.

src: exit bedroom turn into kitchen wait near counter barstool
tgt: Exit the bedroom and turn left. Proceed into the kitchen. Wait near the counter and barstool.

src: walk past christmas out of room at base of stairs under ceiling fan into doorway room between red yellow chairs in front of first chair in dining room
tgt: Walk past the Christmas tree out of the room and go left at the base of the stairs.  Stand under the ceiling fan and go into the doorway to the dining room between the red and yellow chairs.  Stop in front of the first chair you reach in the dining room.

src: turn right through galley kitchen area turn left in pantry right there wait
tgt: Turn right.  Walk through the galley kitchen area.  Turn to the left, you'll be in a pantry.  Stop right there and wait.

src: room right hallway left at end of hallway room stop in doorway
tgt: Leave the room, go right and continue to the hallway. Take a left at the end of the hallway, enter the room and stop in the doorway.

src: turn towards tables turn past shelf into hallway in front of green vase
tgt: Turn left and move towards the tables. Turn left and walk past the shelf into the hallway. Continue walking and stop in front of the green vase.

src: with grass on right walk forward on patio forward until at bistro table with metal chairs just at table with table on left
tgt: With the grass on your right walk forward on the patio and go forward until you are at the bistro table with the metal chairs and stop just at the table with the table on your left.

src: straight through door left then first right before
tgt: Go straight through the door, take a left, and then take your first right before stopping.

src: exit bedroom hall turn at stairs stop
tgt: Exit the bedroom and follow the hall. Turn left at the stairs and stop.

src: walk past bed out of bedroom right in bathroom
tgt: Walk past the bed and out of the bedroom. Turn right and stop in the bathroom.

src: walk straight wait by dining room table
tgt: Walk straight and wait by the dining room table.

src: red carpet hall with fire extinguishers on left side white stairs staircase on right at bottom of next staircase
tgt: Go to the red carpet. Go down the hall with two fire extinguishers on the left side. Go up the three white stairs. Go up the staircase on the right. Stop at the bottom of the next staircase.

src: continue top of stairs then left corner into bathroom just prior bathtub on left
tgt: Continue to the top of the stairs, then turn left to go around the corner and into the bathroom. Stop just prior to reaching the bathtub on your left.

src: down hall turn after stairs down hall wait by bathroom on right
tgt: Walk down the hall and turn left after the stairs. Continue straight down the hall and wait by the bathroom on the right.

src: stand at bottom of staircase towards long table turn into room with blue walls sit in white chair left
tgt: stand at the bottom of the staircase. walk towards long table.   turn left into room with blue walls.  sit in the white chair to your left.

src: turn right outdoors turn then edge of entrance kitchen living room wait just outside of doorway
tgt: Turn to the right.  Go outdoors.  Turn left and then you'll go to the edge of the entrance to the kitchen and living room.  Wait just outside of the doorway.

src: with double doors directly right window directly behind forward past fireplace on right until rope barrier on carpeted pathway
tgt: With the double doors directly to your right and the window directly behind you, move forward past the fireplace on your right until you pass the rope barrier and are standing on the carpeted pathway.

src: alongside glass on left at double wooden doors
tgt: Continue alongside the glass on the left. Stop at the double wooden doors.

src: exit room stairs wait there
tgt: Exit the room. Go down the stairs and wait there.

src: walk past chairs out of cellar up carpet way turn past couches chairs up of steps
tgt: Walk past the chairs and out of the cellar. Walk up the carpet stairs all the way, and turn left. Continue past the two couches, two chairs and up three of the four steps.

src: down hallway left hallway at end of hall right wait at front door
tgt: Walk down the hallway and make a left and walk down that hallway. At the end of the hall make a right and wait at the front door.

src: turn across large work room beside long table at chair behind table slight right hall next green vase
tgt: Turn left and walk across large work room beside long table, turn left at 3rd chair, walk behind table and turn slight right down hall. stop next to green vase.

src: right of couch continue pillar on left skip over wade pool at other side
tgt: Go to the right of the couch and continue. Pass the pillar on your left and skip over the wade pool to stop at the other side.

src: exit office room right right right away into next office room then in doorway
tgt: Exit the office room, make a right, make another right right away into the next office room and then stop in the doorway.

src: stand on second step of stairs
tgt: Go stand on the second step of the curving stairs that go up.

src: turn towards room table on left towards pool on left past outdoor love seat on left past hot tub on right floor rug on right wait at corner of beige woven rug under coffee table
tgt: Turn towards dining room table on left. Turn towards pool on left. Walk past outdoor love seat on left. Walk past hot tub on right. Walk to beige floor rug on the right. Wait at corner of beige woven rug under coffee table.

src: walk out of bedroom slightly hallway slightly right towards flight of stairs walk past stairs onto rug turn through doorway outside stop once past black mat
tgt: Walk out of the bedroom, slightly left down the hallway. Turn slightly right towards the flight of stairs. walk past the stairs onto the rug and turn left. Walk through the doorway to the outside and stop once you are past the black mat.

src: walk out door right left next right wait in bedroom
tgt: Walk out the door to your right. Take a left. Take the next right. Wait in the bedroom.

src: up black stairs exit bathroom through door on left straight past stairs area just after into room with bed in
tgt: Walk up the black stairs and exit the bathroom through the door on your left.  Walk straight past the stairs and sitting area and stop just after stepping into the room with the bed in it.

src: walk out door left.go hall right right into third door on right there
tgt: Walk out the door and take a left.Go down the hall and take a right. Take a right into the third door on the right, wait there.

src: inside past bath tub turn at sink walk into next room towards closet
tgt: Go inside and walk past the bath tub.  Turn left at the sink and walk into the next room towards the closet.

src: travel forward past wall with light switches into first room on right
tgt: Travel forward past the wall with all the light switches and into the first room on your right.

src: turn in till movie ticket on wall left room in by forward forward until near fireplace houseplant right walk forward stairs turn stairs wait
tgt: Turn around in till you can see the movie ticket on the wall to your left. Exit the room you're in by walking forward. Continue to walk forward until you're near the fireplace. Keeping the houseplant to your right walk forward to the stairs. Turn left, go up two stairs and wait.

src: exit bathroom head hallway until arch ahead from arc in front of front door
tgt: Exit the bathroom and head left down the hallway. Keep going until there is an arch ahead, and turn left from the arc, stopping in front of the front door.

src: turn degrees around so steps hallway with photos on right wall steps down hallway pass doorways plant turn toward third doorway
tgt: Turn 180 degrees around so you are facing the steps leading to a hallway with photos on the right wall. Go up the steps. Walk down the hallway. Pass two doorways. When you get to a plant turn toward the third doorway.

src: walk past table chairs up stairs straight at top of stairs in front of stairs
tgt: Walk past the table and chairs and up the stairs.  Walk straight at the top of the stairs and stop in front of the stairs leading down.

src: straight past fireplace then straight into hallway on right right wait near round rug
tgt: Go straight past the fireplace and then turn left and go straight into the hallway on the right. Turn right and wait near the round rug.

src: down path house.turn slight right hallway at couch
tgt: walk down path and enter the house.turn slight right and enter the hallway. stop at the couch.

src: door towards adjustable chair then door by decorative grasses wait there
tgt: Go out the door towards the adjustable chair, then towards the door by the decorative grasses.  Wait there.

src: into room next laundry room wait in en suite bathroom doorway
tgt: Go into the room next to the laundry room and wait in the en suite bathroom doorway.

src: exit bathroom right room door on right right straight past railing then into room on right wait near bed
tgt: Exit the bathroom. Turn right and exit the room using the door on the right. Turn right and go straight past railing then turn left and go into the room on the right. Wait near the bed.

src: from porch enter house through double doors around stairwell stop at archway
tgt: From porch enter house through double doors, walk around the stairwell and stop at archway.

src: walk into room right of end table past bookshelf walk through entryway on right into bathroom in front of sink
tgt: Walk into the room to the right of the end table and past the bookshelf. Walk through the entryway on the right and into the bathroom. Stop in front of the sink.

src: with window behind straight out of room into hallway left in hall into bathroom once past door in bathroom
tgt: With the window behind you go straight and out of the room into the hallway and take a left in the hall and another left into the bathroom stopping once you are past the door in the bathroom.

src: walk forward turn forward forward in room with paintings
tgt: Walk forward and turn left. Walk forward and turn left. Walk forward and wait in the room with 2 paintings.

src: stairs right right again door wait there
tgt: Go down the stairs. Turn right. Turn right again and go out the door. Wait there.

src: straight wait near table then right then straight near fridge turn next left laundry room goal
tgt: go straight wait near dinning table then turn right then go straight near fridge turn left next left laundry room is goal.

src: walk out door in front of then out door right bathroom walk into bedroom walk other side of bed while window over table chairs ocean
tgt: Walk out the door in front of you. Then walk out the door to your right and exit the bathroom. Walk into the bedroom and walk to the other side of the bed. Stop while looking out the window over the table and chairs and the ocean.

src: along grey sidewalk on right toward first metal chair past first chair goal next second metal chair on right
tgt: Move down the along the grey sidewalk on the right toward the first metal chair. .Go past the first chair and the goal is next to the second metal chair on the right.

src: walk into room next rug under large light
tgt: Walk into the room next to the rug. Stand under the large light.

src: down hallway with brown wood tile through open doorway stop
tgt: Walk down the hallway with the brown wood tile. Go through the open doorway and stop.

src: walk between kitchen island brown table kitchen turn hard right dining room dining room left of mirror wait in doorway
tgt: Walk between the kitchen island and the brown table to exit the kitchen, turn left, hard right to enter the dining room, exit the dining room to the left of the mirror, wait in the doorway.

src: head hallway third door on left in bathroom wait near partition
tgt: Head straight down the hallway to the third door on the left. Stop in the bathroom and wait near the partition.

src: straight hallway until chandelier right there near top of stairs
tgt: Go straight down the hallway until you get to the chandelier. Turn right and wait there near the top of the stairs.

src: down hall into first door on left past stairs into dining room stop
tgt: Walk down the hall and into the first door on the left. Walk past the stairs and into the dining room and stop.

src: exit bathroom right bedroom on right between bed mirror
tgt: Exit the bathroom, turn right, enter the bedroom on the right and stand between the bed and mirror.

src: walk forward towards circular desk forward left until sign on floor forward between planters right direction while right on into room until even with end of desk on left here until otherwise
tgt: Walk forward towards the circular desk. Go forward, staying to the left.  Proceed until you pass the sign on the floor. Move forward between the two planters to the furthest right. Change direction and while going to your right, go on into that room until you  are even with the end of the desk on your left. Stand here until you hear otherwise.

src: walk past bed on left past bedside table on left past stairs on left past shag rug on floor right past vase on side table right wait at bathroom sink
tgt: Walk past the bed on the left. Walk past the bedside table on the left. Walk past the stairs on the left. Walk past the shag rug on the floor to the right. Walk past the vase on the side table to the right. Wait at the bathroom sink.

src: walk past chairs walk in front door after walk area right at o'clock position step on carpet in front of window in between couch chairs
tgt: Walk past the chairs and walk in the front door.  After entering, walk to the sitting area to the right at your 2 o'clock position.  Step on the carpet in front of the window and in between the couch and chairs.

src: head steps left of screen then up stairs on right at top of first flight of stairs
tgt: Head up the steps to the left of the screen, then up the stairs on the right. Stop at the top of the first flight of stairs.

src: down hallway through doorway of room hall with half wall on right pictures on wall left at end of half wall turn right at top of stairs
tgt: Walk down the hallway, through the doorway of the room.  Keep walking down the hall with the half wall on your right and the pictures hanging on the wall to your left.  At the end of the half wall turn right and stop at the top of the stairs.

src: turn down long hallway end wait there in hallway by bedroom doors
tgt: Turn left and walk down the long hallway to the end. Wait there in the hallway by the two bedroom doors.

src: walk past hot tub path right through open glass door turn in front of double door entrance home theatre
tgt: walk past the hot tub and take the path to your right. Go through the open sliding glass door and turn left. Stop in front of the double door entrance to the home theatre.

src: walk downstairs stop at bottom left open area at middle of long gray lounger
tgt: Walk downstairs, stop at the bottom and take a left towards the open area, stop at the middle of the long gray lounger.

src: exit dining room right through archway with exit sign stop
tgt: Exit the dining room to the right, go through the archway with the exit sign and stop.

src: turn around bottom of stairs at bottom turn then door left right before white chairs
tgt: Turn around and walk to the bottom of the stairs. At the bottom, turn left and then enter the door to your left, right before the white chairs.

src: enter room left into room head just past white table head outside patio right walk in front of windows stand by windows
tgt: Enter the room to your left. Walk into the room and head just past the white table and head outside to the patio.  Turn right a walk in front of windows.  Stand by the windows.

src: walk through hall into next room chairs through doorway right around desk walk through doorway left of chairs stop
tgt: Walk through the hall into the next room and left around the chairs. Walk through the doorway and right around the desk. Walk through the doorway to the left of the chairs and stop.

src: turn hall onto blue rug then left top of stairs then on past that in hallway in hallway wait
tgt: Turn around and go down the hall.  Go onto the blue rug, and then turn left.  Go to the top of the stairs.  Then go on past that and you'll find yourself in a hallway.  Stop there in the hallway.  Wait.

src: exit bathroom area into bedroom area left then right into closet area wait
tgt: Exit bathroom area into bedroom area, make a left, then make a right into closet area, and wait.

src: straight through kitchen then right into common area straight room by stairs wait by desk
tgt: Go straight through the kitchen and then turn right into the common area, go straight to the room by the stairs, wait by the desk.

src: head into hallway right down hallway until laundry area turn wait at laundry machines
tgt: Head into the hallway and turn right. Travel down the hallway until you reach the laundry area and turn left. Wait at the laundry machines.

src: straight into bright white room right doorway through doorway stop near desk
tgt: Go straight. Turn left into the bright white room and turn right to enter the doorway. Go through the doorway and stop near the desk.

src: walk through bathroom out door right turn through other open door at destination
tgt: Walk through the bathroom and out the door, take a right turn through the other open door and stop at your destination.

src: exit laundry room turn then glass table with fancy chairs round table wait near couches tv
tgt: Exit the laundry room and turn left then turn left and pass the glass table with the fancy chairs. Pass the round table and wait near the couches and the tv.

src: turn so bathroom on left staircase on right straight past next room on left once first room on left
tgt: Turn so the bathroom is on your left and the staircase is on your right. Walk straight past the next room on your left and stop once you pass the first room on your left.

src: through dining area wait right of wooden end table seat
tgt: Go through the dining area and wait to the right of the wooden end table and love seat.

src: exit bathroom right room double doors on right wait in hallway
tgt: Exit the bathroom. Turn right and exit the room using the double doors on the right. Wait in the hallway.

src: into dining room right dining room table step outside through white double doors stop
tgt: Go into the dining room and turn right to go around the dining room table , take a step outside through the white double doors and stop.

src: steps then straight up steps right into bathroom wait near sink
tgt: Go up the steps then continue straight and go up more steps. Turn right and go into the bathroom. Wait near the sink.

src: down stairs into wine room on left
tgt: Walk down the stairs and go into the wine room on the left.

src: from front door straight back until table with white table cloth end of table left stand in doorway right in doorway bathroom doorway in doorway
tgt: From the front door you need to walk straight back until you get to the table with the white table cloth. When you walk to the end of the table make a left and stand in the doorway. Make a right when you are in the doorway and go to the bathroom doorway. You have to wait in the doorway.

src: exit powder room then right down hall right past wine rack
tgt: Exit the powder room then turn right and walk down the hall. Turn to your right and walk past the wine rack.

src: enter building walk through dining area wait in doorway under mounted deer head
tgt: Enter the building and walk through the dining area. Wait in the doorway under the mounted deer head.

src: turn head towards hall way continue until square right through glass doors first into shop
tgt: Turn around and head towards the hall way. Continue , until you see the square windows and make a right. Continue through the glass doors and make your first left into the shop.

src: through living room right at dining room table until front door in hallway
tgt: Go through the living room, take a right at the dining room table, and continue until you reach the front door, stopping in the hallway.

src: enter dining room with hardwood floors turn after dining room walk past dinner table door left of swirly blue orange painting wait here
tgt: Enter the dining room with hardwood floors.  Turn left after you enter the dining room and walk past the dinner table.  Enter the door to the left of the swirly blue and orange painting. Wait here.

src: room straight stairs on landing stairs
tgt: Leave this room, and go straight. Go down the stairs. Stop on the landing to the stairs.

src: porch walk into house through door left into first hallway on left walk forwards turn second door on left just before through door sink
tgt: Leave the porch and walk into the house through the door. Take a left into the first hallway you come to on the left. Walk forwards and turn to face the second door on the left. Stop just before entering through the door, facing the sink.

src: stairs walk straight first right into play room walk forward beside dollhouse
tgt: Go up the stairs and walk straight. Take the first right into the play room and walk forward. Stop beside the dollhouse.

src: rotate body left walk forwards towards treadmill door left
tgt: Rotate body to the left. Walk forwards towards the treadmill, Stop when you reach the door to the left.

src: turn around out of room wait at bottom of steps
tgt: Turn around and walk out of the room. Wait at the bottom of the steps.

src: turn around through room with woven chairs up steps turn through open doors through hallway stop before window with white shade down
tgt: Turn around and walk through the room with the woven chairs. Walk up the two steps and turn left through the open doors. Walk through the hallway and stop before the window with white shade that is drawn down.

src: turn right stairs up stairs desk chair beside chair
tgt: Turn right, walk to the stairs, walk up the stairs, walk to the desk chair and stop beside the chair.

src: walk toward air conditioners turn toward stairs once bottom of stairs
tgt: Walk toward the air conditioners, turn left to go toward the stairs, and stop once you reach the bottom of the stairs.

src: hard right through bedroom door turn hallway turn walk towards stairs down stairs
tgt: turn hard right. go through bedroom door. turn left. go to door that leads to the hallway. turn left. walk towards the stairs. walk down stairs.

src: exit bathroom right walk straight until table chairs there
tgt: Exit the bathroom. Turn right and walk straight until you get to the table and chairs. Stop there.

src: walk past jacket on chair left office right right opposite exit sign from ceiling on left wait in threshold of open door
tgt: Walk past the jacket hanging on the chair to the left. Exit the office, and make a right. Make a right opposite the exit sign hanging from the ceiling on the left. Wait in the threshold of the open door.

src: past stairs straight dining room table stop wait just after kitchen area
tgt: Go past the stairs and continue straight passing the dining room table. Stop and wait just after you enter the kitchen area.

src: exit bedroom walk towards stairs by bookcase downstairs stop inside bedroom
tgt: Exit the bedroom and walk towards the stairs by the bookcase. Go downstairs and stop inside the bedroom.

src: turn right around counter out of kitchen steps turn forward up thermostat
tgt: Turn right around the counter and walk straight out of the kitchen. Go down the three steps.  Turn left and walk forward up to the thermostat.

src: right through living room in hallway left corridor next first lamp on console table behind couch
tgt: Take a right and go through the living room. In the hallway take a left and go down a corridor stopping next to the first lamp on the console table behind the couch.

src: walk forward then mirror then at stairs
tgt: walk forward then turn left when you see a mirror then stop at the stairs.

src: turn door on right then right into room next door wait at entrance
tgt: Turn left and go out the door on your right then turn right and go into the room next door. Wait at the entrance.

src: walk toward black sheer curtain right behind yellow couches turn curtain walk past bed stop at foot of bathtub
tgt: Walk toward the black sheer curtain.  Turn right to walk behind the yellow couches.  Turn left to go around the curtain.  Walk past the bed and stop at the foot of the bathtub.

src: walk onto paving stones turn path toward door wait in entry way
tgt: Walk onto the paving stones and turn left, following the path toward the door. Wait in the entry way.

src: stairway through hall with cabinets at entrance bathroom
tgt: Go up the stairway and through the hall with cabinets.  Stop at the entrance to the bathroom.

src: walk straight across room door on left at first kitchen island first right wait in bathroom
tgt: Walk straight across the room keeping the sliding door on the left. Turn left at the first kitchen island. Make the first right and wait in the bathroom.

src: straight through work area bedroom right few steps then right in big hallway stop wait
tgt: You'll go straight, through a work out area.  When you get to the bedroom, youl'll turn right.  Go a few more steps and then turn right. You will be in a big hallway.  Stop and wait.

src: down stairs forward next with guitar
tgt: Walk down the stairs. Walk forward and stop next to paining with guitar.

src: in office open door hallway though door down hallway until end turn right forward until first door on right hand side
tgt: STARTING IN AN OFFICE FACING AN OPEN DOOR LOOKING DOWN A HALLWAY, WALK THOUGH THE DOOR AND DOWN THE HALLWAY UNTIL YOU REACH THE END, TURN TO THE RIGHT AND WALK FORWARD UNTIL YOU REACH THE FIRST DOOR ON THE RIGHT HAND SIDE.

src: exit bedroom through door turn forward white glass door on left enter inside glass door forward in front of white table
tgt: Exit the bedroom through the door and turn left. Walk forward to the patterned white glass door on your left. Enter inside the glass door, and walk forward, and stop in front of the white table.

src: walk out of room walk into bathroom on left wait there
tgt: Walk out of the room walk into the bathroom on the left and wait there.

src: right then keyboard purple room stop near doorway
tgt: Go right and then go left passed the keyboard. Enter the purple room and stop near the doorway.

src: left at couch stairs through kitchen into hallway outside of door on right after kitchen
tgt: Take a left at the couch and go up the stairs. Walk through the kitchen and into the hallway. Stop outside of the door on the right after you exit the kitchen.

src: left after dresser out of room wait in hallway just outside room
tgt: Take a left after the dresser and walk out of the room. Wait in the hallway just outside the room.

src: turn right across kitchen area walk towards white sofas in living room around white sofa close right wall
tgt: Turn right and walk across the kitchen area. Walk towards the white sofas in the living room. Stay around the white sofa close to the right wall.

src: right hallway couple of stairs on rigth
tgt: Go right down the hallway and go down a couple of stairs on the rigth.

src: walk forward out of kitchen into room with pink chairs walk across foyer office in doorway office
tgt: Walk forward and out of the kitchen into the room with the pink dining chairs. Walk across the foyer and enter the office. Stop in the doorway to the office.

src: stairs turn past stairs through doorway into office office through bookshelf passage on left wait by mirror
tgt: Proceed up the stairs, turn left and walk past the stairs, through the doorway into the office. Exit the office through the bookshelf passage on the left and wait by the mirror.

src: turn walk past stairs walk into bedroom walk past bed door on left at entrance bathroom
tgt: Turn around. Walk past the stairs. Walk into the bedroom. Walk past the bed to the door on the left. Stop at the entrance to the bathroom.

src: forward stairs left at top of stairs bathroom on left in doorway
tgt: Go forward, and go up the stairs. Take a left at the top of the stairs. Enter the bathroom on the left. Stop in the doorway.

src: exit room from double doors next fireplace then hall until living room in front of front door
tgt: Exit the room from the double doors next to the fireplace, then continue down the hall until reaching the living room in front of the front door.

src: turn around past sink right past dishwasher wait at end of counters in front of cupboards
tgt: Turn around and walk past the sink and take a right. Walk past the dishwasher and wait at the end of the counters and in front of the cupboards.

src: hallway towards stairs down stairs straight down stairs right down rest of stairs turn straight right in front of stove
tgt: walk down hallway towards stairs, walk down stairs, continue straight, walk down more stairs, turn right and walk down the rest of the stairs, turn left, walk straight and turn right and stop in front of stove.

src: enter room turn past bed turn into bathroom wait near tub
tgt: Enter the room. Turn left and go past the bed. Turn left into the bathroom. Wait near the tub.

src: turn right enter into house once in house red purple chairs stairs stop
tgt: Turn right and enter into the house. Once in the house, pass the red and purple chairs and go up the stairs and stop.

src: walk into corridor just of statue first door on right wait near sink
tgt: Walk into corridor just left of the statue.  Enter the first door on the right.  Wait near sink.

src: turn around towards kitchen as soon as seating area before tiled kitchen area right towards doorway into bedroom walk into bedroom turn past bed so that bed on right tv on left past bathtub door into bathroom just inside doorway bathroom
tgt: Turn around to walk towards the kitchen. As soon as you leave the seating area and before you enter the tiled kitchen area, turn right to move towards the doorway that leads into the bedroom. Walk into the bedroom and turn left to walk past the bed, so that the bed is on your right and the TV is on your left. Walk past the bathtub and towards the door into the bathroom. Stop when you are standing just inside the doorway to the bathroom.

src: head through dining area turn stairs up second stair stop wait there
tgt: Head through the dining area and turn left to the stairs. Go up to the second stair, stop and wait there.

src: after stairs right turn right into room right of thermostat wait by first bathroom sink
tgt: After you go up the stairs go right turn right and go into the room that is to the right of the thermostat. Wait by the first bathroom sink.

src: at base of stairs path right past black table water fountain onto rocks just before onto blue basketball court
tgt: At the base of the stairs, take the path to the right and walk past the black table and water fountain.  Step onto the rocks and stop just before stepping onto the blue basketball court.

src: bedroom right down hallway into bathroom through last door on right in bathroom doorway
tgt: Leave the bedroom and take a right. Walk down the hallway and go into the bathroom through the last door on the right. Stop in the bathroom doorway.

src: exit room turn straight into room walk past bed straight into bathroom wait near sink
tgt: Exit the room. Turn left and go straight into the room. Walk past the bed and continue straight into the bathroom. Wait near the sink.

src: walk ahead through open doorway down hall up small set of steps wide circular concrete wall out of doorway outside of home
tgt: Walk ahead through the open doorway. Walk down the hall and up the small set of steps. Continue walking passed the wide circular concrete wall. Walk out of the doorway to the outside of the home.

src: straight then stairs down near exit room
tgt: Go straight then turn left to the stairs go down near the exit room.

src: after inside building right stairs wait on second step
tgt: After you walk inside the building make a right and go to the stairs, and wait on the second step.

src: hallway walking straight past stairs doorway at end of hall stop wait
tgt: You have to walk down the hallway and keep walking straight past the stairs, when you get to the doorway at the end of the hall stop and wait.

src: exit bedroom continue straight through double doors outside past bed at guardrail next first of tall windows with circle holes in
tgt: Exit the bedroom and continue straight through the double doors, going outside, past the bed, and turning left at the guardrail. Stop next to the first of three tall windows with circle holes in them.

src: turn right hallway into bathroom on right
tgt: Turn right down the hallway, and go into the bathroom on the right.
