src: walk forward stairs then once first landing
tgt: Walk forward to the stairs and then climb up them and stop once you get to the first landing.

src: towards black sofa right before then straight right past bar straight then right past door
tgt: go towards the black sofa. turn right before it then go straight.  take a right past the bar. go straight then left. stop right past the door.

src: walk past rocking chair right walk past chairs right into building right in hallway
tgt: Walk past the rocking chair. Turn right and walk past both rocking chairs. Turn right and walk into the building. Turn right and stop in the hallway. .

src: walk just right ahead of across from small television stall
tgt: Walk just right ahead of you and across from the small television you will find the shower stall.

src: turn stairs way top walk across room in front of door outside bathroom door stop
tgt: Turn around and go up the stairs all the way to the top. Walk across the room in front of the door to go outside and enter the bathroom door and stop.

src: walk down hall right into bedroom at bookcase
tgt: Walk straight down hall turn right into bedroom, stop at bookcase.

src: walk out of laundry room down stairs turn at bottom of stairs forward into living room wait next piano reclining chair
tgt: Walk out of the laundry room and down the stairs.  Turn left at the bottom of the stairs and go forward into the living room. Wait next to the piano and the reclining chair.

src: up stairs wait at top of stairs
tgt: Walk up the stairs. Wait at the top of the stairs.

src: turn bathroom bedroom hall in hall left then right next sofa
tgt: Turn around and exit the bathroom. Continue to exit the bedroom and enter the hall. In the hall take a left and then stop right next to the sofa.

src: stairs turn at top just before outside
tgt: Go up the stairs and turn left at the top.  Stop just before stepping outside.

src: bedroom right out of glass doors into entry way in front of balcony before stairs
tgt: Leave the bedroom and take a right. Walk out of the glass doors and into the entry way. Stop in front of the balcony before you go down the stairs.

src: down first flight of stairs right down next flight of stairs level of home through columns at bottom of stairs into large room ahead with open curtains on windows
tgt: Walk down the first flight of stairs. Turn right and walk down the next flight of stairs to the lower level of the home. walk through the columns at the bottom of the stairs and into the large room ahead with open curtains on the windows.

src: stairs past christmas tree on right wiat room with fireplaplace
tgt: Go down the stairs, past the Christmas tree on your right, and wiat facing the room with the fireplaplace.

src: walk out of room past island turn past counter right by fireplace
tgt: Walk out of the room and past the island. Turn left and walk past the counter. Turn right and stop by the fireplace.

src: after bathroom left turn down hall end of hall right stairs wait on second step
tgt: After you leave the bathroom make a left turn and walk down the hall. When you get to the end of the hall make a right and go to the stairs, wait on the second step.

src: walk into house right into room with table through door left of painting stop after threshold
tgt: Walk into the house and turn right into the room with the dining table.  Go through the door left of the painting and stop after passing the threshold.

src: up stairs walk towards hallway directly right of room across from stairs into first room on left in front of bed
tgt: Walk up the stairs, and walk towards the hallway directly right of the room across from the stairs. Walk into your first room on your left, and stop in front of the bed.

src: exit bathroom past bed television until bedroom wait in doorway left
tgt: Exit the bathroom, continue past the bed and television until you exit the bedroom, wait in the doorway to your left.

src: stairs toward mirror turn toward rug door rug in front of wait outside in front of door
tgt: Go up the stairs toward the mirror, turn left toward the rug, and turn out the door the rug is in front of. Wait outside in front of the door.

src: walk around bed out door on left
tgt: Walk around the bed and out the door on your left.

src: with bbq grill right forward then right grill right building through glass doors ahead of left
tgt: With the BBQ grill to your right, move forward and then turn to the right keeping the grill to your right. Enter the building through the sliding glass doors ahead of you and to the left.

src: turn around towards large green vase once vase turn room with words downtown beside door once black chair into room
tgt: Turn around and walk towards the large green vase. Once you reach the vase, turn left and enter the room with the words #downtown beside the door. Once you enter stop when you get to black chair looking into the room.

src: indoors couches steps straight hallway turn wait near entrance of bedroom
tgt: Go indoors. Pass the couches and go up the steps. Go straight down the hallway and turn left. Wait near the entrance of that bedroom.

src: exit kitchen across living room with red bed at glass walls
tgt: Exit kitchen across living room to bedroom with red bed. Stop at glass walls.

src: walk out doorway closest bed walk down hallway past stairs walk in first room on right
tgt: Walk out the doorway, the one closest to the bed. Walk straight down the hallway, past the stairs and walk in the first room on the right.

src: down hall right then forward by stairs
tgt: Walk down the hall and turn right, then walk forward and wait by the stairs.

src: left of wooden table turn into doorway turn into second doorway steps in stop
tgt: Go to the left of the wooden table, turn left into the doorway, turn left into the second doorway, take two steps in and the stop.

src: exit room turn hallway right into brown double doorway step in
tgt: Exit the room, turn left and go down the hallway, turn right into the brown double doorway, take a step in and stop.

src: head stairs doorway on right toward kitchen sink right through doorway with wine fridge counter top on left
tgt: Head down the stairs to the doorway on the right.  Go toward the kitchen sink.  Turn right and go through the doorway.  Stop with the wine fridge and counter top on the left.

src: turn around marble table right up stairs past pool at entrance showers
tgt: Turn left. Walk around the marble table. Turn right. Walk up the stairs past the pool. Stop at the entrance to the showers.

src: walk ahead into room on right wait at stairs
tgt: Walk straight ahead and into the room on the right. Wait at the stairs.

src: walk out of bathroom into bedroom then left out of bedroom wait right outside door
tgt: Walk out of the bathroom and into the bedroom then make a left. Walk out of the bedroom and wait right outside the door.

src: pass bed exit then tv wait there
tgt: Pass the bed and exit then pass the tv and wait there.

src: walk out of bedroom turn left down steps through bathroom in doorway on other side
tgt: Walk out of the bedroom is turn left and walk down the steps. Walk through the bathroom and stop in the doorway on the other side.

src: with large mirror right down hallway toward large flower bouquet on end table close flowers turn slightly area in front of staircase so stairs back forward kitchen right of black topped island corner of island beside painting of mountain lake
tgt: With the large mirror to your right, walk down the hallway toward the large flower bouquet on the end table.  When you are close to the flowers, turn to the left slightly and walk to the area in front of the staircase.  Turn so the stairs are to your back, and walk forward entering the kitchen to the right of the black topped island.  Stop when you get to the corner of the island, beside the painting of a mountain and lake.

src: downstairs until few stairs
tgt: Go downstairs until there's a few stairs left to go and stop.

src: down hall right through hall in front of entryway living room
tgt: Walk down the hall and turn right. Walk through the hall and stop in front of the entryway to the living room.

src: walk through bedroom until hallway in hallway towards balcony glass window stand in window frame stop
tgt: Walk through the bedroom until you reach the hallway. In the hallway, walk towards the balcony and open the glass sliding window. Stand in the window frame and stop.

src: turn slight right into hallway right door just outside on mat
tgt: turn slight right into hallway and follow it straight.turn right to open door and stop just outside on mat.

src: stairs room at o'clock position step into doorway of bedroom stop
tgt: Go up the stairs and enter the room at your one o'clock position.  Step into the doorway of this bedroom and stop.

src: stairs steps top
tgt: Go up the stairs, stop two steps to the top.

src: walk out of area past stairs down hallway outside on stoop
tgt: Walk out of the sitting area, past the stairs and down the hallway. Wait outside on the stoop.

src: forward towards steps stairs right end of hall wait just inside last door on left
tgt: Move forward towards the steps. go up the stairs and go right to the end of the hall. Wait just inside the last door on the left.

src: straight into room ahead then near sinks
tgt: Go straight into the room ahead and then wait near the two sinks.

src: turn right through doorway with downtown walk past chairs turn at end of table forward at next table right forward at end of second table in front of table with pink box
tgt: Turn to the right to walk through doorway marked with #downtown. Walk past folding chairs. Turn left at end of table and walk forward. At next table, turn right and walk forward. Stop at end of second table, in front of table with pink box.

src: up stairs turn at carpet at top of stairs in middle of doorway
tgt: Walk up the stairs.  Turn left at the carpet at the top of the stairs, and stop in the middle of the doorway.

src: exit kitchen wait in area between sofas
tgt: Exit the kitchen and wait in the sitting area, between the sofas.

src: down hall left through doors down hall in front of double doors
tgt: Walk down the hall and to the left. Walk through the doors and down the hall. Stop in front of the double doors.

src: turn next chair with white cushions left
tgt: Turn left. Wait next to the chair with the white cushions to the left.

src: turn room out last door on right once out turn then right hallway next white door on right hallway beside entrance storage room with drawers
tgt: Turn around and exit the room out the last door on your right. Once out, turn left and then right. Follow the hallway and enter the next white door on your right. Enter the hallway and stop beside the entrance to the storage room with drawers.

src: exit building turn stairs turn wait at bottom of brick porch stairs
tgt: Exit the building, turn left, go up the stairs, turn left, wait at the bottom of the brick porch stairs.

src: left bathroom then left in hall steps now at bottom of steps in bedroom wait
tgt: You should make a left to leave the bathroom, then make a left in the hall to go down the steps. Now stand at the bottom of the steps in the bedroom and wait.

src: turn door near sink then next hallway right enter room stop at edge of rug couch
tgt: Turn left and exit the door near the sink. Then turn left and enter the next hallway. Turn right and enter room, Stop at the edge of the rug facing the couch.

src: exit closet then right room door on right left hallway until desk with with green chairs
tgt: Exit the closet then turn right and exit the room using the door on the right. Turn left and go down the hallway until you get to a desk with with two green chairs.

src: turn wood door once turn left down stairs way bottom at bottom turn right door left
tgt: Turn around and exit out the wood door. Once out turn left and walk down the stairs all the way to the bottom. At the bottom turn right and enter the door to your left and stop.

src: walk so underneath fan then right door inside straight until head of dining room table behind first chair
tgt: Walk so you are standing underneath the fan and then turn right.  Enter the door going inside and walk straight until you reach the head of the dining room table.  Stop behind the first chair you encounter.

src: exit bedroom move right past stairs into bedroom on left just inside room in between dressers
tgt: Exit the bedroom and move to the right, past the stairs, and into the bedroom on the left. Stop just inside the room, in between the two dressers.

src: away from stairs right at double doors right hallway in front of fireplace on right
tgt: walk away from the stairs and turn right, turn left at the double doors and turn right down hallway stop in front of fireplace on the right.

src: exit bathroom walk towards kitchen beside refrigerator
tgt: Exit the bathroom. Walk towards the kitchen and stop beside the refrigerator.

src: turn past couch past couch on right through hallway through there stairs at bottom of stairs
tgt: Turn left, and go past the couch, when you get past the couch, go on to the right and go through the hallway.  Continue through there to the stairs.  You'll need to wait at the bottom of the stairs.

src: forward into kitchen right in kitchen in kitchen walk straight around counter on left right stairs once down stairs left at table
tgt: Walk forward into the kitchen and take a right in the kitchen. In the kitchen walk straight and go around the counter on your left. Take a right and go down the stairs. Once you are down the stairs take a left and stop at the table.

src: walk through wine closet through tall open door on other side ahead into room with wooden floor past round table by arm chairs past table through open entryway ahead door outside with decorative iron
tgt: Walk through the wine closet and through the tall open door on the other side ahead. Walk into the room with a wooden floor and past the round table surrounded by arm chairs. Continue past the table and through the open entryway ahead that leads to a door to the outside with decorative iron.

src: walk straight wait in entryway of room on right
tgt: Walk straight and wait in the entryway of the room on the right.

src: walk past dining table stairs at top of stairs near end table with potted plant on
tgt: Walk past the dining table and go up the stairs.  Stop at the top of the stairs near the end table with a potted plant on it.

src: turn past doorway stairs way slightly little way in front of washer dryer
tgt: Turn left and walk past the doorway.  Go up the stairs, all the way.  Turn slightly left and walk a little way.  You'll stop when you are in front of the washer dryer set.

src: out of bathroom into bedroom past shelves bed couch out of bedroom door head toward door outside just outside door
tgt: Go out of the bathroom into the bedroom.  Go past the shelves and bed and couch out of the bedroom door.  Head toward the door going outside.  Stop just outside the door.

src: walk through double doors turn through set of double doors wait in front of circle in front of stairs between large columns
tgt: Walk through the double doors and turn left. Continue through another set of double doors. Wait in front of the circle railing in front of the stairs and between the large columns.

src: down hall with marble flooring opening wood-floored hall right
tgt: Walk down the hall with marble flooring. Stop when there is an opening to a wood-floored hall to your right.

src: turn closet walk into closet slightly right out of closet into laundry room right into hallway turn into kitchen near refrigerator
tgt: TURN LEFT TO FACE THE CLOSET AND WALK INTO THE CLOSET, TURN SLIGHTLY TO THE RIGHT AND WALK OUT OF THE CLOSET AND INTO THE LAUNDRY ROOM, TURN RIGHT AND WALK INTO THE HALLWAY, TURN LEFT AND WALK INTO THE KITCHEN NEAR THE REFRIGERATOR.

src: stairs left in sitting room left into changing room in doorway of changing room
tgt: Go down the stairs and take a left. In the sitting room take another left and go into the changing room. Stop in the doorway of the changing room.

src: walk beside bed then door straight stairs then at middle of stairs
tgt: walk straight beside the bed then exit the door, walk straight to the stairs then stop at the middle of the stairs.

src: turn couch on right
tgt: Turn around and pass the couch on your right.

src: right hall into room straight ahead in doorway
tgt: Go to the right, and continue down the hall. Go into the sitting room straight ahead. Stop in the doorway.

src: exit closet into bathroom then bathroom into bedroom opposite side of room then bedroom
tgt: Exit the closet into the bathroom, then turn left and exit the bathroom into the bedroom. Go to the opposite side of the room, then exit the bedroom.

src: turn stairs first landing right again stairs forward towards hallway entrance turn hallway door on left bear into room
tgt: turn right up the stairs to the first landing and right again to continue up the stairs. Continue forward towards the hallway entrance. Turn left to proceed down the hallway. Choose the door on the left and bear left into the room.

src: exit bedroom straight hall wait in front of office on right
tgt: Exit the bedroom and go straight down the hall. Wait in front of the office on the right.

src: enter house through doorway turn through doorway past piano wait
tgt: Enter house through doorway. Turn left and go through the doorway past the piano and wait.

src: stairs ahead left then right straight ahead turn through doorway right into game room
tgt: Go up the stairs, walk straight ahead and go left then right and continue walking straight ahead. Turn left and walk through the doorway. Turn right and walk into the game room.

src: walk past table into kitchen wait by counter
tgt: Walk past table, into kitchen and wait by counter.

src: walk into living room door then across living room foyer wait just inside foyer
tgt: Walk into the living room door.  Then walk across the living room to the foyer and wait just inside the foyer.

src: walk forward towards patterned glass door right there
tgt: Walk forward towards the patterned glass door. Turn right, and stop there.

src: walk straight along brick right at bushes slight left walk towards door turn enter door way into living room at table chairs hard right walk straight between giant pillar chair
tgt: Walk straight along brick. turn right at bushes. turn slight left and walk towards door. turn left and enter door way into living room. At table and chairs turn hard right and walk straight. Stop between giant pillar and chair.

src: past table into bed room then into bathroom stand in front of sink
tgt: go past the table and into the bed room then turn left and go into the bathroom and stand in front of the sink.

src: turn right then plant turn into room on right right into double door on right
tgt: Turn right and then turn left. When you get to the plant turn left and go into the room on the right. Turn right and go into the double door on the right.

src: exit bathroom right straight towards stairs wait at top of staircase
tgt: Exit the bathroom and turn right. Go straight towards the stairs that head down. Wait at the top of the staircase.

src: into dining room china cabinet
tgt: Go into the dining room. Go to the China cabinet.

src: straight chairs large mirror on right then right head toward stairs wait on second step top
tgt: Go straight and pass the chairs and the large mirror on the right then turn right and head toward the stairs. Wait on the second step to the top.

src: exit room through door right of fireplace walk through hallway then right end of table right
tgt: Exit the room through the door to the right of the fireplace. Walk through the hallway, then veer right and continue to the nearest end of the table to your right.

src: right through door between rocks outside then by green table
tgt: Go the right through the door and between the rocks and outside, then turn left and stop by the green table.

src: walk through double doors into building stop left of table with flowers
tgt: Walk through the double doors into the building and stop to the left of the table with the flowers.

src: head out of bedroom right past railing through double doors in front of bed
tgt: Head out of the bedroom and turn right going past the railing.  Go left through the double doors and stop in front of the bed.

src: move around recliner exit building through patio doors just past lawn chair right
tgt: Move around the recliner and exit the building through the patio doors. Move just past the lawn chair to the right and stop.

src: walk past fireplace left next room through open door walk past long white table on right in hallway on next room next water fountain
tgt: walk past the fireplace to your left and enter the next room through the open door. Walk past the long white table on your right and stand in hallway on the next room. Stand next to the water fountain.

src: exit room right straight hall through doorway at end of hall globe on wood bookshelf in front of in room turn left doorway bathroom bathroom there
tgt: Exit the room and turn right.  Walk straight down the hall and through the doorway at the end of the hall.  You will see a globe on a wood bookshelf in front of you in that room.  Turn to the left, and there will be a doorway to the bathroom.  Enter the bathroom and stop there.

src: walk stairs stairs next floor walk towards ship painting into door on left wait there
tgt: Walk to the stairs. Go down the stairs to the next floor. Walk towards the ship painting. Go into the door on your left and wait there.

src: walk towards stair case through hallway left of double doors with mirrors on through hall small room with fireplace directly next first leather chair on right
tgt: Walk towards the stair case, and straight through the hallway to the left of the double doors with mirrors on it. Walk through the hall to the small room with the fireplace. Stop directly next to the first leather chair on your right.

src: pass area down hall stairs way until stairs from top
tgt: Pass the dining area, down the hall, and go up the stairs, all the way until you get 3 stairs from the top.

src: stairs at base of stairs right walk across room hallway at archway
tgt: continue down the stairs, at base of stairs turn right and walk across room to arch hallway. stop at archway.

src: turn through dining room straight through living room until wall turn through doorway stop
tgt: Turn left and walk through the dining room. Continue walking straight through the living room until you reach the wall.  Turn left through the doorway and stop.

src: down staircase turn pool table turn again through double doors walk across room towards green chairs by first leather armchair
tgt: Walk down the staircase and turn left towards the pool table. Turn left again and walk through the double doors. Walk across the room towards the green chairs. Stop by the first leather armchair.

src: bookcases second beam on railing right
tgt: Go left along the bookcases, and stop when there is the second beam on the railing to the right.

src: room right stairs wait on twelfth step
tgt: Go out the room and turn right. Go down the stairs and wait on the twelfth step.

src: walk toward pool right down path into house turn just inside doorway
tgt: Walk toward the pool and turn right. Walk down the path and into the house. Turn left and stop just inside the doorway.

src: turn around out of closet towards mirror hallway right towards stone area forward into stone area zebra picture turn then immediately right into short hallway with long glass table forward hallway toward small tan fabric dark wood chair right through small door into laundry area right inside area right next door handle sink washer/dryer
tgt: Turn around to walk out of the closet towards the mirror and hallway. Turn right to walk towards the stone floored area. Walk forward into the stone floored area and towards the zebra picture. Turn left and then immediately right to walk into the short hallway with the long glass topped table. Walk forward down this hallway toward the small tan fabric and dark wood chair. Turn right to walk through the small door into the laundry area. Stop when you are right inside this area, right next to the door handle and facing the sink and washer/dryer.

src: turn left up stairs next floor down hallway plants before stairs bedroom
tgt: Turn to your left and walk up the stairs to the next floor.  Walk down the hallway that has plants.  Stop before going down the stairs to the bedroom.

src: walk into kitchen through kitchen until fridge before fridge turn right u turn into hallway wait there
tgt: Walk straight into the kitchen. Go through the kitchen until you get to the fridge. Before you get to the fridge turn right. U turn left and go into the hallway. Wait there.

src: forward into room right across room past sinks into last door on right once in doorway
tgt: Walk forward into the room and turn right. Go across the room past all the sinks and turn into the last door on your right. Stop once you are in the doorway.

src: through passageway on left then right hallway after right doorway
tgt: Go through the passageway on the left, then turn right and go down the hallway. After that, take another right and go to the doorway to outside.

src: shower curtain until open door with sink left out of bathroom into exercise room through room open door on opposite side of room next mirror wall down third door on left into doorway
tgt: FACING A SHOWER CURTAIN TURN AROUND UNTIL YOU FACE AN OPEN DOOR WITH A SINK TO THE LEFT, WALK OUT OF THE BATHROOM AND INTO THE EXERCISE ROOM, WALK THROUGH THE ROOM AND TO THE OPEN DOOR ON THE OPPOSITE SIDE OF THE ROOM NEXT TO THE MIRROR WALL, WALK DOWN TO THE THIRD DOOR ON THE LEFT, WALK INTO THE DOORWAY.

src: exit bedroom left toward next bedroom at door
tgt: Exit bedroom, make a left, walk toward next bedroom and stop at door.

src: walk around kitchen through doorway left of refrigerator right in little room stop in doorway laundry room
tgt: Walk around the kitchen and through the doorway to the left of the refrigerator.  Turn right in the little room and stop in the doorway to the laundry room.

src: behind door on right inside room near grey chair
tgt: Go behind you and enter the door on the right. Stop inside the room near the grey chair.

src: walk past dining table table with statue halfway up stairs wait there
tgt: Walk past the dining table and the table with the statue. Walk halfway up the stairs and wait there.

src: walk past foot of bed straight out door down hall past top of stairs end table with potted plant on
tgt: Walk past the foot of the bed and keep going straight out the door.  Walk down the hall and past the top of the stairs and stop when you get to the end table with the potted plant on it.

src: exit bedroom turn through kitchen into first doorway on left outside doorway long room with wine on shelves
tgt: Exit the bedroom. Turn left and go through the kitchen. Turn into the first doorway on the left. Stop outside the doorway to the long room with wine on the shelves.

src: turn ninety degrees large table in front of towards table before rug thirty degrees right towards doorway in front of food station twenty degrees left straight until doorway on right ninety degrees so that open doorway walk through doorway halfway down hall large staircase in front of
tgt: Turn left ninety degrees.  There is a large table in front of you.  Walk towards the table.  Stop before you get to the rug.  Turn thirty degrees to your right.  Walk towards the doorway.  Stop in front of the food warming station.  Turn twenty degrees to your left.  Walk straight until the doorway is on your right.  Turn ninety degrees so that you are facing the open doorway.  Walk through the doorway.  Stop when you are halfway down the hall.  There is a large staircase in front of you.

src: walk forward stairs right top stairs wait there
tgt: Walk forward and head up the stairs to the right.  Continue to the top stairs.  Wait there.

src: exit bathroom hard left past stairs right wait by outside furniture
tgt: Exit bathroom turn hard left.  Walk past stairs.  Turn right and wait by outside furniture.

src: in right hand door turn straight stove sink into room on right
tgt: Go in the right hand door, turn left and continue straight passed the stove and sink. Go into the room on the right and stop.

src: exit room walk straight kitchen turn right past ovens on right large black glass table with chairs stop
tgt: Exit the room and walk straight. When you get to the kitchen turn right and go past the ovens on the right. When you get to a large black glass table with chairs stop.

src: walk towards zebra painting on wall painting turn narrow hallway with solid white door forward wait by mirror
tgt: Walk towards the zebra painting on the wall.  When you reach the painting turn left, and enter the narrow hallway with solid white door.  Walk forward.  Wait by mirror.

src: through door in front of right stairs second set of stairs left halfway down stairs
tgt: Go through the door in front of you and go right down the stairs. Go down the second set of stairs to your left and stop halfway down the stairs.

src: enter building past stove on left by sink then refrigerator finally washing machine dryer in doorway bedroom directly ahead
tgt: Enter the building, walking past the stove on your left, followed by the sink, then the refrigerator and finally, the washing machine and dryer. Stop in the doorway to the bedroom directly ahead.

src: turn living room area past table sofas stop in foyer in front of front door
tgt: Turn and enter the living room area. Go past the table and sofas and stop in the foyer in front of the front door.

src: walk towards counter with bar chairs walking straight past then directly through doorway immediatly after
tgt: Walk towards the counter with the three bar chairs, and keep walking straight past them. Then walk directly through the doorway, and stop immediatly after passing it.

src: walk far end of sitting room wait in entryway
tgt: Walk to the far end of the sitting room and wait in the entryway.

src: bedroom left hallway along stairs at end of stairs right into bedroom in doorway bedroom
tgt: Leave the bedroom and take a left. Go down the hallway that runs along the stairs. At the end of the stairs take a right into the bedroom. Stop in the doorway to the bedroom.

src: walk out door of steps stairs bottom of steps
tgt: walk out door to top of steps. go down the stairs. continue to the bottom of the steps.

src: up stairs right walk hallway right wait by small steps
tgt: Walk up the stairs, turn right and walk to the hallway to your right and wait by the small steps.

src: up stairs right into room ahead there
tgt: Walk up the stairs and take a right. Walk into the room straight ahead and wait there.

src: exit bedroom sharp left toward stairs down stairs at bottom
tgt: Exit the bedroom. Take a sharp left toward the stairs. Walk down the stairs. Stop at the bottom.

src: walk past dining room table chairs walk past fridge in doorway
tgt: Walk past the dining room table and chairs. Walk past the fridge. Stop in the doorway.

src: turn right through kitchen
tgt: turn right and walk through the kitchen.

src: bedroom stairs
tgt: leave the bedroom and go down the stairs.

src: exit through door immediately left hallway once past paintings in hallway turn through doorway right bathroom right in front of sink
tgt: Exit through the door, immediately turn to your left, and move down the hallway. Once you've moved past the paintings in the hallway, turn and move through the doorway to your right. Enter the bathroom to your right and stop in front of the sink.

src: head indoors stairway through through with area on right wait at end of area by blue counter
tgt: Head indoors. Pass the stairway and continue through passing through with the kitchen area on your right.  Wait at the end of the kitchen area by the blue counter.

src: turn right across kitchen once bar turn in door left before desk once in right end of counter
tgt: Turn right and walk across the kitchen. Once you pass the bar, turn in the door to the left before you reach the desk. Once in, turn right and stop when you reach the end of the counter.

src: right towards kitchen kitchen right towards area.wait at entrance of area
tgt: Go right towards the kitchen. Enter the kitchen and turn right towards the dining area.Wait at the entrance of the dining area.

src: exit home office between wall piano keyboard slightly left steps past large column house through gated door wait on other side
tgt: Exit the home office and go between the wall and the piano keyboard. Turn slightly left and go up two steps. Go past the large column and exit the house. Go through the gated door and wait on the other side.

src: exit bathroom through open door first hard right turn possible forward until stairs on left-hand side room ahead of then there wait
tgt: Exit the bathroom through the open door.  Take the first hard right turn that is possible. Continue moving forward until you pass the stairs on your left-hand side. Enter  the room ahead of you and then halt there and wait.

src: turn by pillars straight then by fan
tgt: Turn around and go by the pillars. Keep going straight and then turn left and go by the fan.

src: head indoors pass through bedroom near bathroom entryway
tgt: Head indoors and pass through the bedroom. Stop near the bathroom entryway.

src: stairs through kitchen hallway with plant down hall right of plant office at desk
tgt: Go up the stairs, walk through the kitchen to the hallway with the plant, walk down the hall to the right of the plant, enter the office, wait at the desk.

src: exit bedroom through door on left first door on right wait inside
tgt: Exit the bedroom through the door on the left. Enter the first door on the right and wait inside.

src: straight walkway stop at end just after railing
tgt: Go straight down the walkway and stop at the end, just after the railing.

src: cross room between white side table glass-topped dining table table on right through doorway in front of once through doorway
tgt: Cross the room between the white side table and the glass-topped dining table.  The dining table will be on your right.  Go through the doorway in front of you and stop once you pass through that doorway.

src: with sink on right straight just before onto rug outside in front of first chair outside
tgt: With the sink on your right, walk straight and turn just before stepping onto the rug.  Walk outside and stop in front of the first chair outside.

src: walk past computer desk glass wall past other computer desk walk past book shelf wait near desk by stairs
tgt: Walk past the computer desk and glass wall.  Continue walking past the other computer desk.  Walk past the book shelf.  Wait near the desk by the stairs.

src: past picture with lady out of room into foyer walk past dining room on side of stairs under ceiling fan back of couch
tgt: Go past the picture with a lady, out of the room and into the foyer.  Walk past the dining room and stop on the side of the stairs under a ceiling fan facing the back of a couch.

src: past pink chairs light blue chairs into room on right wait by chair with flowers
tgt: Go past the pink chairs and the light blue chairs and go into the room on the right and wait by the chair with the flowers.

src: walk past rocking chairs into house through hall in front of bathroom
tgt: Walk past the rocking chairs and into the house. Go through hall and stop in front of the bathroom.

src: straight room door on left straight until bedroom wait near bed
tgt: Go straight and exit the room using the door on the left. Go straight until you get to the bedroom. Wait near the bed.

src: after bedroom left in hallway walk picture of beach at picture right into bedroom then bathroom on right side of room wait
tgt: After you leave the bedroom make a left in the hallway and walk to the picture of the beach. When you are at the picture make a right and go into the bedroom. Then go to the bathroom on the right side of the room and wait.

src: walk out of office turn in hall just inside second door on left
tgt: Walk out of the office and turn left in the hall. Stop just inside the second door on the left.

src: kitchen wait near bar stools
tgt: Leave the kitchen and wait near the bar stools.

src: walk towards abstract art wait by doorway
tgt: Walk towards the abstract art and wait by the doorway.

src: turn left down hall then left laundry room near washing machine
tgt: Turn to your left and walk down the hall.  Then turn to your left and enter the laundry room. Stop near the washing machine.

src: turn slightly along hallway walk through doorway north of there
tgt: Turn slightly left and walk along the hallway. Walk through the doorway north of you and wait there.

src: hallway then right steps on right top stop
tgt: Go down the hallway then turn right and go up the steps on the right. when you get to the top stop.

src: away from chair past bed through doorway right in hallway straight walk through doorway on left bedroom on carpet
tgt: walk away from the chair, past the bed and through the doorway, turn right in the hallway continue straight walk through the doorway on the left, enter the bedroom and stop on the carpet.

src: right into hallway first door on left into living area walk forward through door bathroom wait there
tgt: Turn right into the hallway. Take the first door on the left into the living area. Walk forward through the door to the bathroom. Wait there.

src: walk far end of room through archway on left wait inside sauna
tgt: Walk to the far end of the room and through the archway on the left wait inside the sauna.

src: straight then right inside house right wait near hallway
tgt: Go straight and then turn right to go inside the house. Turn right and wait near the hallway.

src: walk into kitchen right through door on left walk stairs on second stair from bottom
tgt: Walk into the kitchen and take a right. Go out through the door on the left, and walk to the stairs. Stop on the second stair from the bottom.

src: exit bathroom area right enter other bathroom area
tgt: Exit bathroom or bathing area, make a right, enter other bathroom area.

src: walk out of bedroom right into dining room behind dining room chairs walk past island into hallway stop
tgt: Walk out of the bedroom and turn right. Walk into the dining room and behind the dining room chairs. Walk past the island into the hallway and stop.

src: turn forward steps stop
tgt: Turn around, move forward 4 steps, stop.

src: stairs at bottom first door on right hallway inside room next fireplace
tgt: Go down the stairs and at the bottom, enter the first door on the right. Continue down the hallway and stop inside the room next to the fireplace.

src: turn left walk straight towards glass door outside left at clay sofa slight stairs
tgt: Turn to the left and walk straight towards the glass door that leads to the outside. Make another left at the clay sofa. Make another slight left and climb the stairs.

src: walk along hallway out through open door walk towards chair turn walk towards room with lounge beds glass shelf
tgt: Walk along the hallway out through the open door. Walk towards the barber chair. Turn and walk towards the room with lounge beds and a glass shelf.

src: exit study down hall bathroom stop
tgt: Exit the study. Walk down the hall. Enter the bathroom and stop.

src: straight dog stairs straight through hallway until fireplace on right then
tgt: Go straight. pass the dog and the stairs. Go straight through the hallway until you see a fireplace on the right then stop.

src: exit closet bathroom bedroom through door at foot of bed once hallway
tgt: Exit the closet and bathroom and enter the bedroom.  Leave through the door at the foot of the bed and stop once you have entered the hallway.

src: room with water tanks right just outside door next sink wait
tgt: You need to leave the room with the water tanks and make a right just outside the door. When you get next to the sink wait.

src: room right straight ahead room on right with large bench in center once room
tgt: Leave the room and go right. Looking straight ahead enter the room on the right with the large bench in the center. Stop once you enter the room.

src: bedroom stairs then left turn set of stairs in room at top of steps wait
tgt: Leave the bedroom and go up the stairs then make a left turn and go up the set of stairs. Go in the room at the top of the steps and wait.

src: stairs couch stopping at far end of couch
tgt: Go down the stairs, walking to the couch and stopping at the far end of the couch.

src: walk in between area of red sofa couch on right aluminum office wall on left up flight of stairs wait in room
tgt: Walk in between the area of the red sofa couch which will be on your right and a aluminum office wall which be on your left. Walk up the flight of stairs and wait in the room.

src: turn right then left into hallway hall stairs down about stairs wait there
tgt: Turn to the right and then to the left.  Walk into the hallway.  Go down the hall towards the stairs.  When you go down about 2 or 3 stairs, wait there.

src: walk behind sofa toward bar left toward toward pool table stop near round grey chair
tgt: Walk behind the sofa, toward the bar. Turn left toward toward the pool table and stop near the round, grey chair.

src: stand at top of stairs on level right next black animal head on wall
tgt: Go stand at the top of the stairs on this level, right next to the black animal head on the wall.

src: stairs turn right down stairs turn on second door wait near fireplace
tgt: Go down the stairs turn right and continue going down the stairs. Turn left on the second door. Wait near the fireplace.

src: turn shower around left of tub towards doorway before bedroom stop
tgt: Turn around and exit the shower, follow it around to the left of the tub and go towards the doorway before the bedroom, and stop.

src: stand so door inside behind straight deck towards table chairs at end stand between pillars on left closest table chairs
tgt: Stand so the door going inside is behind you and walk straight down the deck towards the table and chairs at the end.  Stand between the two pillars on the farthest left closest to the table and chairs.

src: walk into building turn right down steps on second step from top
tgt: Walk into the building and turn right. Walk down the steps. Stop on the second step from the top.

src: stairs right at top of stairs past wood french doors past candelabra sconce through door on right on rug
tgt: Walk up stairs. Make right at top of stairs. Walk past wood french doors. Walk past candelabra sconce. Walk through door on right. Wait on rug.

src: up steps right walk up steps at top of stairs
tgt: Walk up the steps and turn right Walk up the steps and stop at the top of the stairs.

src: walk through kitchen on top step of stairs
tgt: Walk through the kitchen and stop on the top step of the stairs.

src: exit garage via door after steps then stairs right steps from top
tgt: Exit the garage via the door after climbing three steps. Then climb the stairs to your right, stopping two steps from the top.

src: walk inside into bedroom walk past area turn at foot of bed inside doorway out of room
tgt: Walk inside and into the bedroom.  Walk past the sitting area and turn left at the foot of the bed.  Stop inside the doorway leading out of the room.

src: through laundry room exit room right step into dining room stop
tgt: Go through the laundry room and exit the room, make a right and step into the dining room and stop.

src: walk straight along path away from plants with guardrail on right through door ahead once inside turn next sink
tgt: Walk straight along the path away from the plants, with the guardrail on your right. Go through the door straight ahead. Once inside, turn left. Stop next to the sink.

src: exit living room stairs wait at top of stairs
tgt: Exit the living room and go up the stairs. Wait at the top of the stairs.

src: up stairs turn through doorway sharp turn hall right up stairs at fourth step
tgt: Walk up the stairs. Turn left and walk through the doorway. Make a sharp turn left down the hall. Turn right and walk up the stairs. Stop at the fourth step.

src: exit through door outside sidewalk first right turn off of sidewalk onto stone flooring step just past white columns then
tgt: Exit through the door to go outside.  Follow the sidewalk and take the first right turn.  Step off of the sidewalk onto the stone flooring.  Step just past the white columns and then stop.

src: exit bathroom right hall turn into kitchen area once kitchen area turn right immediately right again wait in kitchen area in front of sink
tgt: Exit the bathroom and turn right. Continue down the hall and turn left into the kitchen area. Once you enter the kitchen area turn right. Immediately turn right again. Wait in the smaller kitchen area in front of the sink.

src: turn until other house then across deck through open door few steps then on rug
tgt: Turn around until you are facing the other house, then walk across the deck, go through open door, take few steps, then stop on the rug.

src: turn toward pool right in front of pool wait by plants
tgt: Turn around and go toward the pool. Turn right in front of the pool and wait by the plants.

src: walk inside left piano wait at set of stairs immediate left of piano
tgt: Walk inside and take a left towards the piano.  Wait at the set of stairs to the immediate left of the piano.

src: right into office right again between bookshelves then quick left into second doorway on left near toilet
tgt: Turn right into the office, make a right again between the bookshelves and then a quick left. Turn into the second doorway on the left. Stop and wait near the toilet.

src: walk past zebra painting into room walk in front of animal print bench
tgt: Walk past the zebra painting and into the room. Walk left and stop in front of the animal print bench.

src: walk out of office right past stairs turn in front of piano
tgt: Walk out of the office and turn right. Walk past the stairs and turn left. stop in front of the piano.

src: walk forward foot of beds hallway n't forward anymore degrees right forward until kitchen just inside kitchen
tgt: Walk forward, passed the foot of both beds.  Enter the hallway, when you can't go forward anymore, turn 90 degrees to the right and walk forward until you enter the kitchen.  Stop just inside the kitchen.

src: through grand room right into doorway immediately after victorian east lake chairs
tgt: Go through the grand room and take a right into the doorway that is immediately after the two Victorian east lake chairs.

src: exit kitchen walk past stairs wait in sitting room
tgt: Exit the kitchen and walk past the stairs. Wait in the sitting room.

src: walk door then right little bit then straight small stair then at mini bar
tgt: go walk to the door then turn right walk a little bit then turn left go straight to the small stair then stop at the mini bar.

src: dining room walk through washroom into room wait in doorway near couch
tgt: Leave the dining room and walk through the washroom into the sitting room. Wait in the doorway near the couch.

src: walk towards kitchen turn into dining room through dining area right into living room walk through living room toward fireplace slight right into bathroom wait by sink
tgt: Walk towards the kitchen and turn left into the dining room. Continue through the dining area and turn right into the living room. Walk through the living room toward the fireplace and make a slight right into the bathroom. Wait by the sink.

src: walk past stairs right past dining room table chairs in entryway outside
tgt: Walk past the stairs and turn right. Walk past the dining room table and chairs and stop in the entryway to the outside.

src: walk past dual ovens refrigerator forward wait in front of bedroom door
tgt: Walk past the dual ovens and refrigerator and continue forward.  Wait in front of the bedroom door.

src: exit bedroom straight down hallway on left enter stop in doorway
tgt: exit bedroom to hallway. Go straight down hallway to staircase, turn left to bedroom on left and enter, stop in doorway.

src: exit bathroom right into bedroom stop wait near dresser
tgt: Exit the bathroom and turn right into the bedroom. Stop and wait near the dresser.

src: exit room right down hallway over rug at very end of hallway after stairs
tgt: Exit the room and turn right and walk down the hallway over the rug.  Stop at the very end of the hallway after passing the stairs.

src: down cement walkway through door into building walk through door entrance bedroom
tgt: walk down the cement walkway and through the door into the building.  Walk through the door and to the entrance to the bedroom.

src: steps in front of at top walk straight forward down next set of steps at bottom kitchen outside
tgt: Continue up the steps in front of you. At the top walk straight forward and down the next set of steps. At the bottom, stop facing the the kitchen and outside.

src: out of bathroom closet left bathroom once in bedroom walk around bed through door bedroom after bedroom immediate left turn then left into bathroom wait by sink
tgt: You should walk out of the bathroom closet and make a left to leave the bathroom. Once you are in the bedroom walk around the bed and go through the door to leave the bedroom. After you leave the bedroom make an immediate left turn, then make another left to go into the bathroom and wait by the sink.

src: walk past stairway towards long glass table room perpendicular glass table by beside table
tgt: Walk past the stairway, towards the long glass table.  Enter the room perpendicular to the glass table by turning left.  Wait beside the table.

src: turn right hallway until end then right hall door brown doors on right right after second door right into office room
tgt: Turn right, go down the hallway until you come to the end and then make a right, go down the hall passed the door brown doors on the right, right after the second door go right into the office room.

src: walk towards door outside in front of door turn right across room once in front of stairs turn room once in door
tgt: Walk towards the door going outside. In front of the door turn right. Walk across the room. Once you are in front of the stairs, turn left and enter the room. Stop once in the door.

src: walk straight exit room right then into room wait near entrance
tgt: Walk straight and exit the room. Turn right and then turn left into the room. Wait near the entrance.

src: walk toward bedroom right right just inside bathroom door
tgt: Walk toward the bedroom and turn right. Turn right and stop just inside the bathroom door.

src: turn slightly right straight across area set of tables set of tables against wall between wait
tgt: Turn slightly to your right. Walk straight across the dining area, passing one set of tables. When you come to another set of tables, which are against the wall, stand between them and wait.

src: up stairs then through doorway down hall toward brown chair
tgt: walk up the stairs. Then go through the doorway. Walk down the hall. Go toward the brown chair.

src: exit bathroom through door opening across hall then right head top of stairs on right steps down stairs
tgt: Exit the bathroom and go through the door opening across the hall, then turn right and head to the top of the stairs on your right. Take two steps down the stairs.

src: down stairs bottom then hallway right bedroom wait by closet door
tgt: Walk down the stairs to  the bottom.  Then walk down the hallway to your right and enter the bedroom. Wait by the closet door.

src: bathroom right outside of bathroom door
tgt: Leave the bathroom and stop right outside of the bathroom door.

src: walk past barber chair turn in front of plants
tgt: Walk past the barber chair and turn left. Stop in front of the plants.

src: walk towards bedroom turn then through door left of black desk immediately right house wait here
tgt: Walk towards bedroom.  Turn left, then walk through the door to the left of the black desk.  Immediately turn right, and exit the house.  Wait here.

src: exit bedroom turn right before steps right behind couch
tgt: Exit bedroom turn right before steps and stop right behind the couch.

src: down hallway past stairs stop at doorway on right chairs desk
tgt: Walk down the hallway past the stairs and stop at the doorway on your right where there's three chairs and a desk.

src: stairs straight in living room veer in front of tree in large planter on left
tgt: Go down the stairs, and go straight. In the living room veer left. Stop in front of the tree in the large planter on the left.

src: turn around out door swirl on left into room directly next door end of room by mirror
tgt: Turn around and walk out the door that has the swirl on it. Make a left into the room directly next door. Go to the end of the room by the mirror.

src: bathroom bedroom in doorway
tgt: Leave the bathroom. Exit the bedroom. Stop in the doorway.

src: turn stairs then right down hall at bedroom entrance
tgt: Turn around and head up the stairs, then turn right and walk down the hall. Stop at the bedroom entrance.

src: walk past tv through living room right behind far couch behind couch in front of mottled painting
tgt: Walk past the TV through the living room. and take a right behind the far couch. Stop behind the couch in front of the mottled painting.

src: turn entire staircase stop at top of stairway on second floor
tgt: Turn around and head up the entire staircase, Stop at the top of the stairway on the second floor.

src: turn room out of curtains on left once turn left white door once through right steps first turn in steps
tgt: Turn around and exit the room out of the curtains on your left. Once out turn left and enter the white door. Once through, turn right and go down the steps. Stop when you reach the first turn in the steps.

src: walk out of bedroom across hall walk past table chairs walk into bedroom right just inside bathroom
tgt: Walk out of the bedroom and across the hall. Walk past the table and chairs. Walk into the bedroom and turn right. Stop just inside the bathroom.

src: down stairs at bottom near vase with white flowers
tgt: Walk down the stairs and stop at the bottom near the vase with white flowers.

src: walk into elevator area out of elevator down hall into kitchen area around kitchen counter tops towards living room area up backside of couches near table lamp
tgt: Walk into the elevator area. Walk out of the elevator and down the hall into the kitchen area. Walk around the kitchen counter tops towards the living room area. Walk up to the backside of the couches near the table lamp.

src: along railing stairs on left straight until in middle of hallway then
tgt: Go along the railing passed the stairs on your left and keep going straight until your in the middle of the hallway, then stop.

src: turn down hallway wait just inside bedroom
tgt: Turn left and walk down the hallway. Wait just inside the bedroom.

src: turn wood door behind kitchen once inside slightly right through kitchen hallway into room on right in front of washer dryer
tgt: Turn around and exit the wood door  behind you and enter the kitchen. Once inside turn slightly right and walk through the kitchen and head down the hallway. Turn into the 2nd room on the right and stop in front of the washer and dryer.

src: turn left walk other side of bedroom right in front of glass door
tgt: Turn to your left and walk to the other side of the bedroom. Stop right in front of the glass door leading to outside.

src: bedroom right stairs at top of stairs outside of bathroom
tgt: Leave the bedroom, and take a right. Go up the stairs and stop at the top of the stairs outside of the bathroom.

src: stairs left into bedroom around into bathroom behind bedroom door.stand wait just inside entrance bathroom
tgt: Go up the stairs and take a left into the bedroom. Turn around and to into the bathroom behind the bedroom door.Stand and wait just inside the entrance to the bathroom.

src: into hallway right down hall left into dining room past table tight into living room wait between armoire fireplace
tgt: Go into the hallway and go to the right and down the hall. Make a left into the dining room, go past the table and turn tight into the living room. Wait between the armoire and the fireplace.

src: exit bathroom right then hallway turn near stairs wait near door of second bedroom
tgt: Exit the bathroom and turn right, then proceed down the hallway. Turn left and stop near the stairs. Wait near the door of the second bedroom.

src: turn walk towards oriental rug up stairs in front of framed art on wall
tgt: Turn around. Walk towards the oriental rug. Walk up the stairs and stand in front of the framed art on the wall.

src: walk past animal carpet out of room turn in hallway walk towards patio on darker wood floor behind brown chair on right
tgt: Walk past the animal carpet and out of the room.  Turn left in the hallway and walk towards the patio.  Stop on the darker wood floor behind the brown chair on the right.

src: straight until large red white poster impact hub then by hammock
tgt: Go straight until you get to a large red and white poster that says Impact Hub then turn left and wait by the hammock.

src: bedroom down hall wait inside laundry room
tgt: Leave the bedroom, walk down the hall and wait inside the laundry room.

src: entryway couch stairs third stair stop
tgt: Leave the entryway and go to the couch. Go up the stairs to the third stair and stop.

src: exit bedroom right towards stairs upwards stairs head straight hallway until stairs ahead of left leading downwards at top of stairs
tgt: Exit the bedroom and turn right to head towards the stairs leading upwards. Climb the stairs and head straight down the hallway until you see some stairs ahead of you and to the left leading downwards. Stop at the top of those stairs.

src: exit bathroom pass stairs straight until brown chairs then right into room with peach wallpaper wait at entrance
tgt: Exit the bathroom pass the stairs and go straight until you pass the two brown chairs then turn right and go into the room with the peach wallpaper. Wait at the entrance.

src: walk into hallway right through doorway sharp turn on second step
tgt: Walk into the hallway and to the right. Walk through the doorway and make a sharp turn left. Stop on the second step.

src: walk through gate enter building turn down steps near lamp
tgt: walk through gate, enter building, turn left, walk down 2 steps and stop near the lamp.

src: washroom hard left through doorway hard right wait near lockers
tgt: Leave the washroom and make a hard left to go through the doorway. Make a hard right and wait near the lockers.

src: turn through door stairs on left
tgt: Turn around and go through the door. Go up the stairs on the left.

src: turn right door hallway at hallway beside tv
tgt: Turn to you right and walk to the door leading to the hallway. Stop when you are looking at the hallway and are beside the TV.

src: at bottom of stairs through doorway right of glass doors bedroom wait there
tgt: At the bottom of the stairs turn left. Walk through the doorway to the right of the glass doors. Enter the bedroom. Wait there.

src: walk out of library left in front of piano left head into room on right through door left of bookcase in doorway
tgt: Walk out of the library and take a left in front of the piano. Take another left and head into the room on the right through the door left of the bookcase. Stop in the doorway.

src: turn around through door porch forward slightly then right out straight stairs at top of starins with chairs in front of
tgt: Turn around and walk through the door to the porch, walk forward slightly and then turn right and walk out to deck and continue continue straight and walk up stairs.  Stop at top of starins with the rocking chairs in front of you.

src: into bathroom door on left wait near sink
tgt: Go into the bathroom using the door on the left. Wait near the sink.

src: turn at bottom of stairs walk past dining table behind last chair on right on deck outside
tgt: Turn left at the bottom of the stairs and walk past the dining table.  Stop behind the last chair on the right on the deck outside.

src: recreation room straight hall bedroom at end of hall next letter s
tgt: Leave the recreation room, and go straight down the hall. Enter the bedroom at the end of the hall, and stop next to the letter S.

src: down stairs into second door on left next fireplace
tgt: Walk down the stairs and turn into the second door on the left. Stop next to the fireplace.

src: exit women locker room walk through doors on from reception desk walk through double doors on left wait in hallway
tgt: Exit the women's locker room and walk through the doors on the left away from the reception desk. Walk through the double doors on the left and wait in the hallway.

src: down stairs rightmost doorway left along red carpet gated area right wait there
tgt: Walk down the stairs. and enter the rightmost doorway to your left. Walk along the red carpet, cross the gated area to the right  and wait there.

src: turn degrees into hallway right in front of kitchen island walk end of hallway into bathroom on right right of sink
tgt: Turn around 180 degrees and go into the hallway to the right in front of the kitchen island.  Walk to the end of the hallway and go into the bathroom on the right and stand to the right of the sink.

src: straight down stairs steps bottom
tgt: Go straight and down the stairs. Stop three steps to the bottom.

src: walk past television outside right just outside doorway
tgt: Walk past the television and outside. Turn right and stop just outside the doorway.

src: out of bathroom go in first door on hallway right into bathroom stand in doorway
tgt: Go left out of the bathroom the go in the first door on the left down the hallway. Go right into the bathroom and stand in the doorway.

src: walk way until third window from left wait there
tgt: Walk straight all the way down until you get to the third window from the left. Wait there.

src: walk end of hallway right at stairs sets of stairs wait at top
tgt: Walk to the end of the hallway and make a right at the stairs. Go up both sets of stairs and wait at the top.

src: turn right room out curtains once turn left through white door down end of hallway at end turn right bedroom at door in
tgt: Turn right and exit the room out the curtains. Once out turn left and go through the white door and down to the end of the hallway. At the end turn right and enter the bedroom. Stop at the door looking in.

src: up steps right into second door on right
tgt: Walk up the steps and turn right. Walk into the second door on the right and stop.

src: straight hallway outside of bedroom straight in front of far door on right next light switch
tgt: Go straight down the hallway outside of the bedroom. Go straight and stop in front of the far door on the right, next to the light switch.

src: walk through doorway then hard left past dining room table open doorway once outside
tgt: Walk through the doorway and then make a hard left past the dining room table and towards the open doorway, stop once you're outside.

src: stairs right then straight until room with red comforter then right into hallway turn left into bathroom wait by clear sink
tgt: Go down the stairs and turn right then go straight until you get to a room with a red comforter then turn right and go into that hallway and turn left and go into the bathroom. Wait by the clear sink.

src: walk between counter across kitchen in middle of room
tgt: Walk between counter and stove across  kitchen and stop in the middle of dinning room.

src: bedroom right hall stairs office through first door on right in doorway office
tgt: Leave the bedroom and take a right. Go down the hall passing the stairs and enter the office through the first door on your right. Stop in the doorway to the office.

src: head upstairs at top
tgt: Head upstairs and stop at the top.

src: turn straight path right last plant
tgt: Turn around and go straight down the path. Turn right passed the last plant.

src: walk outside of bathroom right head towards end of bedroom way door destination outside door
tgt: walk outside of the bathroom and turn right. Head towards the end of the bedroom and make your way to the door. The destination will be outside the door.

src: forward into down middle of work space forward until white pail on floor next desk with black chair tan chairs stop
tgt: Walk forward into, and down the middle of the work space. Walk forward until you reach a white pail on the floor next to a desk with a black chair and two tan chairs and stop.

src: walk past bed toward desk table just outside bathroom
tgt: Walk past the bed and toward the desk and table. Stop just outside the bathroom.

src: head hall past mirror then across living room far left hallway wait near bathroom door
tgt: Head straight down the hall past the mirror, then across the living room to the far left hallway. Wait near the bathroom door.

src: past bed down hallway until in doorway of room at end of hall
tgt: Go past the bed and down the hallway. Continue until you are in the doorway of the room at the end of the hall.

src: turn door on left long hallway door at end travel up stairs on left
tgt: Turn around and pass the door on the left. Go down the long hallway to the door at the end. Travel up three stairs on the left.

src: exit bedroom between recliner lamp with duck on lampshade
tgt: Exit the bedroom. Stop between the recliner and the lamp with a duck on the lampshade.

src: exit kitchen across living room right into archway into theater room at chair sports picture on wall
tgt: Exit kitchen, go across living room, turn right into archway and walk into theater room. Stop at chair and sports picture on wall.

src: straight by garden table turn into doorway
tgt: Go straight by the garden and passed the table.  Turn left and enter into the doorway.

src: indoors then right on second opening head straight past table with straw chairs straight wait by grey couch
tgt: Go indoors then turn right on the second opening and head straight past the table with the straw chairs. Go straight and wait by the grey couch.

src: walk through kitchen until doors through door on left after into room
tgt: Walk through the kitchen until you reach two doors.  Walk through the door on the left and stop after stepping into the room.

src: bathroom turn at foosball table turn again into bedroom walk foot of bed stop in doorway of bathroom
tgt: Leave the bathroom and turn left.  At the Foosball table turn left again into the bedroom.  Walk to the foot of the bed and stop in the doorway of the bathroom.

src: walk until in next room right into room on right in front of water heater
tgt: Walk until your in the next room. Make a right into the room on the right. Stop in front of the water heater.

src: turn forward few steps then right towards chairs in front of then there
tgt: Turn around. Go forward a few steps then turn right. Walk towards the chairs in front of you then wait there.

src: turn right through first archway turn through double doors down several steps into hallway head hallway until stairway on left wait at top of stairs
tgt: Turn right and walk through the first archway. Turn left and walk through the double doors and down several steps into the hallway. Head straight down the hallway until you reach the stairway on your left. Wait at the top of the stairs.

src: exit room down hallway right at glass door wait
tgt: Exit room and walk down the hallway. Turn right at glass door and wait.

src: turn right through kitchen then foyer wait at bottom of stairs
tgt: Turn right and walk through the kitchen.  Then turn left and enter the foyer. Wait at the bottom of the stairs.

src: exit room right straight hallway right into room past bed turn into second room on left wait there
tgt: Exit the room. Turn right and go straight down the hallway. Turn right and go into the room. Go past the bed and turn left into the second room on the left. Wait there.

src: straight toward stairs on right stairs then hallway wait near fireplace
tgt: Go straight toward the stairs on the right. Pass the stairs then head down the hallway. Wait near the fireplace.

tgt: Move towards the bed and stop once you are between the bed and the television.
