tgt: Face the pool and walk around it clockwise, passing two palm trees and a column.  Stop when you have reached the opposite side from where you started and are in front of an empty urn that is in between the two windows on the right side of the door.

src: stairs landing bottom floor in front of television at bottom of stairs
tgt: Go down the stairs to the landing and continue to the bottom floor. Stop in front of the television at the bottom of the stairs.

src: walk towards area left on walkway stop before stairs
tgt: Walk towards door that leads to out area, take a left on walkway, stop before the two stairs.

src: out of room right towards stairs stairs bar room on left
tgt: Make a left out of the room. Go right, towards the stairs. Pass the stairs and the bar. The room will be on your left.

src: walk out of bathroom stall past sink area through open door at end of bathroom walk across hall open double doors directly ahead into large dining room stop near armchairs around fireplace
tgt: Walk out of the bathroom stall and past the sink area. Continue through the open door at the end of the bathroom. Walk across the hall towards the open double doors directly ahead. Walk into the large dining room and stop near the armchairs around the fireplace.

src: past sculpture house down hallway turn just before orange leather chair
tgt: Go past the sculpture and enter the house. Walk down the hallway and turn left. Stop just before reaching the orange leather chair.

src: walk across room glass wall on right right at stone pillar next box
tgt: Walk across room following glass wall on right, turn right at stone pillar and stop next to OSB box.

src: walk sharp right turn corridor before slight right turn top of steps
tgt: Walk straight, take a sharp right turn and continue down the corridor before making a slight right turn to the top of the steps.

src: head stairs into kitchen right head towards recliner right into bedroom wait
tgt: Head up the stairs and into the kitchen. Turn right and head towards the recliner and take a right into the bedroom and wait.

src: down stairs at bottom
tgt: walk down the stairs. stop at the bottom.

src: finish stairs then straight u turn wait near couches
tgt: Finish going down the stairs then go straight and U turn left. Wait near the couches.

src: straight opposite white door until pillar then few steps pillar towards table stop
tgt: Go straight opposite the white door until you reach the pillar and then take a few steps passed the pillar towards the table and stop.

src: walk past piano wait in front of middle pillar
tgt: Walk past the piano and wait in front of the middle pillar.

src: through door next bed turn around straight hall right outside bathroom
tgt: Go through the door an stand next to the bed the turn around and got straight down the hall and stand right outside the bathroom.

src: way up stairs into first door on left outside of bathroom first door on left in long hall
tgt: Go all the way up the stairs and turn into the first door on the left. Stop outside of the bathroom, the first door on the left in the long hall.

src: stairs in garage walk across foyer past front door left hard right walk past tv walk past dining table left through door patio wait near outdoor table
tgt: Walk up stairs in garage. Walk across foyer, past the front door to the left. Make a hard right, and walk past the TV. Walk past the dining table to the left, and through the sliding door to the patio. Wait near the outdoor dining table.

src: right down stair case next stair case at landing
tgt: Go the right and down the stair case. go to the next stair case and go up it. Stop at the landing.

src: turn right straight until room on right just inside room
tgt: Turn right and go straight until you see a room on your right, stop just inside that room.

src: bathroom into room in sitting room forward towards christmas tree left into dining room in dining room next small serving trolley on right
tgt: Leave the bathroom and go into the sitting room. In the sitting room walk forward towards the Christmas tree, and take a left into the dining room, In the dining room stand next the small serving trolley on your right and stop.

src: exit bedroom right straight across glass floor into narrow hallway wait in front of bedroom on right
tgt: Exit the bedroom and turn right. Continue straight across the glass floor into the narrow hallway. Wait in front of the bedroom on the right.

src: exit bedroom by middle door turn down hall enter bedroom by first doorway on right
tgt: Exit the bedroom where you start by the middle door.  Turn left, and walk down the hall.  Enter another bedroom by the first doorway on your right.

src: straight in through doors down hall bit turn right by planter step at top of stairs wait right there
tgt: Go straight in, through the doors, and down the hall a bit.  Turn to the right by the planter.  Go another step or two and you'll be at the top of the stairs.  Wait right there.

src: walk into house up stairs in living room walk past kitchen down hall on left of refrigerator at tree left next hall stand in doorway first door on left
tgt: Walk into the house and up the stairs in the living room. Walk past the kitchen and down the hall on the left of the refrigerator. At the tree take a left to go down the next hall. Stand in the doorway to the first door on your left.

src: turn hallway right laundry room wait by desk
tgt: Turn left and go down the hallway. Turn right, enter the laundry room and wait by the desk.

src: down wood hallway past open doors photographs on walls stairwell at end of hall first few steps
tgt: Walk down the wood floored hallway past the open doors and framed photographs on the walls. Continue down the stairwell at the end of the hall down the first few steps.

src: enter past thermostat through left opening walk past beds into bathroom wait in front of sink
tgt: Enter past the thermostat and go through the left opening. Walk past the beds into the bathroom and wait in front of the sink.

src: walk upstairs into kitchen in archway dining room
tgt: Walk upstairs, into the kitchen and stop in the archway to the dining room.

src: exit bathroom walk staircase wait here
tgt: Exit the bathroom.   Walk to the staircase.  Wait here.

src: turn right stairs turn up large flight of stairs up left side at fork in stairs at stair just before
tgt: Turn right to walk up stairs. Turn left. Walk up large flight of stairs. Walk up left side at fork in stairs. Stop at stair just before landing.

src: up stairs at fourth stair from top
tgt: Walk up the stairs. Stop at the fourth stair from the top.

src: down hallway bathroom picture with worded text through open door ahead hall into bedroom at end with couches arm chairs around fireplace
tgt: Walk down the hallway passing the bathroom and picture with worded text. Continue through the open door straight ahead. Continue down the hall and into the bedroom at the end with couches and arm chairs around a fireplace.

src: walk right of fireplace into first room after on blue carpet walk through bedroom past green counter top walk through door bedroom on left after into second bedroom
tgt: Walk to the right of the fireplace and go into the first room after stepping on the blue carpet.  Walk through the bedroom and past the green counter top.  Walk through the door to the bedroom on the left.  Stop after stepping into this second bedroom.

src: walk straight hallway head until picture frame on wall
tgt: Walk straight. Enter the hallway. Head straight until you get to a picture frame on the wall.

src: after out of building walk railing right steps pool area wait
tgt: After you walk out of the building walk to the railing and make a right, walk to the steps leading to the pool area and wait.

src: pass beds straight out of room door ahead through laundry room steps then right into room wait by bed
tgt: Pass the beds and go straight out of the room using the door straight ahead. Go through the laundry room. Go up the steps then turn right and go into the room. Wait by the bed.

src: up stairs into first room on right into closet once inside
tgt: Walk up the stairs and go into the first room on the right.  Walk into the closet and stop once inside.

src: straight until table chairs then stairs right steps then
tgt: Go straight until you get to the table and chairs then turn left and go down the stairs. Turn right and go down three steps then stop.

src: exit bedroom left straight down hall door in doorway christmas tree
tgt: exit bedroom to hallway, turn left and go straight down hall to open door, stop in doorway facing christmas tree.

src: turn right then right again hallway little set of stairs now in dining room wait there
tgt: Turn to the right and then to the right again.  Go down the hallway.  Go up the little set of stairs.  You're now in the dining room.  Wait there.

src: straight right hallway until hallway
tgt: Go straight down the right hallway until it intersects another hallway.

src: enter massage room ahead left wait there
tgt: Enter the massage room that is straight ahead and to the left. Wait there.

src: walk towards fireplace turn walk straight through doorway straight past bench in first doorway on right
tgt: walk towards fireplace, turn left and walk straight through doorway, walk straight past bench, stop in first doorway on your right.

src: turn around towards left stairs at bottom
tgt: Turn around and walk towards the left. Descend the stairs and stop at the bottom.

src: double doors directly behind then straight across main hallway past cheetah on right right laundry room with sink
tgt: Put the double doors directly behind you. Then walk straight across the main hallway. Go past the cheetah painting on your right. Turn right, and enter the laundry room with a sink.

src: make at exit sign down hall second office on left office bulletin board full of notices in front of desk with green chair
tgt: Make left at exit sign, walk down the hall to second office on the left. This office has a  bulletin board full of notices. Stop in front of desk with green chair.

src: exit laundry room turn hallway stop near counter
tgt: Exit the laundry room, turn left and go down the hallway and stop near the counter.

src: downstairs wait in bathroom doorway
tgt: Go downstairs and wait in the bathroom doorway.

src: stairs stop
tgt: go down the stairs and stop.

src: walk out of bedroom right into bedroom turn by rug
tgt: Walk out of the bedroom and turn right. Walk into the bedroom and turn left. Stop by the rug.

src: exit bedroom walk past pool table on right through archway left of stair wait at alcove on stair landing
tgt: Exit the bedroom. Walk past the pool table on the right. Walk through the archway to the left of the stair railing. Wait at the alcove on the stair landing.

src: straight until double doors wait there
tgt: Go straight until you go out two double doors that lead to outside. Wait there.

src: pool turn left hall exercise bike on left at end of hallway in doorway on right few feet in front of sinks stop wait
tgt: Go passed the pool and turn left. Go down this hall passing the exercise bike on your left. At the end of the hallway go in the doorway on your right. When you are a few feet in front of the sinks, stop and wait.

src: past stairs through doorway
tgt: Go past the stairs and through the doorway.

src: up stairs right straight ahead potted plant into office room
tgt: Walk up the stairs and turn right. Walk straight ahead, passed the potted plant. Turn into the office room.

src: head past dining table turn kitchen straight ahead in small room past door ahead
tgt: Head past the dining table and turn left towards the kitchen. Go straight ahead and stop in the small room past the door straight ahead.

src: exit living area right toward stairs head way up stairs at top of stairs
tgt: Exit the living area and turn right. Go toward the stairs. Head all the way up the stairs. Stop at the top of the stairs.

src: turn between stairs wall after few steps again towards living room living room right between breakfast table wall
tgt: Turn left and go between the stairs and the wall. After a few steps turn left again towards the living room. Enter the living room.  Turn right and go between the breakfast table and the wall.

src: along couch then stairs into archway left left into archway down stairs then right into doorway of bathroom
tgt: Go along the couch and then turn left up the stairs and proceed into the archway to the left, make a left into another archway, down some stairs, then turn right into the doorway of a bathroom.

src: exit room turn way down hallway open door wait in doorway
tgt: Exit the room, turn left, walk all the way down the hallway to the open door, wait in the doorway.

src: around bed stand in doorway on left
tgt: Go around the bed and stand in the doorway on the left.

src: along bookshelf turn table right along table wait near second black chair
tgt: Go along the bookshelf, turn left along the table, turn right along the table and wait near the second black chair.

src: stairs way up down hallway before door on left
tgt: Go up the stairs. Continue all the way straight up and down the hallway. Stop before you get to the door on the left.

src: stairs then behind chair door enter door bedroom
tgt: go up the stairs then behind the chair there is a door, enter that door you will see a bedroom.

src: steps right pool table into second room on right wait near bed
tgt: Go up the steps. Turn right and pass the pool table. Go into the second room on the right. Wait near the bed.

src: walk end of pool table head right hall right bedroom right past bed on left
tgt: Walk to the end of the pool table and head right. Go down the hall, turn right and enter the bedroom. Turn right and walk past the bed on your left.

src: walk out of bedroom right next small white table
tgt: Walk out of the bedroom and take a right. Wait next to the small white table.

src: leave bedroom in slight left straight enter living room behind couch
tgt: leave bedroom in to hall, turn slight left. continute down hall straight and enter living room, stop behind the couch.

src: turn house hallway open room with couches right walking towards large table beside door outside right before middle table
tgt: Turn left and enter the house. Go down the hallway. When you reach the open room with all the couches , turn right. Keep walking towards the large table beside the door leading outside. Stop right before you reach the middle table.

src: hall then stairs turn right past table chairs till in hallway then wait there
tgt: Continue down the hall.  And then proceed up the stairs.  Turn to the right and go past the table and chairs.  Go till you are standing in the hallway and then stop.  Wait there.

src: turn around across room living room walk through living room dining room wait near table
tgt: Turn around and walk across the room and enter the living room.  Walk through the living room and enter the dining room. Wait near  the table.

src: through bathroom through doorway on left then right at doorway
tgt: Go through the bathroom and through the doorway on your left then make a right and stop at the nearest doorway.

src: turn at fridge hallway right at second skylight walk into bedroom wait at bookshelf
tgt: Turn left at fridge. Walk down hallway. Turn right at second skylight. Walk into bedroom. Wait at bookshelf.

src: turn around out of bathroom past closet area into bedroom next bed on side stop wait there
tgt: Turn around and walk out of the bathroom.  Continue past the closet area.  When you get into the bedroom and are next to the bed, on the side, stop.  Wait there.

src: exit living room up stairs at first landing turn walk stair second from landing wait there by banister
tgt: Exit the living room and walk up the stairs, at the first landing turn left. Walk to the stair that is second from the landing and wait there by the banister.

src: walk forward through gate house second right at bottom of stairs
tgt: Walk forward, and go through the gate. Enter the house and take the second right. Stop at the bottom of the stairs.

src: turn around towards bed turn dining table straight ahead toward small refrigerator under counter on right
tgt: Turn around and walk towards the bed, turn left, pass the dining table, look straight ahead and walk toward the small refrigerator under the counter on the right.

src: walk straight along gray path on floor walk past benches on right then doorway after couple steps in from door in front of rounded edging of table
tgt: Walk straight along the gray path on the floor.  Walk past the two benches on your right and then enter the doorway after them.  Stand a couple steps in from the door in front of the rounded edging of the table.

src: walk top of stairs down stairs sharp turn right down stairs at bottom of stairs
tgt: Walk to the top of the stairs. Walk down the stairs and make a sharp turn right. Walk down the stairs and stop at the bottom of the stairs.

src: walk toward chairs right past chairs up stairs into kitchen at top of stairs
tgt: Walk toward the chairs and turn right. Walk past the chairs and up the stairs into the kitchen. Stop at the top of the stairs.

src: stairs then in doorway outside
tgt: Go up the stairs and then go left.  Stop in the doorway leading outside.

src: walk past table with flowers bed out of bedroom down hall in front of railing
tgt: Walk past the table with the flowers and the bed out of the bedroom. Walk down the hall and stop in front of the railing.

src: hallway turn door pass pot with plant before second turn on second entrance table chairs right head into living room wait by fireplace
tgt: Go down the hallway and turn left when you get to a door. Pass one pot with a plant and before you get to the second one turn left on the second entrance. Pass the table and chairs and turn right. Head into the living room and wait by the fireplace.

src: turn dining room forward through dining room past bottom of staircase just past end of stairs
tgt: Turn around and face the dining room.  Go forward through the dining room, past the bottom of the staircase and stop just past the end of the stairs.

src: exit room walk up steps on right wait in hallway outside weight room
tgt: Exit the room a walk up the steps on the right. Wait in the hallway outside the weight room.

src: walk past dining room table left hallway then into office wait by desk
tgt: Walk past the dining room table and enter the left hallway. Then turn left and walk into the office. Wait by the desk.

src: stairs left left into foyer past round table right into living room stop at edge of couch closest
tgt: Go down the stairs and take a left. Take a left and go into the foyer. Past the round table take a right into the living room. Stop at the edge of the couch closest to where you entered.

src: up stairs sharp left walk behind stairs left wait in laundry room
tgt: Walk up the stairs. Take a sharp left. Walk behind the stairs and take a left. Wait in the laundry room.

src: forward towards wall then towards living room forward until couch then right on steps
tgt: Move forward towards the wall then turn left to head towards the living room. Keep going forward until you reach the couch, then turn right and wait on the steps.

src: walk around bed chairs bathroom on left near shower
tgt: Walk around the bed and chairs and enter the bathroom on your left. Stop near the shower.

src: turn house through living room into foyer onto steps on right wait near bottom
tgt: Turn around and enter the house.  Walk through the living room and into the foyer.  Walk onto the steps on your right. Wait near the bottom.

src: exit room then right pass chair with sink then left hallway room on left stairs wait there by desk
tgt: Exit the room then turn right pass the chair with the sink then turn left to go down the hallway. Enter the room on the left. Pass the stairs and wait there by the desk.

src: walk inside immediately straight towards room in front of inside at door
tgt: Walk inside and turn left immediately. Keep walking straight towards the room in front of you. Enter inside, and stop at the door.

src: enter house through front door walk straight after wooden dresser near wall right down stairs next hard left walk until bathroom on left into bathroom wait by sink
tgt: Enter the house through the front door and walk straight. After you reach the wooden dresser near the wall, turn right and walk down the stairs.  Next make a hard left, and walk until you reach the bathroom on your left.  Continue into the bathroom, and wait by the sink.

src: exit bedroom via door left then bedroom door right there
tgt: Exit the bedroom via the door. Take a left then enter the bedroom door to the right. Wait there.

src: walk out of laundry room right walk end of hallway right into bedroom in front of bed
tgt: Walk out of the laundry room and turn right. Walk to the end of the hallway and turn right. Walk into the bedroom and stop in front of the bed.

src: towards pool then left of pool straight towards diamond shape on wall turn right through way then near plant
tgt: Go towards the pool and then go to the left of the pool, go straight towards the diamond shape on the wall, turn right through the way and then left, and stop near the plant.

src: bottom of staircase in dining room into office
tgt: Go to the bottom of the staircase in the dining room. Go into the office.

src: straight hallway then left past bed veer right through white door in doorway
tgt: Go straight to the hallway and then turn left.  Go past the bed.  Veer to the right and go through the white door.  Stop when you're in the doorway.

src: stairs towards living room fire place on right in front of large round fireplace
tgt: Go down the stairs and go towards the living room fire place on the right. Stop in front of the large round fireplace.

src: turn right room way until white couch at table in front of white couch
tgt: Turn right and cross the room all the way until you reach the white couch. Stop at the table in front of the white couch.

src: walk into bedroom once inside right straight into bathroom walk wait here
tgt: Walk into bedroom.  Once inside, turn right, and walk straight into the bathroom.  Walk to shower.  Wait here.

src: continue rest of stairs turn at top walk towards closet turn hallway bedroom down at end of hallway turn in front of beds
tgt: continue walking up the rest of the stairs, turn left at the top and walk towards the closet. Turn left down the hallway and enter the bedroom straight down at the end of the hallway, turn left and stand in front of the two beds.

src: steps inside then stairs level next blue art on wall
tgt: Go up the steps and inside. Then start up the stairs and stop where it becomes level, next to the blue art on the wall.

src: down hallway turn at guitar wait in doorway bedroom
tgt: Walk down the hallway, turn left at the guitar, wait in the doorway to the bedroom.

src: turn left past hose towards entrance of house right through doorway stairs couple of stairs then wait
tgt: Turn to the left and past the hose.  Go towards the entrance of the house and turn right.  Go through the doorway.  Proceed to the stairs. Go down a couple of stairs and then wait.

src: turn around down stairs wait at bottom of stairs
tgt: Turn around and walk down the stairs. Wait at the bottom of the stairs.

src: walk through kitchen outside wait on porch next chair
tgt: Walk through the kitchen and outside. Wait on the porch next to the chair.

src: down hallway right wait near entrance bathroom
tgt: Walk down the hallway and turn right. Wait near the entrance to the bathroom.

src: head toward room with white couch left toward kitchen then front door turn hall in front of stairs
tgt: Head toward the room with the white couch.  Go left toward the kitchen and then to the front door.  Turn left down the hall and stop in front of the stairs.

src: enter glass door turn stairs down stairs midway at staircase
tgt: Enter the glass door. Turn left towards the stairs, and walk down the stairs, and stop midway at the staircase.

src: stairs left in doorway across from stairs
tgt: Go down the stairs and take a left. Stop in the doorway across from the stairs.

src: walk past bed bedroom hard right in bathroom by shower
tgt: Walk past the bed to exit the bedroom and turn hard right. Stop in the bathroom by the shower.

src: exit room through glass door on right through room television at door on left past television turn room walk bottom of spiral staircase stop
tgt: Exit the room through the glass door on your right. Walk through the room to the television.  At the door on the left past the television, turn left and exit the room.  Walk to the bottom of the spiral staircase and stop.

src: exit room straight past couches on right way table chairs wait there
tgt: Exit the room. Go straight past the couches on the right. Walk all the way to the table and chairs and wait there.

src: stairs turn wait in open doorway down hall on right
tgt: Go down the stairs and turn left. Wait in the open doorway down the hall on the right.

src: walk around bed stop in doorway near painting
tgt: Walk around the bed and stop in the doorway near the painting.

src: turn up stairs at top of stairs
tgt: Turn left and walk up the stairs. Stop at the top of the stairs.

src: walk out of massage room left of pool in front of massage table
tgt: Walk left out of the massage room and to the left of the pool. Stop in front of the massage table.

src: face window right hallway right at banister turn towards pool table right before pool table again past pool table right through doorway
tgt: face window to outside, turn right to walk down hallway, turn right at banister, turn left and walk towards pool table, turn right before you pass the pool table, and left again, walk past the pool table, turn right and walk through doorway to bedroom, stop.

src: enter room next door table chairs right into kitchen then into laundry room wait by sink
tgt: Enter the room next door. Pass the table and chairs. Turn right into the kitchen then turn left and go into the laundry room. Wait by the sink.

src: walk past outdoor chairs on right home through open door left in front of round foyer table wait in dining room door threshold
tgt: Walk past outdoor chairs on the right. Enter the home through the open door. Make a left in front of the round foyer table. Wait in the dining room door threshold.

src: walk through dining room with table on right past doorway on left table on right in between faucet marble cylinder on left
tgt: walk through the dining room with the table on your right, continue past a doorway on your left, a table on your right and stop in between the faucet and marble cylinder on your left.

src: walk past metal chairs into room with red bed head of right side of bed right through passageway walk into bathroom area past mirror in doorway shower
tgt: Walk past the two metal chairs into the room with the red bed.  Go to the head of the right side of the bed and turn right.  Walk through the passageway and walk into the bathroom area.  Walk past the mirror and stop in the doorway to the shower.

src: exit bathroom by straight then right straight second door on right enter that room wait at door
tgt: Exit the bathroom by walking straight then turn right and go straight and enter the second door on the right. Enter that room and wait at the door.

src: turn hallways with pictures on wall left into bedroom through open door turn degrees walk towards bathroom right outside door
tgt: Turn around and go down the hallways with the pictures on the wall.  They will be to your left.  Go into the bedroom through the open door.  Turn left 90 degrees and walk towards the bathroom stopping right outside the door.

src: turn stairs wait there
tgt: Turn left and walk down three stairs. Wait there.

src: walk through door left of fireplace slight right stairs wait on first landing of red stairs
tgt: Walk through the door to the left of the fireplace. Take a slight right to walk up the stairs. Wait on the first landing of the red stairs.

src: exit bedroom stairs straight television on right at door
tgt: Exit the bedroom. Go down the stairs. Keep walking straight passing the television on the right and stop at the door.

src: stairs right into bedroom then left into bathroom
tgt: Go down the stairs and take a right. Go into the bedroom then take a left to go into the bathroom.

src: straight past living room on right into hall at end of hall right in hall left into bedroom in doorway bedroom
tgt: Go straight past the living room on your right. Go into the hall at the end of the hall. Take a right  in a hall, and take a left into a bedroom. Stop in the doorway to the bedroom.

src: pass pool indoors double glass doors large table with chairs turn by wine by
tgt: Pass the pool and go indoors using the double glass doors. Pass the large table with chairs and turn left and wait by the wine bottles that have grapes by them.

src: with glass display case right forward slightly right short series of steps down at bottom of stairs into room immediate left
tgt: With the glass display case to your right, move forward and slightly to your right to take the short series of five steps down. At the bottom of the stairs, go into the room to your immediate left.

src: through big room table on left toward mirror then left through archway wait mid-archway
tgt: Go through the big room passed the table on your left toward the mirror then make a left through the archway and wait mid-archway.

src: walk out double white doors left once in hallway turn right once rug
tgt: Walk out the double white doors to your left. Once in the hallway turn right and stop once you reach the 2nd rug.

src: walk stationary bike turn down staircase walk bottom of stairs into first door on right office
tgt: Walk passed the stationary bike and turn and walk down the staircase. Walk to the bottom of the stairs and turn into the first door on the right which is an office.

src: exit bedroom.turn hallway wait at fireplace
tgt: Exit bedroom.turn left down hallway and wait at fireplace.

src: stairs right few steps by room with carpet
tgt: Go down the stairs, and turn right to go down a few steps. Stop by the room with carpet.

src: exit bedroom right door exit house at chairs
tgt: Exit bedroom to hallway, turn right to front door. Exit house to porch, stop at rocking chairs.

src: turn right out into hallway turn short distance hallway banister on right stairs bottom as soon as at bottom of stairs front door house slightly ahead of right
tgt: Turn to the right and out into the hallway. Turn left and walk a short distance down the hallway, keeping the banister on your right. Turn left to walk down the stairs to the bottom. Stop as soon as you are at the bottom of the stairs. The front door to the house will be slightly ahead of you and to the right.

src: turn room way down steps bottom stop
tgt: Turn around and exit the room. Walk all the way down the steps to the bottom and stop.

src: bathroom past kitchen wait in area
tgt: Leave the bathroom, walk past the kitchen and wait in the sitting area.

src: set of stairs towards area right second set of stairs.wait there
tgt: Go up the set of stairs, go towards the seating area, and turn right to go up the second set of stairs.Wait there.

src: stairs at top of stairs right in hall left into bathroom in doorway bathroom
tgt: Go up the stairs. At the top of the stairs take a right. In the hall take a left into the bathroom. Stop in the doorway to the bathroom.

src: stairs turn into area by wooden bench
tgt: Go down the stairs and turn left.  Walk into the sitting area and stop by the wooden bench.

src: exit bathroom sharp right through doorway then left top of stairs stop
tgt: Exit the bathroom, make a sharp right through the doorway, then make a left to the top of the stairs and stop.

src: walk towards black chairs inside house right room on left past sink on right through next doorway towards brown chair at brown chair
tgt: walk towards the two black chairs inside the house. Turn right and enter the room on your left. walk past the sink on your right and through the next doorway towards the brown chair. Stop at the brown chair.

src: circle mirror on wall through double brown doors right just off area stop
tgt: Facing the circle mirror on the wall go left through the double brown doors, make a right and go just passed the roped off area and stop.

src: down stairs wait at sink
tgt: Walk down hall passed stairs to bathroom, wait at sink.

src: walk through room through sliding glass door on deck
tgt: Walk through the room and through the sliding glass door and stop on the deck.

src: walk past pictures towards white globe on floor after through doorway right past closet wait at entrance bathroom
tgt: Walk past pictures towards white globe on floor. After you go through the doorway, take a right. Go past closet and wait at entrance to the bathroom.

src: exit office toward papers on glass wall.turn immediate follow glass hallway at exit sign
tgt: Exit office toward papers on glass wall.Turn immediate and follow glass hallway. Stop at exit sign.

src: stairs right straight pathway until pool turn at pool walk on first stone in grass near pool
tgt: Go down the stairs and turn right.  Walk straight down the pathway until you get to the pool.  Turn left at the pool and walk on the first stepping stone in the grass near the pool.

src: up steps right out of front door just outside front door
tgt: Walk up the steps and right out of the front door. Stop just outside the front door.

src: exit massage room then straight into hall silver hangings hangings into archway on right of archways stop
tgt: Exit massage room, then go straight into the hall towards the three silver hangings, go passed the hangings and go into the archway on the right of the two archways and stop.

src: exit room hard left into very next doorway stop wait near mirror

tgt: Go to the bed. Exit the bedroom. Go straight into the next room.

tgt: Go down the brick walkway towards the brick stairs.  Go into the large room on the left, before you get to the stairs.Wait.

tgt: walk along the edge of the house and enter the house through the patio door.

tgt: Exit bathroom and turn right. Go through second door on the right and stop.
