src: hallway right toward painting of zebras hard right into doorway wooden floor walkway continue through hallway toward bedroom area left into bathroom doorway on left next white marble countertop
tgt: Move down the hallway to your right toward the painting of the zebras. Make  hard right into the doorway and wooden floor walkway. Continue walking through the hallway toward the bedroom area. Make a left into the bathroom using the doorway on the left. Wait next to the white marble countertop.

src: walk past picture of leopard on wall turn wait at entrance walk in closet
tgt: Walk past the picture of the leopard on the wall and turn left. Wait at the entrance to the walk in closet.

src: exit room door right outside straight at bushes
tgt: Exit dining room to open door,  turn right and go outside. Walk straight and stop at bushes.

src: walk past bar stools near kitchen counter staircase past mirrored doors around corner towards small lounge area with fireplace
tgt: Walk past the bar stools near the kitchen counter.  Continue passed the staircase and past the mirrored doors. Walk around the corner towards the small lounge area with a fireplace.

src: stairs way then right at second doorway in front of black desk
tgt: take the stairs, all the way down , then a right. turn left at the second doorway and stop in front of the black desk.

src: from stairs right around staircase then hall then right wait in doorway of bathroom
tgt: From the stairs turn right and walk around the staircase then walk down the hall. Then take a right and wait in the doorway of the bathroom.

src: stairs patio door wait at patio door
tgt: Go down the stairs, walk to the patio door, wait at the patio door.

src: down stairs wait in kitchen next stove
tgt: Walk down the stairs. Wait in the kitchen next to the stove.

src: turn right chairs right into house wait near coffee table
tgt: Turn right and pass the two rocking chairs. Turn right into the house and wait near the coffee table.

src: walk out of bedroom right immediately down hallway first left into kitchen right head outside wait behind wicker sofa
tgt: Walk out of the bedroom and turn right immediately.  Walk down the hallway and take the first left, into the kitchen. Stay right, and head outside. Wait behind the wicker sofa.

src: exit closet forward into room ahead wait just inside entrance
tgt: Exit the closet and walk forward into the room ahead. Wait just inside the entrance.

src: turn hallway marbled hallway room with carpet work out room there wait
tgt: Turn around and go down the hallway.  Continue down the marbled hallway.  When you get to a room with carpet, a work out room, stop there.  Wait.

src: walk end of hall with guardrail on right into last door on right into bedroom next corner chair
tgt: Walk to the end of the hall with the guardrail on your right. Turn into the last door on the right and go into the bedroom. Stop next to the nearest corner chair.

src: exit study walk across room with closets at closets
tgt: Exit study and walk across dining room to hallway with closets. Stop at closets.

src: exit office right into office on left next black chair
tgt: Exit office to hall turn right, go into office on the left and stop next to black chair.

src: walk out of small room turn out of room into second doorway on left stop
tgt: Walk out of the small room and turn left. Walk out of that room and into the second doorway on the left and stop.

src: enter recreation room straight right at hall bathroom through first right in front of sink
tgt: Enter the recreation room and go straight. Take a right at the hall, and enter the bathroom through the first right. Stop in front of the sink.

src: turn across hall walk across bedroom area doorway left wait there
tgt: Turn left and walk across the hall. Walk across the bedroom area and enter the doorway to your left. Wait there.

src: turn through door into hallway turn forward through doorway next turn right end of runner turn again forward past stairway left quick right into next door wait in doorway
tgt: Turn around, move through the door and into the hallway. Turn left and move forward to through the doorway. Next turn right, walk to the end of the runner and turn left again. Go forward past the stairway, take a left and a quick right into the next door. Wait in that doorway.

src: walk through bathroom turn into hallway in front of fireplace
tgt: Walk through the bathroom and turn left. Walk into the hallway and stop in front of the fireplace.

src: walk around house past chairs sofa large doorway kitchen turn though kitchen into hallway into bedroom wait inside doorway of bedroom next light switches
tgt: Walk around the house, past the chairs and sofa. Enter the large doorway to the kitchen. Turn left and walk though the kitchen, into the hallway and straight into the bedroom.  Wait inside the doorway of the bedroom, next to the light switches.

src: stairs wait in middle of second flight of stairs
tgt: Go down the stairs and wait in the middle of the second flight of stairs.

src: turn around hallway first room on left wait near counter
tgt: Turn around to walk down the hallway and enter the first room on the left. Wait near the counter.

src: walk parallel foot of bed exit bedroom through door at right corner in front of pass by sink on right forward until set of double doors on left just prior wall in front of through doors then
tgt: Walk parallel to the foot of the bed and exit the bedroom through the door at the right corner in front of you. Pass by the sink on your right and go forward until you see a set of double doors on your left just prior to the wall in front of you. Go through those doors and then stop.

src: first sets of steps left walk kitchen at end of hall wait by counter
tgt: Go down the first two sets of steps and make a left. Walk to the kitchen at the end of the hall and wait by the counter.

src: with doors bedrooms behind forward then right stairs after flights of stairs slightly left stop
tgt: With the doors to the two bedrooms behind you, move forward, then turn right to climb down the stairs. After descending three flights of stairs, move slightly to the left and stop.

src: bathroom door on left around white bed through open arch right door outside onto porch
tgt: Go out the bathroom door on the left. Go around the white bed and through the open arch. Take a right and go to the door to the outside. Go out onto the porch.

src: exit bedroom walk toward stairway down stairway mid way down stairs
tgt: Exit bedroom walk toward stairway, walk down stairway, and stop mid way down the stairs.

src: walk left of table then straight between chairs few feet in front of patisserie stand
tgt: Walk to the left of the table then walk straight between the chairs and go stand a few feet in front of the patisserie stand.

src: forward toward blue furniture left in main room out of main door on right once outside
tgt: Walk forward toward the blue furniture and take a left. In the main room go out of the main door on the right. Stop once you are outside.

src: turn on deck couches towards living room near coffee table couch
tgt: Turn around and go on to the deck. Pass the couches and go towards the living room. Stop near the coffee table and the couch.

src: enter room head straight until doorway straight ahead through door wait by door on right
tgt: Enter the room and head straight until you get to a doorway straight ahead go through the door and wait by the door on you right.

src: turn around out door behind across room other side of table in door left of painting with sailboats stop
tgt: Turn around and walk out the door behind you. Go across the room to the other side of the table. Go in the door to the left of the painting with sailboats and stop.

src: walk past stairs turn down second step stop
tgt: Walk past the stairs and turn left. Step down to the second step and stop.

src: forward with wall on left house left right before piano right into library in front of sink
tgt: Walk forward with the wall on your left. Enter the house and take a left. Take a right before you reach the piano and take a right into the library. Stop in front of the sink.

src: walk past couch across room walk through third doorway from left just inside doorway
tgt: Walk past the couch and across the room. Walk through the third doorway from the left. Stop just inside the doorway.

src: walk towards door with exit sign above turn walk through doorway on left bedroom around foot of bed towards bathtub turn in front of flower barrier near bathroom
tgt: walk towards the door with the exit sign above it, turn and walk through the doorway on the left, enter the bedroom, walk around the foot of the bed, towards the bathtub, turn left and stop in front of the flower barrier near the bathroom.

src: between pool chairs once door
tgt: Go left between the pool and the chairs and stop once you reach the door.

src: turn around up steps through glass doors just outside doors
tgt: Turn around and walk up the steps and through the glass doors. Stop Just outside the doors.

src: men room veer right at water fountain then veer in direction of wooden staircase pass by staircase right hallway exit on right in front of padded bench right
tgt: Exiting the men's room, veer right at the water fountain and then veer left to start walking in the direction of a wooden staircase. Pass by the staircase and turn right when the hallway leading to the exit appears on your right. Stop in front of the padded bench to your right.

src: fitness room right down hall third into closet in doorway closet
tgt: Leave the fitness room and take a right,. Walk down the hall and take your third left into the closet. Stop in the doorway to the closet.

src: walk through hallway on left hallway turn then right into kitchen walk through kitchen towards living room right wait near desk
tgt: Walk through the hallway on the left. Continue down the hallway and turn left, then right, to walk into the kitchen. Walk through the kitchen towards the living room and turn right. Wait near the desk.

src: enter building first left in doorway
tgt: Enter the building, and the first left, stopping in the doorway.

src: turn toward inside of house talk through foyer at stairs turn stairs stop
tgt: Turn toward inside of house. Talk through foyer. At stairs, turn left. Go up two stairs. Stop.

src: walk around bed out bedroom hallway first door on right into bedroom in doorway tub toilet
tgt: Walk around the bed and out the bedroom. Go down the hallway to the first door on the right. Go into the bedroom and stop in the doorway to the tub and toilet.

src: hallway fireplace then slightly stairs kitchen wait by first bar stool
tgt: Go down the hallway and pass the fireplace then turn slightly left and pass the stairs and when you get to the kitchen wait by the first bar stool.

src: through kitchen turn doors patio outside wait there
tgt: Go through the kitchen, turn left and exit the doors that lead to the patio outside, wait there.

src: walk into hallway toward twirly plants through hallway turn through dining room right in front of couch
tgt: Walk into the hallway toward the twirly plants. Walk through the hallway and turn left and walk through the dining room. Turn right and stop in front of the couch.

src: walk out of closet right out of bedroom turn into second door from right in front of bed
tgt: Walk out of the closet and turn right. Walk out of the bedroom and turn left. Walk into the second door from the right. Stop in front of the bed.

src: turn hallway sink on until bathtub wait there
tgt: Turn left and go down the hallway pass the sink and keep on going until you get to the bathtub and wait there.

src: walk out of closet into bedroom right right again into hallway hall slightly laundry room near sink
tgt: Walk out of the closet into the bedroom, turn right and right again into the hallway. Cross the hall, angling slightly left, and enter the laundry room. Stop near the sink.

src: walk past table chairs into hallway right just inside bathroom door
tgt: Walk past the table and chairs and turn left into the hallway. Turn right and stop just inside the bathroom door.

src: stairs turn at bottom walk area walk clockwise around blue counter top at far end of blue counter top
tgt: Go down the stairs and turn left at the bottom.  Walk to the kitchen area and walk clockwise around the blue counter top.  Stop at the far end of the blue counter top.

src: walk past bed turn through door down hall turn inside large doorway next double doors
tgt: Walk past the bed and turn left. Walk through the door and down the hall. Turn left and wait inside the large doorway next to the sliding double doors.

src: turn around computer desk on left slight left walk towards center of room long tables wait
tgt: Turn around and walk passed the computer desk on your left. Make a slight left and walk towards the center of the room. Stop when you reach the two long tables and wait.

src: exit room turn into exercise room straight left pool on right into room sharp left into massage room stop
tgt: Exit the room, turn left into the exercise room, go straight and to the left passed the pool on the right into the room and take a sharp left into a massage room and stop.

src: exit room hard right into hallway end stop wait near partition
tgt: Exit the room and turn hard right into the hallway to its end. Stop and wait near the partition.

src: exit bathroom left through office area then exit outside area wait
tgt: Exit bathroom, make a left, pass through office area, then exit to the outside area, and wait.

src: face treadmill doorway on left past table right walk through doorway on left in front of phone
tgt: face the treadmill, walk thought the doorway on the left, walk past the table and turn right walk through the doorway on the left and stop in front of the phone.

src: down hall into large room right through center double doors past table stop
tgt: Walk down the hall into the large room and turn right. Walk through the center double doors past the table and stop.

src: walk toward door with vented bottom turn kitchen walk past trellised wall into small hallway into double bedroom arrive between beds
tgt: Walk toward the door with the vented bottom and turn left to leave the kitchen. Walk past the trellised wall into a small hallway. Go left into the double bedroom. Arrive between two beds.

src: walk through doorway towards stairs turn near front door right of chairs past small desk with bench past fireplace as rug
tgt: walk through the doorway towards the stairs, turn left near the front door, walk to the right of the chairs, past the small desk with the bench, continue straight past the fireplace, and stop as you reach the rug.

src: exit room then right stairs right into kitchen wait by small painting on wall on right
tgt: Exit the room then go right and pass the stairs. Go right and into the kitchen. Wait by the small painting on the wall on the right.

src: exit bathroom into bedroom with blue white bed covers exit that bedroom right into living area with brown sofas chair next tall lamp
tgt: Exit the bathroom into the bedroom with the blue and white bed covers. Exit that bedroom and turn right into the living area with the two brown sofas and rocking chair. Stop next to the tall lamp.

src: down stairs forward into bathroom stop near bathroom sink
tgt: Walk down the stairs, walk forward into the bathroom, stop near the bathroom sink.

src: turn down hall at first door turn
tgt: Turn left and walk down the hall, at the first door turn left and stop.

src: exit room under construction move into hall into first bedroom on right in doorway of bathroom
tgt: Exit the room under construction and move into the hall. Turn into the first bedroom on the right and stand in the doorway of the bathroom.

src: turn right staircase around bend up top of stairs top wait
tgt: Turn to the right and go up the staircase, around the bend, up to the top of the stairs.  When you get to the top, stop there and wait.

src: walk past audio/visual shelves up stairs wait at top of landing
tgt: Walk past audio/visual shelves. Walk up stairs. Wait at top of landing.

src: exit bedroom right then head outside near large cactus
tgt: Exit the bedroom and turn right.  Then head outside. Stop near the large cactus.

src: walk out of bathroom bedroom into hall in hall left into laundry room in front of sink in laundry room
tgt: Walk out of the bathroom, and bedroom into the hall. in the Hall take a left, and another left into the laundry room. Stop in front of the sink in the laundry room.

src: bathroom walk straight across hallway room on other side just before on yellow rug under dining table
tgt: Leave the bathroom and walk straight across the hallway to the room on the other side.  Stop just before stepping on the yellow rug under the dining table.

src: walk past glass desk exit room into hallway turn staircase in middle of bottom landing
tgt: Walk past the glass desk and exit the room into the hallway. Turn left and walk to the staircase. Stop in the middle of the bottom landing.

src: walk past granite bar on left turn straight past staircase turn into bedroom wait near closet doors on left
tgt: Walk past the granite bar on the left and turn left. Continue straight past the staircase and turn left. Continue into the bedroom and wait near the closet doors on the left.

src: walk around wooden furniture towards stairwell up stairs top of next level
tgt: Walk around the wooden furniture towards the stairwell. Walk up the stairs to the top of the next level.

src: exit bedroom right down hallway stairs right down stairs wait on landing
tgt: Exit the bedroom, turn right and walk down the hallway to the stairs, turn right and walk down the stairs, wait on the landing.

src: turn into ballroom/meeting room area turn ballroom right at entrance tables chairs
tgt: Turn around and go into the ballroom/meeting room area.  Turn left and walk to the ballroom.  You should stop right at the entrance where the tables and chairs are.

src: walk through doorway second from right of wall of family pictures forward towards pictures of kids then right through bedroom then once into bathroom
tgt: Walk through the doorway that is second from the right of the wall of family pictures. Continue forward towards the pictures of the two kids and then turn right and walk through the bedroom and then stop once you walk into the bathroom.

src: walk toward white table until shower stairs wait at top of stairs
tgt: Walk toward the white table. Continue walking until you pass the shower and reach the stairs. Wait at the top of the stairs.

src: left walking towards exit sign left through first doorway on right towards middle of room stop
tgt: Take a left, and start walking towards the exit sign. Take a left, and walk through the first doorway on your right. Walk towards the middle of the room and stop.

src: walk behind couch steps right steps at turn steps turn last step at end of stairs in hall
tgt: Walk behind couch to steps, turn right and walk down steps. At landing turn left continue down steps. turn left and take last step. stop at end of stairs in hall.

src: up stairs wait near top of stairs
tgt: Walk up the stairs and wait near the top of the stairs.

src: stairs into room with yellow bed right int room walk past purple bed into bathroom next tub
tgt: Continue up the stairs and into the room with the yellow bed. Turn right int he room. Walk past the purple bed and into the bathroom. Stop next to the tub.

src: turn movie area through left doorway turn along hall right on first doorway right wait in bathroom
tgt: Turn around and exit the movie area through the left doorway. Turn left and walk along the hall. Turn right on the first doorway to your right. Wait in the bathroom.

src: up steps right up steps turn down hall in bedroom doorway on right
tgt: Walk up the steps and turn right. Walk up the steps and turn left. Walk down the hall and stop in the bedroom doorway on the right.

src: head toward plant book case hallway steps into room then into bathroom wait near toilet on left
tgt: Head toward the plant and the book case. Continue down the hallway, go down the steps and into the room then turn left and go into the bathroom. Wait near the toilet on the left.

src: walk out of bathroom walk right past oven through kitchen walk past refrigerator right
tgt: Walk out of the bathroom and walk right past the oven and through the kitchen. Walk past the refrigerator and turn right and stop.

src: up stairs right past table into bedroom at end of hall by wicker chest of drawers
tgt: Walk up the stairs and turn right. Walk past the table into the bedroom at the end of the hall. Stop by the wicker chest of drawers.

src: up stairs right at rope barrier turn after rope barrier right through doorway next on left
tgt: walk up the stairs, turn right at rope barrier, turn left after rope barrier,  turn right and walk through doorway, stop next to chair on left.

src: exit barbecue area enter through door on left across living area wait in hallway
tgt: Exit the barbecue area and enter through the door on left. Walk across the living area and wait in the hallway.

src: walk kitchen left of left of marble-topped island with sink flight of stairs turn at landing at top of stairs kitchen
tgt: Walk to the kitchen.  To the left of the left of the marble-topped island with the sink, there is a flight of stairs.  Turn left and stop at the landing at the top of the stairs exiting the kitchen.

src: enter door slight right forward left then into bathroom
tgt: Enter door. Slight right. Go forward. Take a left, then enter into the bathroom.

src: enter office turn exit office hall in bathroom doorway on left
tgt: enter office, turn left, exit office, enter hall, stop in bathroom doorway on left.

src: walk forward curves of hallway path of hallway straight not sharp turns.enter bathroom wait at mirror
tgt: Walk forward and follow the curves of the hallway. keep following the path of the hallway straight.  Do not make any sharp turns.Enter the bathroom and wait at the mirror.

src: left at stairs down stairs out door ahead of slight right turn at floor vase at banister
tgt: Make a left at the stairs. Walk down the stairs. Walk out the door ahead of you. Make a slight right turn at the floor vase. Stop at the banister.

src: stairs then right hallway golden lion statues left into room wait near tv
tgt: Go up the stairs then turn right and go down the hallway. When you get to two golden lion statues turn left and go into that room. Wait near the tv.

src: walk into bathroom
tgt: Walk into the bathroom.

src: bathroom right down hall up stairs house through main door stop
tgt: Leave the bathroom and take a right. Walk down the hall and up the stairs. Leave the house through the main door and stop.

src: move through bathroom door right forward with large counter top left right entryway for stairs just past oven on right in few feet stop
tgt: Move through the bathroom door. Turn right and move forward with a large counter top to your left. Turn right when you to the entryway for the stairs, which is just past the oven on your right. Move in a few feet and stop.

src: walk right around fireplace through doorway right wait in hallway by pocket door
tgt: Walk to the right, around the fireplace, through the doorway and turn right. Wait in the hallway by the pocket door.

src: bedroom into dining room walk stairs on fourth stair from bottom
tgt: Leave the bedroom and go into the dining room. Walk to the stairs and go up. Stop on the fourth stair from the bottom.

src: walk inside straight forward carpeted area
tgt: Walk inside.  Continue straight forward and stop when you reach the carpeted sitting area.

src: into bedroom sharp right into doorway straight down hall then at first archway on left
tgt: Go into the bedroom, make sharp right into doorway. Go straight down hall and then turn left at the first archway on the left.

src: turn into hallway turn again hallway into kitchen out back door on rug just outside doorway
tgt: Turn left and walk into the hallway.  Turn left again and go down the hallway, into the kitchen and out the back door.  Stop on the rug just outside the doorway.

src: face table walk around table on right side straight right turn after sink turn at first turn bedroom near foot of bed
tgt: Face dining table and walk around the table on the right side.  Go straight and make a right turn after the sink. Turn left at the first turn and enter the bedroom. Stop near the foot of the bed.

src: walk past stairs download hall near alcove outdoors
tgt: Walk past the stairs and download hall. Stop near the alcove that leads outdoors.

src: slight left at ping pong table toward staircase wait by white chair at desk
tgt: Take a slight left at the ping pong table. Go toward the staircase. Wait by the white chair at the desk.

src: turn left balcony hallway down hallway towards horse painting at end of hall before end of hall turn right towards top of stairs down stairs first landing turn rest of stairs
tgt: Turn to the left to face the balcony hallway. Walk down the hallway towards the horse painting at the end of the hall. Before you reach the end of the hall turn to the right towards the top of the stairs. Walk down the stairs to the first landing and turn to face the rest of the stairs leading down.

src: walk forward towards big round table into hallway on left near stairs just outside of first door on left
tgt: Walk forward towards the big round table. Go into the hallway on the left near the stairs. stop just outside of the first door on your left.

src: walk toward television on wall turn before television forward through door ahead wait here
tgt: Walk toward the television on the wall.  Turn left before you reach the television.  Walk forward to exit through the door straight ahead.  Wait here.

src: turn around through great room stairs first room on left wait near ottoman
tgt: Turn around to walk through the great room, pass the stairs and enter the first room on the left. Wait near the ottoman.

src: enter door on right with desk through room out door then left room immediately door on right in empty room with ceiling fan
tgt: Enter the door on the right with the desk, travel through the room out the door, then take a left, enter the room and immediately enter the door on the right. You will be in an empty room with a ceiling fan.

src: down hall away from stairs before room at end of hall
tgt: Walk down the hall away from the stairs. Stop before you enter the room at the end of the hall.

src: walk into foyer past mirror left at column past office wait at bedroom door threshold
tgt: Walk into foyer. Walk past mirror. Make left at column. Walk past office. Wait at bedroom door threshold.

src: exit bedroom through door once outside of room hard left into doorway beside slot machine wait by mirror
tgt: Exit the bedroom through the door.  Once outside of the room, make a hard left into doorway beside the slot machine. Wait by the mirror.

src: walk through garage up small steps into open door home corner walk into adjacent doorway dining room area around dining table through open door in corner near wicker vases
tgt: Walk through the garage and up the small steps into the open door to the home. Turn the corner and walk into the adjacent doorway to a dining room area. Walk around the dining table and through the open door in the corner near two wicker vases.

src: walk right side then up stairs reach
tgt: walk and take right side. Then up stairs and reach.

src: walk past purple chairs wait behind second silver sculpture
tgt: Walk past the purple chairs. Wait behind the second silver sculpture.

src: turn right stairs once top slight left wait in front of white doorknob on right side
tgt: Turn right and move up the stairs. Once you reach the top, hang a slight left and wait in front of the white doorknob, keeping it on your right side.

src: across room chairs turn kitchen slight right chairs counter.continue dining table behind couch
tgt: Go across the room passed the chairs. turn left and enter the kitchen. Turn slight right to avoid the chairs and counter.continue passed the dining table and stop behind the couch.

src: walk forward turn forward until room wait in doorway
tgt: Walk forward and turn left. Walk forward until you reach room 339. Wait in the doorway.

src: down steps directly in front pass by brown chairs forward next left there
tgt: Walk down the steps directly in front. Pass by the two brown chairs. Continue walking forward. Take the next left. Stop there.

src: down stairs turn down stairs at bottom walk left side of single brown chair stop
tgt: walk down stairs, turn left, walk down stairs,  at bottom walk to the left side of single brown chair and stop.

src: stairs landing turn stairs straight bathroom entrance wait
tgt: Go down the stairs to the landing. Turn left and go down the stairs. Go straight to the bathroom entrance and wait.

src: walk inside down stairs at bottom of stairs in front of crab artwork
tgt: Walk inside and down the stairs.  Stop at the bottom of the stairs in front of the crab artwork.

src: along railing left of staircase left into glass doorway step in
tgt: Go along the railing to the left of the staircase, make a left into the glass doorway, take a step in and stop.

src: toward stairs left into kitchen left beyond dining table living room on left stop
tgt: Go toward the stairs, and take a left into the kitchen. Take the left beyond the dining table. Enter the living room on the left, and stop.

src: kitchen head into dining room left before dining table walk in direction of stairs next bottom of stairs before in front of stairs
tgt: Leave the kitchen and head into the dining room. Take a left before you reach the dining table and walk in the direction of the stairs. Stop next to the bottom of the stairs before you walk in front of the stairs.

src: exit room then right stairs wait on last step top
tgt: Exit the room then turn right and go up the stairs. Wait on the last step to the top.

src: inside past black sofas rug toward potted plant turn saxophone right toward window right walking next room walk inside next room stop near radiator
tgt: Go inside. Walk past the black sofas and rug toward the potted plant. Turn left and walk to the saxophone. Turn right and walk toward the window. Turn right and keep walking to the next room. Walk inside the next room and stop near the radiator.

src: turn right forward bed on right forward towards right door entrance room there
tgt: Turn right, and walk forward. Pass the bed on the right, and walk forward towards the right door entrance. Enter the room, and stop there.

src: turn down set of stairs level of home at bottom of stairs near black gold cabinet
tgt: Turn and down the set of stairs to the lower level of the home. Stop at the bottom of the stairs near the black and gold cabinet.

src: turn hallway after large pots with bushes left into living room right arch wait near front door
tgt: Turn left and go down the hallway. After you pass the three large pots with the bushes Turn left and go into the living room. Turn right and pass the arch. Wait near the front door.

src: down hallway until in front of wooden door next exist sign turn stand in front of next door over
tgt: Walk down the hallway until  you're in front of a wooden door next to an exist sign. Turn left and go stand in front of the next door over.

src: walk indoors into kitchen area through kitchen top of stairs then halfway stairs wait there
tgt: Walk indoors into the kitchen area, walk through the kitchen to the top of the stairs then walk halfway down the stairs and wait there.

src: exit bedroom main hall right wood railings left turn in front of recliners in front of door into bedroom
tgt: exit bedroom to main hall and turn right follow wood railings to the left turn left and walk in front of recliners  stop in front of door going into bedroom.

src: walk past foot of bed exit bedroom through double doors ahead of once out of bedroom quick dogleg left large room with ahead of
tgt: Walk past the foot of the bed and exit the bedroom through the double doors ahead of you. Once out of the bedroom take a quick dogleg to the left and enter the large room with a chandelier ahead of you.

src: head outside rail left until doors on right then through doorway stop
tgt: Head outside to the rail and take a left, keep going until you see sliding doors on the right, and then go through the doorway and stop.

src: turn right stairs doorway not door wait at bottom of stairs
tgt: Turn right and go down the stairs. Enter the doorway that does not have a door. Wait at the bottom of the stairs.

src: straight then into room with number sign around staircase in tiled laundry room
tgt: Go straight and then go left into the room with the number 1 sign.  Go around the staircase and stop in the tiled laundry room.

src: enter room with large rounded mirror on left straight turn through door ahead at hallway
tgt: Enter the room with the large rounded mirror on the left. Go straight and turn left to go through the door ahead. Stop at the hallway.

src: turn around past bar stools once bar stools right large entry way hallway right end right once bedroom
tgt: Turn around and walk past all the bar stools. Once you pass the bar stools, turn right and enter the large entry way. Go down the hallway to the right to the end and turn right. Stop once you enter the bedroom.

src: through kitchen then right then hallway into first door on left then there
tgt: Go through the kitchen then turn right and then left to the hallway. Go into the first door on your left then wait there.

src: walk through door away from left wait at top of white marble stairs
tgt: Walk through the door furthest away from you and take a left. Wait at the top of the white marble stairs.

src: walk towards stairs at bottom of stairs top in front of weight on cabinet on of stairs
tgt: Walk towards and go down the stairs. At the bottom of the stairs top in front of the weight on the cabinet on he left of the stairs.

src: walk across room bed on right through doorway hall right wait at top of stairs
tgt: Walk across the room passing the bed on the right. Exit through the doorway and go down the hall. Turn right and wait at the top of the stairs.

src: walk past fireplace exit room through doorway on right immediately turn through hallway right on stairway landing
tgt: Walk past the fireplace and exit the room through the doorway on the right. Immediately turn left, walk through the hallway, turn right and wait on the stairway landing.

src: right wall couch ledge right door on right in front of washing machine
tgt: Go to your right and follow the wall. Go passed the couch and the ledge. Turn right and enter the door on the right. Stop in front of the washing machine.

src: turn down hallway past open house doors corner left through door at end of hall into bedroom with large beds through room into bathroom near sink
tgt: Turn around walk down the hallway past the open house doors and turn the corner to the left. Walk through the door at the end of the hall and into the bedroom with two large beds. Walk through the room and into the bathroom stopping near the sink.

src: closet turn at kitchen area walk patio behind first chair out there near corner column
tgt: Leave the closet and turn left at the kitchen area.  Walk to the patio and stop behind the first chair out there near the corner column.

src: walk forward through ornate double doors into hallway in hall forward into room on left in doorway room
tgt: walk forward through the ornate double doors and into the hallway In the hall walk forward and go into the sitting room on the left. Stop in the doorway to the sitting room.

src: exit bedroom enter room with table football game wait here
tgt: Exit bedroom and enter room with table football game.  Wait here.

src: walkway room walk past fireplace wait in archway dining room
tgt: Go down the walkway to the sitting room. Walk past the fireplace and wait in the archway to the dining room.

src: walk through corridor down steps at bottom of steps
tgt: Walk straight through corridor, and down steps. Stop at bottom of steps.

src: turn past pool table bedroom on left wait near closet door
tgt: Turn left, walk past the Pool table and enter the bedroom on the left. Wait near the closet door.

src: walk out of closet turn in entryway
tgt: Walk out of the closet and turn left. Stop in the entryway.

src: walk past bed walk past green double chaises wait at threshold of white door
tgt: Walk past bed. Walk past green double chaises. Wait at threshold of white door.

src: with kitchen behind straight past round table chairs down stairs straight bedroom after into bedroom
tgt: With the kitchen behind you, walk straight past the round table and chairs and down the stairs.  Keep going straight and enter the bedroom.  Stop after stepping into the bedroom.

src: down steps turn follow steps way hard right enter stairs straight into room stop at picture on wall right
tgt: Walk down steps, turn left and follow steps to entry way. Turn hard right and enter go down stairs. Walk straight into dining room. Stop at picture on wall to the right.

src: turn around past large table forward door outside stop right in front of door
tgt: Turn around and walk past the large table. Keep heading forward to the door leading outside and stop right in front of the door.

src: down hallway toward paintings living room wait behind gray couch
tgt: Walk down the hallway toward the paintings, enter the living room, wait behind the gray couch.

src: turn hallway turn right at end of hallway by water cooler wait there
tgt: Turn around and go down the hallway.  Turn to the right at the end of the hallway. Stop by the water cooler.  Wait there.

src: position so windows on left walk straight past front door columns stairs enter into room with circular couch around fireplace at end of couch closest in pot on left of fireplace
tgt: Position yourself so the windows are on your left and walk straight past the front door, columns, and stairs.  Enter into the larger room with a circular couch around a fireplace.  Stop at the end of the couch closest to tree in the pot on the left of the fireplace.

src: walk into hallway right wait in doorway next bathroom at end of hall
tgt: Walk into the hallway and to the right. Wait in the doorway next to the bathroom, at the end of the hall.

src: walk towards hallway in door frame prior hallway
tgt: Walk towards the hallway and stop in the door frame prior to entering the hallway.

src: down stairs turn right through area by balcony doors
tgt: Walk down the stairs, turn right, walk through the sitting area, stop by the balcony doors.

src: door outside degrees left then forward left forward past dinning table on left then after chair on right right into hallway at door right
tgt: Facing the door to the outside, turn 90 degrees to the left, then go forward and to the left. Move forward past the dinning table on your left. Then after passing the 2nd chair on your right, turn right and step into the hallway, stopping at the door to your right.

src: walk into room spiral stairs wait there
tgt: Walk straight into the room. Go up the spiral stairs. Wait there.

src: bathroom move towards bed in center of wood floor next refrigerator
tgt: Leave the bathroom and move towards the bed. Stop in the center of the wood floor next to the refrigerator.

src: through near doorway left through doorway then right top of stairs stairs midway level wait
tgt: Go through the near doorway and make a left through the doorway and then make a right and go to the top of the stairs, go down the stairs to the midway level and wait.

src: turn right top of stairs through wood doors once through turn down hallway up small set of steps stop
tgt: Turn right and walk to the top of the stairs and through the wood doors. Once through, turn left and walk down the hallway. Walk up the small set of steps and stop.

src: turn right into hallway turn down hallway wait by bedroom
tgt: Turn right, walk into the hallway, turn left, walk down the hallway, and wait by the bedroom.

src: bathroom out of bedroom into hallway forward stairs on fourth stair from top
tgt: Leave the bathroom and go out of the bedroom into the hallway.  Go forward and go down the stairs. Stop on the fourth stair from the top.

src: walk past bed right bathroom wait by toilet
tgt: Walk past the bed, turn right, enter the bathroom, wait by the toilet.

src: walk left of dining room table chairs past television turn across entryway inside garage
tgt: Walk to the left of the dining room table and chairs and past the television. Turn left and walk across the entryway and stop inside the garage.

src: past big chairs up short staircase into room hard left into bathroom stop
tgt: Go past the big chairs and up the short staircase. Go into the room and turn hard left. Go into the bathroom and stop.

src: stairs at bottom right
tgt: Descend the stairs and at the bottom, turn right and stop.

src: walk out of closet straight balcony wait
tgt: Walk out of the closet and go straight to the balcony and wait.

src: walk through living room area past natural wooden table top walk past armchair around fireplace right through open double doors with plaque above around stairwell into hallway walk past rotary phone on wall walk into open door at end near elevator into bathroom
tgt: Walk through the living room area past the natural wooden table top. Walk past the armchair and around the fireplace to the right through the open double doors with a plaque above it. Walk around the stairwell and into the hallway. Walk past the rotary phone hanging on the wall. Walk into the open door at the end near the elevator and into a bathroom.

src: walk out of blue wall bedroom into hallway in hallway turn left walk second of brown chairs
tgt: Walk out of the blue wall bedroom and into the hallway. In the hallway, turn to the left and walk to the second of the two brown chairs.

src: straight past pool turn into house large glass doors table wait near door room
tgt: Go straight past the pool. Turn left and go into the house using the large glass sliding doors. Pass the table and wait near the door to exit the room.

src: walk through room exit via door next giant clock down hallway right at top of stairs in doorway deck
tgt: Walk through the room and exit via the door next to the giant clock.  Walk down the hallway and turn right at the top of the stairs.  Stop in the doorway to the deck.

src: walk through double glass doors into living area turn past dining table hallway right at first doorway wait in laundry room
tgt: Walk through the double glass doors into the living area and turn left. Walk past the dining table and towards the hallway. Turn right at the first doorway and wait in the laundry room.

src: enter large lobby turn walk end of room at center through double doors on porch
tgt: Enter large lobby and turn left. walk to the end of the room at center through double doors and stop on porch.

src: walk around big display turn left through entryway down hallway by other display on right
tgt: Walk around the big roped off display and turn left. Go through that entryway and down that hallway. Stop by the other roped off display on your right.

src: room into room across hall then wait by bed in room
tgt: Leave the room and go into the room across the hall then wait by the bed in the room.

src: walk forward towards couch between couch chair left at counter walk end of room left in hallway room on inside of room past doorway
tgt: Walk forward towards the couch, and between the couch and the chair. Take a left at the counter and walk to the end of the room and take a left in the hallway. Enter the room and stop on the inside of the room past the doorway.

src: turn men room stand near sink
tgt: Turn around and enter the men's room.  Stand near the sink.

src: walk towards chair at end of long table right towards brick wall walk until vase of white flowers stop
tgt: Walk towards the chair at the end of the long table. Turn right and begin walking towards the brick wall. Walk until you have reached the vase of white flowers and stop.

src: away from meeting room doors through tables wait at temporary wood/fabric wall towards very back of room
tgt: Walk away from the meeting room doors. Walk through the tables and wait at the temporary wood/fabric wall towards the very back of the room.

src: inside left into living room left into powder room on rug right next door
tgt: Go inside and take a left. Walk into the living room and take a left into the powder room. Stop on the rug right next to the door.

src: turn then right small rug on floor turn outside next black rug
tgt: Turn left and then turn right. When you reach small rug on the floor turn left. Walk outside and wait next the black rug.

src: exit room stairs right at top of stairs immediate left through opening
tgt: Exit the room and climb the stairs to your right. At the top of the stairs, take an immediate left through the opening.

src: step forward right up stairs at landing right second flight of stairs at top of stairs straight ahead until dining room table in front of table
tgt: Step forward, turn right, and walk up the stairs.  At the landing, turn right and continue up the second flight of stairs.  At the top of the stairs, walk straight ahead until you get to the dining room table.  Stop in front of the table.

src: head stairs turn at top of stairs laundry room right before bedroom ahead into bathroom through first doorway on right there
tgt: Head up the stairs. Turn left at the top of the stairs. Pass the laundry room. Turn right before reaching the bedroom ahead. Turn into the bathroom through the first doorway on the right. Stop there.

src: up stairs right at landing up next set of stairs wait at top
tgt: Walk up the stairs to your right. Turn left at the landing and walk up the next set of stairs and wait at the top.

src: turn room once in pool room past pool right into doorway stairs elevator reception area
tgt: Turn left and exit the room. Once in the pool room, walk past the pool and turn right. Walk into the doorway and stop facing the stairs, elevator and reception area.

src: exit bathroom short dogleg right stop after room ahead
tgt: Exit the bathroom and take a short dogleg to the right, the stop after entering the room ahead.

src: walk across room past glass wood wall separator wicker basket down hall across mosaic floor enter door on opposite wall turn inside room in front of massage table
tgt: Walk across room past glass and wood wall separator and wicker basket. Walk down hall and across mosaic floor. Enter left door on opposite wall. Turn left. Stop inside room in front of massage table.

src: exit office right straight toward clear table chairs right table wait near stairs up on right
tgt: Exit the office. Turn right. Walk straight toward the clear table and chairs. Turn right and pass the table. Wait near the stairs that go up on the right.

src: into large room marble counter with stools in direction until room with ovens stovetops long serving window oudside wait
tgt: Go into the large room and towards the marble counter with stools  Continue in the direction until you enter a room with ovens and stovetops and a long serving window that opens to the oudside and wait.

src: exit pool room through door on right by tub
tgt: exit pool room through door on right, stop by tub.

src: down path past cactus past plants into room stop by door
tgt: Walk down the path past the cactus. Keep walking past the plants step into the room and stop by the door.

src: past second sink out door down hall into closet there
tgt: Go past the second sink and out the door. Walk down the hall into the closet and stop there.

src: around staircase past bar through door just inside door at pool with bar on right
tgt: Go around the staircase, walking past the bar. Walk through the door, and stop just inside the door, looking at the pool with a bar on your right.

src: straight couches near windows in corner
tgt: Go straight passed the couches and stop near the windows in the corner.

src: move towards refrigerator right after kitchen island walk towards hallway in middle of hallway
tgt: Move towards the refrigerator. Turn right after the kitchen island. Walk towards the hallway and stop in the middle of the hallway.

src: past main entrance hall with large tapestry into office with walnut table crystal vase on mantle
tgt: Go past the main entrance and travel down the hall with the large tapestry and into the office with the walnut table and crystal vase on the mantle.

src: walk towards sofa turn across door turn again next room walk across office area right room right wait by sink in bathroom
tgt: Walk towards the sofa. Turn left and walk across the door. Turn left again and enter the next room. Walk across the office area and turn right. Enter the room to your right. Wait by the sink in the bathroom.

src: through door opposite bathroom white bed through door on right straight through double doors
tgt: Go through the door opposite the bathroom. Continue to the white bed. Turn around and go through the door on the right. Go straight through the double doors.

src: turn right top of stairs down stairs then right stairs few steps near dining room then there
tgt: Turn right and go to the top of the stairs.  Walk down the stairs, and then take a right when you get down the stairs.  You'll go a few steps, near the dining room and then you'll stop and wait there.

src: exit bedroom turn right.walk past staircase door on right in front of entryway through door in office area
tgt: Exit the bedroom and turn right.Walk past the staircase and to the door on the right in front of an entryway. Go through the door and you'll be in an office area.

src: turn right exit out double wood doors once turn right end of hallway double wood doors once inside turn on rug in front of animal print chair
tgt: Turn right and exit out the double wood doors. Once out turn right and walk to the end of the hallway and enter the double wood doors. Once inside, turn left and stop on the rug in front of the animal print chair.

src: exit bathroom right then toward kitchen wait near kitchen area
tgt: Exit the bathroom. Turn right and then turn left and walk toward the kitchen. Wait near kitchen area.

src: exit room through middle doorway wait at table
tgt: Exit the room through the middle doorway, and wait at the table.

src: turn on rug in front of bench with giraffe print
tgt: Turn left and wait on the rug in front of the bench with the giraffe print.

src: turn through kitchen then stairs on first landing
tgt: Turn left and walk through the kitchen.  Then walk up the stairs and stop on the first landing.

src: turn right out of bedroom door turn once into hallway then right at first door into bathroom into doorway
tgt: Turn to the right and walk out of the bedroom door.  Turn left once you get into the hallway.  Then turn right at the first door.  You'll be looking into the bathroom.  Stop when you get into the doorway.

src: walk into living room next red ottoman
tgt: Walk into the living room and stand next to the red ottoman.

src: steps right at counter top
tgt: go up steps, turn right, stop at counter top.

src: outside double doors turn into house again turn then right into bathroom wait near entrance
tgt: Go outside using the double doors. Turn left and go into the house again. Turn left and then turn right into the bathroom. Wait near the entrance.

src: head long hallway turn at exit sign numbered lockers on left kitchenette on right
tgt: Head down the long hallway and turn left at the exit sign.  Stop where numbered lockers are on the left, and the kitchenette is on your right.

src: walk along porch past bench table walk into entry door home into home walk into hallway past desk ahead forward through hall in next room near counter top area
tgt: Walk along the tiled porch past the bench and table. Walk into the entry door to the home. Continue into the home and walk into the hallway past the desk ahead. Continue forward through the hall and stop in the next room near the counter top and dining area.

src: exit bathroom door right walk bedroom door exit through left hallway step through door right dining room right there
tgt: Exit the bathroom door and turn right. Walk to the bedroom door and exit through it. Turn left and go down the hallway.  Take one step through the door to your right which is the dining room. Stop right there.

src: exit bathroom toward bedroom then bedroom door on left then straight until into room wait by first green chair
tgt: Exit the bathroom toward the bedroom then exit the bedroom using the door on the left then turn left and head straight until you go into the room. Wait by the first green chair.

src: dining table behind stairs at top of stairs right bedroom just after room
tgt: Put the dining table behind you and go up the stairs.  At the top of the stairs turn right and enter the bedroom.  Stop just after entering the room.

src: with deck behind way down right side of room couches fireplace after final couch in front of white door
tgt: With the deck behind you, walk all the way down the right side of the room, passing couches and a fireplace.  Stop after you pass the final couch and are in front of the white door.

src: down stairs right stairs stop at bottom of stairs at sauna
tgt: Walk down stairs, turn right and continue down stairs, stop at bottom of stairs at sauna.

src: with pool back staircase second floor patio left of staircase covered archway with table under table towards blue basketball court off of tile floor of patio onto rock in between patio court
tgt: With the pool to your back, locate the staircase to the second floor patio.  To the left of the staircase a covered archway with a table under it.  Proceed to the table, walking passed it heading towards the blue basketball court.  Step off of the tile floor of the patio onto the rock, and stop in between the patio and the court.

src: walk out of bedroom walk under stairs right
tgt: Walk out of the bedroom. Walk under the stairs. Turn right and stop.

src: exit spa room walk into reception area through set of double doors wait there
tgt: Exit the spa room and walk into the reception area through the set of double doors.  Wait there.

src: turn past table chairs into main part of house veer left in dining room through doorway into hallway bedroom door
tgt: Turn around, go past the table and chairs.  Go into the main part of the house and veer to the left in the dining room.  Go through a doorway and into a hallway.  You must stop when you get to the bedroom door.

src: dining area head kitchen enter area left of kitchen also stove in front of jar of marshmallows
tgt: Leave the dining area, and head to the kitchen. Enter area left of the kitchen which also has a stove. Stop in front of the jar of marshmallows.

src: walk ahead past stove sink refrigerator washer dryer once bedroom door past washer dryer
tgt: Walk straight ahead past the stove, sink, refrigerator, washer and dryer. Stop once you reach the bedroom door past the washer and dryer.

src: turn around past table right into den right into bathroom ahead in front of sink
tgt: Turn around and walk past the table and take a right. Walk into the den and take a right. Walk into the bathroom straight ahead and wait in front of the sink.

src: turn left around table left pass by next table as well between table last table stop
tgt: Turn to your left and walk around the table to your left. Pass by the next table as well and turn left between that table and the last table and stop.

src: turn left stone path past pool house wait by door
tgt: Turn to the left and follow stone path past the pool. Enter the house and wait by the door.

src: with stairs behind forward at corner just before door ahead forward by glass door on right steps through wooden door ahead of just after room
tgt: With the stairs behind you, go forward and turn left at the corner just before the door straight ahead. Continue moving forward passing by the glass door on your right. Climb the two steps and go through the wooden door ahead of you. Stop just after entering that room.

src: desk steps right toward bed turn enter closet
tgt: Leave desk and walk up steps. Turn right and walk toward bed. Turn left and enter closet.

src: exit room right stairs turn through doorway up stairs wait at foot of curved steps
tgt: Exit room, turn right and go up stairs. Turn left through the doorway and walk up the stairs. Wait at the foot of the curved steps.

src: walk across room exit wait at bottom of stairs
tgt: Walk across sitting room and exit, wait at bottom of stairs.

src: picture of guitar through door on right stairs step into bedroom in o'clock position from top of stairs stop after into room
tgt: Facing the picture of the guitar, go through the door on the right.  Go up the stairs and step into the bedroom in the 1 o'clock position from the top of the stairs.  Stop after stepping into the room.

src: stairs then right wait near kitchen sink
tgt: Go down the stairs then turn right and wait near the kitchen sink.

src: bathroom walk right massage room last door on right into room right inside room next door
tgt: Leave the bathroom and walk to the right. Enter the massage room that is the last door on your right. Walk into the room that is the farthest right and stop inside, the room next to the door.

src: up stairs stop
tgt: Walk up the stairs and stop.

src: into doorway bed past bed through door
tgt: Go into the doorway that leads to a bed. Go past the bed and through the door.

src: exit bathroom at bed turn into hallway at double doors on left
tgt: exit bathroom to bedroom at bed turn left and walk into hallway. Stop at double doors on your left.

src: into room with staircase right between grey couch glass table after glass table right before left of thermostat
tgt: Go into the room with the staircase to the right, go between the grey couch and the glass table, after passing the glass table make a right, and stop before and to the left of the thermostat.

src: exit room right past living room area wait by column
tgt: Exit the room and turn right. Walk past the living room and dining area. Wait by the column.

src: bathroom walk through bedroom bedroom by door on left out of bedroom down hall end of hall by elevator right at foot of stairs from there
tgt: Leave the bathroom and walk through the bedroom to exit the bedroom by the door on your left.  Make a left out of the bedroom and walk down the hall.  When you get to the end of the hall by the elevator, make a right and stop at the foot of the stairs ascending from there.

src: with bathroom right room then hallway passing by stairs on left eventually room at extreme end of hallway
tgt: With the bathroom to your right, exit the room, then turn left and go down the hallway, passing by the stairs on your left to eventually enter the room at the extreme end of the hallway.

src: walk through doorway sharp turn right then behind couch walk past table with plants by dining room table chairs
tgt: Walk through the doorway and make a sharp turn right then left behind the couch. Walk past the table with the plants and stop by the dining room table and chairs.

src: up stairs turn up first section of stairs wait there
tgt: Walk up the stairs. Turn left and walk up the first section of stairs. Wait there.

src: bathroom left in hallway then right in other hallway inside room left room wait in hallway in front of first room on right
tgt: Leave the bathroom and make a left in the hallway then make a right in the other hallway. Go inside the room and make a left to leave the room. Wait in the hallway in front of the first room on the right.

src: turn hall turn bedroom walk past bed bathroom wait in front of sink
tgt: Turn around and enter the hall. Turn left and enter the bedroom. Walk past the bed, enter the bathroom and wait in front of the sink.

src: exit bathroom walk though adjacent room past black desk desk on left as in next room sink sink on left as
tgt: Exit the bathroom and walk though the adjacent room past the black desk. The desk will be on your left as you pass.  In the next room, stop when you get to the sink.  The sink will be on your left as you approach.

src: around table near window on past ornate clock straight until large office
tgt: Go around the table near the window and continue on past the ornate clock and go straight until you find the large office.

src: with ping pong table behind down length of room staircases one on right on first stop
tgt: With the ping pong table behind you, walk down the length of the room.  When you see two staircases, take the one on the right and stop on the first stop.

src: bookshelf door on same wall as bookshelf right travel past elephant photo left into next room with couch at bowl of apples
tgt: Locate the bookshelf. Enter the door that is located on the same wall as the bookshelf. Turn right and travel past the elephant photo, and go left into the next room with a couch. Stop at the bowl of apples.

src: closet room left right foyer right into office in doorway office
tgt: Leave the closet and the room. Take a left, and right. Enter the foyer and take a right into the office. Stop in the doorway to the office.

src: exit bedroom walk into next bedroom in hall stand in room bathroom doorway
tgt: Exit the bedroom and walk into the next bedroom in the hall. Go stand in that room's bathroom doorway.
